msgstr ""
"For at oprette en udfordring skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Settings --"
"> Gamification Tools --> Challenges`. Klik på :guilabel:`New` i øverste "
"venstre hjørne for at åbne en tom udfordringsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:92
msgid "At the top of the form, enter a :guilabel:`Challenge Name`."
msgstr "Øverst i formularen skal du indtaste et :guilabel:`Udfordringsnavn`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:95
