msgstr "Visning af sektionen for tildelingsregler i en udfordringsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:115
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Periodicity` field, select a time frame for goals to be "
"automatically assessed."
msgstr ""
"I feltet :guilabel:`Periodicitet` skal du vælge en tidsramme for automatisk "
