msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forventet MRR`: Måler den forventede månedlige tilbagevendende "
"omsætning for en mulighed."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/performance/win_loss.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prorated MRR`: Measures the prorated monthly recurring revenue of "
"an opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forholdsmæssig MRR`: Måler den forholdsmæssige månedlige "
"tilbagevendende omsætning for en mulighed."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/performance/win_loss.rst:149
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prorated Recurring Revenues`: Measures the prorated recurring "
"revenues of an opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forholdsmæssige tilbagevendende indtægter`: Måler de "
