#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:5
msgid ""
"The preparation display helps manage POS orders that require preparation "
"prior to completion. It is intended for use in environments where ordered "
"items must be assembled, cooked, or otherwise processed before they are "
"handed over to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Forberedelsesdisplayet hjælper med at administrere POS-ordrer, der kræver "
"forberedelse inden færdiggørelse. Det er beregnet til brug i miljøer, hvor "
"bestilte varer skal samles, tilberedes eller på anden måde behandles, før de "
"udleveres til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:9
msgid "Use cases"
msgstr "Anvendelsestilfælde"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:11
msgid ""
"**For retail**: Once an order is completed and paid in the :ref:`POS "
"register <pos/use/open-register>`, it is sent to the preparation display. "
"This notifies the preparation team to collect and prepare the purchased "
"items for customer pickup."
msgstr ""
"**For detail**: Når en ordre er gennemført og betalt i :ref:`POS-registret "
"<pos/use/open-register>`, sendes den til forberedelsesdisplayet. Dette "
"underretter forberedelsesholdet om at indsamle og forberede de købte varer "
"til kundeafhentning."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:14
msgid ""
"**For restaurants**: Once orders are placed in the :ref:`POS register <pos/"
"use/open-register>`, they are sent to the preparation display to inform the "
"kitchen about the meals that need to be prepared."
msgstr ""
"**For restauranter**: Når ordrer er afgivet i :ref:`POS-registret <pos/use/"
"open-register>`, sendes de til forberedelsesdisplayet for at informere "
"køkkenet om de måltider, der skal tilberedes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:23
msgid ""
"To create and set up a preparation display, go to :menuselection:`Point of "
"Sale --> Orders --> Preparation Display`, click :guilabel:`New`, and "
"configure it:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette og konfigurere et forberedelsesdisplay skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`POS --> Ordrer --> Forberedelsesdisplay`, klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` og konfigurere det:"

