#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/presets.rst:5
msgid ""
"Presets are preconfigured settings used to quickly apply predefined "
"configurations to POS orders, such as the fiscal position, pricelist, "
"opening hours, order capacity limit, etc. They are particularly useful for "
"businesses that need different configurations depending on the type of sale."
msgstr ""
"Presets er forudkonfigurerede indstillinger, der bruges til hurtigt at "
"anvende foruddefinerede konfigurationer på POS-ordrer, såsom skatteposition, "
"prisliste, åbningstider, ordrekapacitetsgrænse osv. De er særligt nyttige "
"for virksomheder, der har brug for forskellige konfigurationer afhængigt af "
"salgstypen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/presets.rst:10
msgid ""
"Restaurants can use presets to adjust pricelists and capacities based on the "
"order type, such as :guilabel:`Dine In`, :guilabel:`Takeout`, "
"or :guilabel:`Delivery`."
msgstr ""
"Restauranter kan bruge presets til at justere prislister og kapaciteter "
"baseret på ordretype, såsom :guilabel:`Dine In`, :guilabel:`Takeout` "
"eller :guilabel:`Delivery`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/presets.rst:13
msgid ""
"Flower shops can use presets to apply different taxes when selling flowers "
"and plants (taxed as goods) versus creating arrangements for funerals or "
"weddings (taxed as services). Presets can also help streamline returns and "
"apply different pricelists (with discounts) for loyal customers and/or "
"members."
msgstr ""
"Blomsterbutikker kan bruge presets til at anvende forskellige skatter, når "
"de sælger blomster og planter (beskattet som varer) i forhold til at lave "
"arrangementer til begravelser eller bryllupper (beskattet som tjenester). "
"Presets kan også hjælpe med at strømline returer og anvende forskellige "
"prislister (med rabatter) for loyale kunder og/eller medlemmer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/presets.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Odoo Presets Tutorial <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/manage-"
