#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo Point of Sale allows you to :ref:`create products <pos/products/"
"creation>` and :ref:`manage product information <pos/products/information-"
"display>` from the backend or in the POS register. Products can "
"be :ref:`configured <pos/products/configuration>` in various ways, including "
"creating :ref:`variants <pos/products/variants>`, :ref:`product combinations "
"<pos/products/combos>`, and :ref:`POS-specific product categories <pos/"
"products/categories>`, and adding :ref:`tags <pos/products/tags>` "
"and :ref:`images <pos/products/images>`. You can also group products "
"by :ref:`units <pos/products/units>` and :ref:`manage stock <pos/products/"
"sn>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo POS giver dig mulighed for at :ref:`oprette produkter <pos/products/"
"creation>` og :ref:`administrere produktoplysninger <pos/products/"
"information-display>` fra backend eller i POS-kassesystemet. Produkter kan "
":ref:`konfigureres <pos/products/configuration>` på forskellige måder, "
"herunder oprettelse af :ref:`varianter <pos/products/variants>`, "
":ref:`produktkombinationer <pos/products/combos>` og :ref:`POS-specifikke "
"produktkategorier <pos/products/categories>`, samt tilføjelse af :ref:`tags "
"<pos/products/tags>` og :ref:`billeder <pos/products/images>`. Du kan også "
"gruppere produkter efter :ref:`enheder <pos/products/units>` og "
":ref:`administrere lager <pos/products/sn>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:16
msgid "Product creation"
msgstr "Produktoprettelse"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:18
msgid ""
"To create products from the backend, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Products --> Products`, and click :guilabel:`New` to create a product, or "
"select an existing one to edit it. Ensure the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` "
"checkbox is enabled at the top of the form, then :doc:`configure the "
"product's general information </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure>`, such as defining the :doc:`product type </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure/"
"type>`, setting a :ref:`tracking strategy <pos/products/sn>`, or adding a "
"product image, as needed. Configure advanced, POS-specific :ref:`product "
"details <pos/products/configuration>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette produkter fra backend skal du gå til :menuselection:`POS --> "
"Produkter --> Produkter` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette et "
"produkt eller vælge et eksisterende for at redigere det. Sørg for, at "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`POS` er aktiveret øverst i formularen, og "
":doc:`konfigurér produktets generelle oplysninger </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/configure>`, såsom definition "
"af :doc:`produkttype </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"product_management/configure/type>`, indstilling af en "
":ref:`sporingsstrategi <pos/products/sn>` eller tilføjelse af et "
"produktbillede efter behov. Konfigurér avancerede, POS-specifikke "
":ref:`produktdetaljer <pos/products/configuration>` efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:28
msgid ""
"It is also possible to create a product from the POS interface. To do so, "
"open the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-register>`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon, then select :guilabel:`Create "
"Product`. Enter the product details in the popover and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. The product is immediately available in the POS "
"register. Existing products can also be updated directly from the POS "
"register through the :ref:`product information popover <pos/products/"
"information-display>`."
msgstr ""
"Det er også muligt at oprette et produkt fra POS-brugerfladen. For at gøre "
"dette skal du åbne :ref:`POS-kassesystemet <pos/use/open-register>`, klikke "
"på ikonet :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburgermenu`) og derefter vælge "
":guilabel:`Opret produkt`. Indtast produktoplysningerne i popoveren og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Gem`. Produktet er straks tilgængeligt i POS-kassesystemet. "
"Eksisterende produkter kan også opdateres direkte fra POS-kassesystemet "
"gennem :ref:`produktoplysningspopoveren <pos/products/information-display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:36
msgid ""
"When using :ref:`POS product categories <pos/products/categories>`, each "
"product must be assigned to a :guilabel:`POS Category`; otherwise, the "
"product will not be displayed or available for selection."
msgstr ""
"Når du bruger :ref:`POS-produktkategorier <pos/products/categories>`, skal "
"hvert produkt tildeles en :guilabel:`POS-kategori`; ellers vises produktet "
"ikke eller er tilgængeligt for valg."

