#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:275
msgid ""
"To only display specific categories in the POS register, go to the :ref:`POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>`, navigate to the :guilabel:`Product & PoS "
"categories` section, then, in the :guilabel:`Restrict Categories` field, "
