"settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`PoS Interface` "
"section, and enable :guilabel:`Group products by categories`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ingen kategori er valgt i POS-registeret, vises alle produkter. For at "
"organisere produkter efter kategori i denne visning skal du navigere til "
":ref:`POS-indstillingerne <pos/use/settings>`, rulle ned til afsnittet "
":guilabel:`POS-grænseflade` og aktivere :guilabel:`Gruppér produkter efter "
"kategorier`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:294
msgid ""
"In this POS register, two categories are configured, :guilabel:`Food` "
"and :guilabel:`Drinks`, but neither of them is currently selected. The "
"overview shows all products in both categories, grouped by category on "
"separate rows."
msgstr ""
"I dette POS-register er to kategorier konfigureret, :guilabel:`Mad` og "
":guilabel:`Drikkevarer`, men ingen af dem er aktuelt valgt. Oversigten viser "
"alle produkter i begge kategorier, grupperet efter kategori på separate "
"rækker."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:0
msgid "Group products by categories."
msgstr "Gruppér produkter efter kategorier."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:304
msgid "Product combos"
msgstr "Produktkombinationer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:306
msgid ""
"A product combo is a bundle of multiple products sold together as a single "
"unit. Each product combo consists of multiple categories, known "
"as :ref:`combo choices <pos/products/combo-choices>`, and each combo choice "
"contains several items. When purchasing a product combo, customers can "
"select one or more items from each combo choice."
msgstr ""
"En produktkombo er en samling af flere produkter solgt sammen som en enkelt "
"enhed. Hver produktkombo består af flere kategorier, kendt som "
":ref:`kombovalg <pos/products/combo-choices>`, og hvert kombovalg indeholder "
"flere varer. Ved køb af en produktkombo kan kunderne vælge en eller flere "
"varer fra hvert kombovalg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:312
msgid ""
"A burger menu is offered as a product combo including three combo choices: "
"one burger, one drink, and one portion of fries. For each combo choice, "
"customers select one item from the available options (e.g., cheese burger or "
"bacon burger; water or soda; large or regular fries)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:0
msgid "Combo selection in the POS register."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:321
