msgstr ""
"Přejděte na :menuselection:`POS --> Produkty --> Výběry komba` a klikněte "
"na :guilabel:`Nový`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:336
msgid "Enter a name for the :guilabel:`Combo Choice`."
msgstr "Zadejte název pro :guilabel:`Výběr komba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:337
msgid ""
"Set the maximum selectable items for the combo choice using "
"the :guilabel:`Maximum items` field."
msgstr ""
"Nastavte maximální počet volitelných položek pro výběr komba pomocí "
"pole :guilabel:`Maximum položek`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:338
msgid ""
"Set the number of items included in the combo choice using "
"the :guilabel:`Includes items` field."
msgstr ""
"Nastavte počet položek zahrnutých ve výběru komba pomocí "
"pole :guilabel:`Zahrnuje položky`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:339
msgid ""
"If you are in a :doc:`multi-company </applications/general/companies/"
"multi_company>` environment, choose the relevant :guilabel:`Company`. Leave "
"the field empty to make it available for *all* companies."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:342
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` under the :guilabel:`Options` section to add "
"the products that constitute the :guilabel:`Combo Choices`."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat řádek` v sekci :guilabel:`Možnosti` a přidejte "
"produkty, které tvoří :guilabel:`Výběry komba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:344
msgid "If needed, click a product to add an :guilabel:`Extra Price`."
msgstr ""
"V případě potřeby klikněte na produkt a přidejte :guilabel:`Příplatek`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:346
msgid "Combo Price vs. Extra Price"
msgstr "Cena komba vs. příplatek"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:348
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Combo Price` field shows the price applied to any additional "
"product a customer might select (i.e., when the :guilabel:`Maximum items` "
"field is set to `2` or higher). This price is automatically calculated based "
"on the price of the least expensive product defined in the :guilabel:`Combo "
"Choice`."
msgstr ""
"Pole :guilabel:`Cena komba` zobrazuje cenu uplatněnou na jakýkoli další "
"produkt, který si zákazník může vybrat (tj. když je pole :guilabel:`Maximum "
"položek` nastaveno na `2` nebo vyšší). Tato cena se automaticky vypočítá na "
"základě ceny nejlevnějšího produktu definovaného ve :guilabel:`Výběru komba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:352
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Price` field is used to set an additional charge for a "
"specific product in the combo choice, e.g., to cover higher costs or "
"encourage upselling. This extra price is applied each time a customer "
"selects that product within the combo choice."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Ekstra pris` bruges til at angive et ekstra gebyr for et "
"specifikt produkt i kombovalget, f.eks. for at dække højere omkostninger "
"eller tilskynde til mersalg. Denne ekstrapris anvendes hver gang en kunde "
"vælger det pågældende produkt inden for kombovalget."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:359
msgid "Product combo creation"
msgstr "Oprettelse af produktkombo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:361
msgid ""
"To create a specific product that contains :ref:`combo choices <pos/products/"
"combo-choices>`, follow the next steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et specifikt produkt, der indeholder :ref:`kombovalg <pos/"
"products/combo-choices>`, skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:364
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Products --> Products` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Produkter --> Produkter` og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:365
msgid "Enter a product name."
msgstr "Indtast et produktnavn."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:366
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Combo` and select the "
"relevant :ref:`Combo Choices <pos/products/combo-choices>`."
msgstr ""
"Indstil :guilabel:`Produkttype` til :guilabel:`Kombo`, og vælg de "
"relevante :ref:`kombovalg <pos/products/combo-choices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:368
msgid "Add a :guilabel:`Sales Price`."
msgstr "Tilføj en :guilabel:`salgspris`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:369
msgid ""
"Optionally, click the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` tab to select the "
"preferred :guilabel:`Category`."
msgstr ""
"Klik eventuelt på fanen :guilabel:`POS` for at vælge den "
"ønskede :guilabel:`kategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:372
msgid ""
"The total price of the product combo displayed in the :ref:`POS register "
"<pos/use/open-register>` is based on the :guilabel:`Sales Price` defined on "
"the :ref:`product combo's form <pos/products/combo-creation>`. Selecting "
"several products in the combo choices and selecting a product with "
"an :guilabel:`Extra Price` influences the total price."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:378
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Office Combo` has a :guilabel:`Sales Price` of **300** € and "
"offers a selection of chairs and desks. The combo choice for chairs includes "
"a conference chair, an office chair, and an armchair, with a maximum "
"selectable amount set to 2. For each additional chair a customer selects, "
"a :guilabel:`Combo Price` of **35** € is added. The armchair has "
"an :guilabel:`Extra Price` of **100** € because it is made of leather. "
"Selecting both the conference chair and the armchair increases the price of "
"the :guilabel:`Office Combo` to **435** €, i.e., :guilabel:`Sales Price` + "
"**35** € (:guilabel:`Combo Price`) for adding a second chair + **100** € "
"(:guilabel:`Extra Price`) for the leather armchair."
msgstr ""

