"ikonet for at omdøbe :guilabel:`Etageplan`, :icon:`fa-files-o` "
"(:guilabel:`Klon`) ikonet for at oprette en kopi, eller :icon:`fa-trash` "
"(:guilabel:`Slet`) ikonet for at slette den."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:147
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`Table` to add a new table. To edit a "
