#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:166
msgid "Booking"
msgstr "Booking"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:168
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Booking` setting allows for creating and managing "
"reservations for a designated point of sale directly from the POS interface."
msgstr ""
"Nastavení :guilabel:`Rezervace` umožňuje vytvářet a spravovat rezervace pro "
"určené prodejní místo přímo z rozhraní POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:172
msgid ""
"Enabling the :guilabel:`Booking` setting automatically installs "
"the :doc:`Appointments </applications/productivity/appointments>` app."
msgstr ""
"Povolení nastavení :guilabel:`Rezervace` automaticky nainstaluje "
"aplikaci :doc:`Aftaler </applications/productivity/appointments>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:178
msgid "Booking configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurace rezervací"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:180
msgid "To enable and configure the bookings, follow these steps:"
msgstr "For at aktivere og konfigurere bookinger skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:182
msgid ""
"Go to the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`PoS Interface` section, and enable :guilabel:`Booking`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :ref:`POS indstillinger <pos/use/settings>`, rul ned til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`POS grænseflade` og aktiver :guilabel:`Booking`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:184
msgid ""
"Enter a name in the :guilabel:`Appointment type` field and "
"click :guilabel:`Create and edit`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast et navn i feltet :guilabel:`Aftaletype` og klik på :guilabel:`Opret "
"og rediger`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:185
msgid ""
"Configure the :ref:`Appointment type <appointments/configure>` form and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer formularen :ref:`Aftaletype <appointments/configure>` og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:186
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` in the POS settings."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Gem` i POS-indstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:189
msgid ""
"To ensure that only existing resources can be booked for a specific point of "
"sale, set the :guilabel:`Book` field to :guilabel:`Resources` in "
"the :guilabel:`Appointment type` form and select tables. Then, "
"enable :guilabel:`Manage Capacities` to define the maximum amount each "
"resource can handle."
msgstr ""
"For at sikre, at kun eksisterende ressourcer kan bookes til et specifikt "
"salgssted, skal du indstille feltet :guilabel:`Book` "
"til :guilabel:`Ressourcer` i formularen :guilabel:`Aftaletype` og vælge "
"borde. Aktiver derefter :guilabel:`Administrer kapaciteter` for at definere "
"den maksimale mængde, hver ressource kan håndtere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:195
msgid ""
"To accommodate a booking that exceeds the capacity of a single table, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cubes` (:guilabel:`Resources`) icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Appointment Type` form, select a table, and add additional "
"tables in the :guilabel:`Linked Resource` field to merge them."
msgstr ""
"For at imødekomme en booking, der overstiger kapaciteten for et enkelt bord, "
"skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-cubes` (:guilabel:`Ressourcer`) i "
"formularen :guilabel:`Aftaletype`, vælge et bord og tilføje yderligere borde "
"i feltet :guilabel:`Tilknyttet ressource` for at flette dem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:200
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/appointments`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/appointments`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:205
msgid "Booking management"
msgstr "Bookingstyring"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:207
msgid ""
"To manage table bookings from the POS interface, click :guilabel:`Booking`, "
"then:"
msgstr ""
"For at administrere bordreservationer fra POS-brugerfladen skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Booking` og derefter:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:209
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a booking. Add a name, the date and time, "
"number of guests, phone number, duration, and :ref:`resources <appointments/"
"resources>`, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette en booking. Tilføj et navn, dato og "
"tidspunkt, antal gæster, telefonnummer, varighed og :ref:`ressourcer "
"<appointments/resources>`, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:211
msgid ""
"Click a booking to :guilabel:`Edit` or :guilabel:`Delete` it. Click a stage "
"name (e.g., :guilabel:`Booked`, :guilabel:`Checked-In`, or :guilabel:`No "
"Show`) or drag the booking card to move it to the relevant stage."
msgstr ""
"Klik på en booking for at :guilabel:`Rediger` eller :guilabel:`Slet` den. "
"Klik på et stadie-navn (f.eks. :guilabel:`Booket`, :guilabel:`Tjekket ind` "
"eller :guilabel:`Udeblevet`) eller træk bookingkortet for at flytte det til "
"det relevante stadie."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:216
msgid ""
"To quickly edit a booking from the :ref:`Floor plan <pos/restaurant/floors>` "
"view, click the booking notification on the booked table."
msgstr ""
"For hurtigt at redigere en booking fra visningen :ref:`Plantegning <pos/"
"restaurant/floors>` skal du klikke på bookingmeddelelsen på det bookede bord."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:222
msgid "Order management"
msgstr "Ordrestyring"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:224
msgid ""
"The POS register allows for :ref:`processing <pos/restaurant/orders/"
"process>` and :ref:`transferring <pos/restaurant/floors/transfer>` orders, "
"defining :doc:`presets <extra/presets>`, and managing :ref:`courses <pos/"
"restaurant/orders/courses>`."
msgstr ""
"POS-registret giver mulighed for :ref:`behandling <pos/restaurant/orders/"
"process>` og :ref:`overførsel <pos/restaurant/floors/transfer>` af ordrer, "
"definition af :doc:`forudindstillinger <extra/presets>` og administration "
"af :ref:`retter <pos/restaurant/orders/courses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:231
msgid "Order process"
msgstr "Ordreproces"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:233
msgid "To process an order from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr "For at behandle en ordre fra POS-registeret skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:235
msgid "Click products to add them to the cart."
msgstr "Klik på produkter for at tilføje dem til kurven."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:236
msgid "Define how the order is handled:"
msgstr "Definer, hvordan ordren håndteres:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:238
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Set Table` to link the order to a table. Enter a table "
"number and click :guilabel:`Assign`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tildel bord` for at knytte ordren til et bord. Indtast et "
"bordnummer og klik på :guilabel:`Tildel`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:240
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Set Tab` to enter the open order's name and "
"click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Angiv fane` for at indtaste den åbne ordres navn og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Anvend`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:242
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Send` to validate the order."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Send` for at validere ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:243
msgid ""
"When ready, :ref:`process the order payment <pos/restaurant/bills/payment>`."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, :ref:`behandl betalingen for ordren <pos/restaurant/bills/"
"payment>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:246
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Send` redirects to the :ref:`Floor plan <pos/restaurant/"
"floors>` view if :guilabel:`Tables` is selected as the :ref:`default start "
"screen <pos/restaurant/default>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknutím na :guilabel:`Send` dojde k přesměrování do zobrazení :ref:`Floor "
"plan <pos/restaurant/floors>`, pokud je jako :ref:`výchozí úvodní obrazovka "
"<pos/restaurant/default>` vybrána možnost :guilabel:`Tables`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:250
msgid ""
"To cancel an order, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Actions`) "
"icon, then :guilabel:`Cancel Order`. If an :ref:`order printer is configured "
"<pos/restaurant/orders-printing>`, a cancellation ticket is automatically "
"printed for an order sent to the kitchen."
msgstr ""
"For at annullere en ordre skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`Handlinger`) og derefter :guilabel:`Annuller ordre`. Hvis "
"en :ref:`ordreprinter er konfigureret <pos/restaurant/orders-printing>`, "
"udskrives en annulleringsbillet automatisk for en ordre sendt til køkkenet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:254
msgid ""
"After selecting a table in the :ref:`Floor plan <pos/restaurant/floors>` "
"view, click :guilabel:`Release table` in the cart to cancel the table's "
"occupancy. This action is available when the cart is empty."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have valgt et bord i visningen :ref:`Plantegning <pos/restaurant/"
"floors>` skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Frigiv bord` i kurven for at annullere "
"bordets optaget status. Denne handling er tilgængelig, når kurven er tom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:257
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure a printer <pos/restaurant/orders-printing>` to send an order "
"to the kitchen printer when clicking :guilabel:`Order`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurer en printer <pos/restaurant/orders-printing>` for at sende "
"en ordre til køkkensprinteren, når du klikker på :guilabel:`Ordre`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:259
msgid ""
"Use :doc:`presets <extra/presets>` when offering different service types, "
"e.g., :guilabel:`Dine In`, :guilabel:`Takeout`, or :guilabel:`Delivery`."
msgstr ""
"Použijte :doc:`presets <extra/presets>` při nabízení různých typů služeb, "
"např. :guilabel:`Dine In`, :guilabel:`Takeout` nebo :guilabel:`Delivery`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:261
msgid ""
"If the order is a direct sale not linked to any table, its name can be "
"modified by clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Actions`) menu "
"and selecting :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Edit Order Name`."
msgstr ""
"Pokud objednávka není přiřazena k žádnému stolu a jedná se o přímý prodej, "
"lze její název upravit kliknutím na nabídku :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`Akce`) a výběrem :icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Upravit "
"název objednávky`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:266
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:354
msgid ":doc:`extra/preparation`"
msgstr ":doc:`extra/preparation`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:267
msgid ""
":doc:`UrbanPiper order management for food delivery <restaurant/urban_piper>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Správa objednávek UrbanPiper pro rozvoz jídla <restaurant/urban_piper>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:272
msgid "Order transfer"
msgstr "Ordreoverførsel"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:274
msgid ""
"To transfer an order to another table from the :ref:`POS register <pos/"
"restaurant/orders>`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Actions`) "
"icon, then :guilabel:`Transfer/Merge`, and choose the target table in "
"the :ref:`Floor plan <pos/restaurant/floors>` view:"
msgstr ""
"For at overføre en ordre til et andet bord fra :ref:`POS-registeret <pos/"
"restaurant/orders>`, klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`Handlinger`), derefter :guilabel:`Overfør/Flet`, og vælg "
"målbordet i visningen :ref:`Plantegning <pos/restaurant/floors>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:278
msgid "Select an available table to transfer customers and their orders."
msgstr "Vælg et ledigt bord for at overføre kunder og deres ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:279
msgid "Select an occupied table to merge customers and their orders."
msgstr "Vælg et optaget bord for at flette kunder og deres ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:284
msgid "Courses"
msgstr "Retter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:286
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Course` button allows for splitting orders into multiple "
"courses, sending each course to the kitchen sequentially."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Gang` gør det muligt at opdele ordrer i flere gange og "
"sende hver gang til køkkenet sekventielt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:289
msgid ""
"To split an order into courses from the :ref:`register <pos/restaurant/"
"orders>`, click :guilabel:`Course` and add products. Repeat the action as "
"many times as needed, then click :guilabel:`Order` to send the order to the "
"kitchen, which also fires the first course."
msgstr ""
"For at opdele en ordre i gange fra :ref:`registeret <pos/restaurant/"
"orders>`, klik på :guilabel:`Gang` og tilføj produkter. Gentag handlingen så "
"mange gange som nødvendigt, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Bestil` for at "
"sende ordren til køkkenet, hvilket også affyrer den første gang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:293
msgid ""
"When ready for the second course, retrieve the order from the :ref:`Floor "
"plan <pos/restaurant/floors>` view or the :guilabel:`Orders` overview, and "
"click :guilabel:`Fire Course 2`. Repeat the action as many times as needed."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar til den anden gang, hent ordren fra "
"visningen :ref:`Plantegning <pos/restaurant/floors>` eller "
"oversigten :guilabel:`Ordrer`, og klik på :guilabel:`Affyr gang 2`. Gentag "
"handlingen så mange gange som nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:298
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click :guilabel:`Course` as often as needed to display the "
"desired number of courses in the cart. Then, click each course, add "
"products, and click :guilabel:`Order`."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du klikke på :guilabel:`Gang` så ofte som nødvendigt for at "
"vise det ønskede antal gange i kurven. Klik derefter på hver gang, tilføj "
"produkter, og klik på :guilabel:`Bestil`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:300
msgid ""
"To transfer a product or an entire course into another course, select it in "
"the cart, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Actions`) icon, "
"then :icon:`fa-arrow-down` :guilabel:`Transfer course`, and select the "
"preferred course."
msgstr ""
"For at overføre et produkt eller en hel gang til en anden gang skal du vælge "
"det i kurven, klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`Handlinger`), derefter :icon:`fa-arrow-down` :guilabel:`Overfør "
"gang`, og vælge den foretrukne gang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:307
msgid "Order printing"
msgstr "Ordreudskrivning"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:309
msgid ""
"To enable sending orders to a kitchen or a bar printer, :doc:`connect a "
"printer <hardware_network/receipt_printers>` to Odoo, go to the :ref:`POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>`, and follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere afsendelse af ordrer til en køkken- eller barprinter skal "
"du :doc:`forbinde en printer <hardware_network/receipt_printers>` til Odoo, "
"gå til :ref:`POS-indstillingerne <pos/use/settings>` og følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:313
msgid ""
"Scroll down to the :guilabel:`Preparation` section and enable "
"the :guilabel:`Preparation Printers` setting."
msgstr ""
"Rul ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Forberedelse` og aktiver "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Forberedelsesprinters`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:315
msgid ""
"Type the printer's name in the :guilabel:`Printers` field and "
"click :guilabel:`Create and edit`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast printerens navn i feltet :guilabel:`Printere` og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Opret og rediger`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:316
msgid "On the printer setup form, select the :guilabel:`Printer Type`:"
msgstr "På printeropsætningsformularen skal du vælge :guilabel:`Printertype`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:318
msgid ""
"If the printer is connected to an :doc:`IoT system </applications/general/"
"iot>`, select :guilabel:`Use a printer connected to the IoT`, and choose the "
"relevant :doc:`device </applications/general/iot/devices/printer>`. This "
"process requires the IoT app and an IoT system."
msgstr ""
"Hvis printeren er forbundet til et :doc:`IoT-system </applications/general/"
"iot>`, vælg :guilabel:`Brug en printer forbundet til IoT` og vælg den "
"relevante :doc:`enhed </applications/general/iot/devices/printer>`. Denne "
"proces kræver IoT-appen og et IoT-system."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:322
msgid ""
"If using an :doc:`Epson printer that does not require an IoT system "
"connection <hardware_network/receipt_printers>`, select :guilabel:`Use an "
"Epson printer` and enter the :guilabel:`Epson Printer IP Address`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du bruger en :doc:`Epson-printer, der ikke kræver en IoT-"
"systemforbindelse <hardware_network/receipt_printers>`, skal du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Use an Epson printer` og indtaste :guilabel:`Epson Printer "
"IP Address`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:325
msgid ""
"Define the product categories to be printed by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` in the :guilabel:`Printed Product Categories` field and selecting the "
"preferred category from the popover."
msgstr ""
"Definer de produktkategorier, der skal udskrives, ved at klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` i feltet :guilabel:`Udskrevne "
"produktkategorier` og vælge den foretrukne kategori fra popover-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:329
msgid "In the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"I :ref:`POS indstillinger <pos/use/settings>` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:331
msgid ""
"The printer is then connected to the point of sale and can print kitchen "
"orders and order receipts."
msgstr ""
"Printeren er derefter forbundet til POS'en og kan udskrive køkkenordrer og "
"ordrekvitteringer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:334
msgid ""
"Printing kitchen orders requires assigning a :guilabel:`PoS Product "
"Category`."
msgstr ""
"Udskrivning af køkkenordrer kræver tildeling af en :guilabel:`POS-"
"produktkategori`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:335
msgid ""
"To create a :guilabel:`Printed Product Category` on the :guilabel:`Add: "
"Printed Product Categories` popover, click :guilabel:`New`. Enter a name, "
"select a :guilabel:`Parent Category`, choose a :guilabel:`Color`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil` (:guilabel:`Edit`) icon to add an image, determine the "
