"gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Ordrer --> Forberedelsesprintere`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:344
msgid ""
"After :ref:`processing an order <pos/restaurant/orders/process>`, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cutlery` (:guilabel:`order`) icon in the :ref:`POS register "
"<pos/restaurant/orders>` next to :guilabel:`Payment` to reprint a duplicate "
"of the last kitchen order."
msgstr ""
"Efter :ref:`behandling af en ordre <pos/restaurant/orders/process>`, klik på "
