msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Drikkepenge"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:427
msgid ""
"To allow tipping in a POS, go to the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`, "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Payment` section, enable :guilabel:`Tips`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at tillade drikkepenge i en POS skal du gå til :ref:`POS-indstillingerne "
"<pos/use/settings>`, rulle ned til sektionen :guilabel:`Betaling`, "
"aktivere :guilabel:`Drikkepenge` og klikke på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:431
msgid ""
"Depending on your hardware setup and geographical location, enable the "
"following options as relevant:"
msgstr ""
"V závislosti na vašem hardwarovém nastavení a zeměpisné poloze povolte "
"následující možnosti podle potřeby:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:434
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add tip through payment terminal (Adyen)`: Only works with "
"an :doc:`Adyen <payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` card terminal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Přidat spropitné prostřednictvím platebního terminálu (Adyen)`: "
"Funguje pouze s platebním terminálem :doc:`Adyen <payment_methods/terminals/"
"adyen>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:436
msgid ""
":ref:`Add tip after payment <pos/restaurant/tips-after-payment>`: Only works "
"for a POS in the United States of America with an :doc:`Adyen "
"<payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` or a :doc:`Stripe <payment_methods/"
"terminals/stripe>` :ref:`payment terminal <pos/terminals/configuration>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Přidat spropitné po platbě <pos/restaurant/tips-after-payment>`: "
"Funguje pouze pro POS ve Spojených státech amerických s :doc:`Adyen "
"<payment_methods/terminals/adyen>` nebo :doc:`Stripe <payment_methods/"
"terminals/stripe>` :ref:`platebním terminálem <pos/terminals/configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:442
msgid ""
"Saving the :guilabel:`Tips` setting automatically fills the :guilabel:`Tip "
"product` field with the preconfigured :guilabel:`[TIPS] Tips` product, which "
"is only used for tips. When selecting another product in the :guilabel:`Tip "
"product` field, the chosen product is no longer available on the :ref:`POS "
"register <pos/restaurant/orders>`."
msgstr ""
"Gem af indstillingen :guilabel:`Drikkepenge` udfylder automatisk "
"feltet :guilabel:`Drikkepengeprodukt` med det prækonfigurerede "
"produkt :guilabel:`[TIPS] Drikkepenge`, som kun bruges til drikkepenge. Når "
"du vælger et andet produkt i feltet :guilabel:`Drikkepengeprodukt`, er det "
"valgte produkt ikke længere tilgængeligt på :ref:`POS-registeret <pos/"
"restaurant/orders>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant.rst:446
msgid "Choose only one tip product per POS."
msgstr "Vælg kun ét drikkepengeprodukt pr. POS."

