#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:317
msgid "Order rejection"
msgstr "Ordreafvisning"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:319
msgid ""
"Sometimes, the shop or restaurant may want to **reject** an order. In this "
"case, open the orders' list view,"
msgstr ""
"Nogle gange ønsker butikken eller restauranten at **afvise** en ordre. I "
"dette tilfælde skal du åbne listevisningen af ordrer,"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:323
msgid "Click the :guilabel:`Reject` button."
msgstr "Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Afvis`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:324
msgid "Select one of the reasons from the popup window."
msgstr "Vælg en af grundene i pop op-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:None
msgid "Reject order pop-up"
msgstr "Pop op til afvisning af ordre"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:330
msgid ""
"**Swiggy** orders cannot be directly rejected. Attempting to reject one "
"prompts Swiggy customer support to contact the restaurant. Similarly, "
"**Deliveroo**, **JustEat**, and **HungerStation** do not allow order "
"rejection. Always follow the respective provider's guidelines for handling "
"such cases."
msgstr ""
"**Swiggy**-ordrer kan ikke afvises direkte. Forsøg på at afvise en ordre "
"medfører, at Swiggys kundesupport kontakter restauranten. Tilsvarende "
"tillader **Deliveroo**, **JustEat** og **HungerStation** ikke "
"ordreafvisning. Følg altid den respektive udbyders retningslinjer for "
"håndtering af sådanne tilfælde."

