"From the POS register, click the :icon:`oi-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical "
"ellipsis`) icon and :icon:`fa-link` :guilabel:`Quotation/Order` to open the "
"list of quotations and sales orders created from the sales application. When "
