#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:35
msgid ""
"Enter the percentage or fixed amount the customer is paying, and "
"click :guilabel:`Apply` to add the down payment to the cart."
msgstr ""
"Indtast procentsatsen eller det faste beløb, kunden betaler, og klik "
