#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:81
msgid ""
"On the payment screen, set a customer and select :guilabel:`Ship Later`."
msgstr "På betalingsskærmen angiv en kunde og vælg :guilabel:`Send senere`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/shop.rst:82
