msgid "Access the POS settings"
msgstr "Tilgå POS-indstillingerne"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:52
msgid ""
"To access the general POS settings, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Then, open the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` "
"dropdown menu and select the POS to configure."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til de generelle POS-indstillinger skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`POS --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Åbn derefter "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`POS` og vælg den POS, der skal konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:None
msgid "Dropdown menu to select the POS in the app settings"
msgstr "Rullemenu til at vælge POS i app-indstillingerne"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:59
msgid ""
"To configure basic settings, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Dashboard`, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) "
"icon on the relevant POS card, then select :guilabel:`Configure` to perform "
"the following actions:"
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li nakonfigurovat základní nastavení, přejděte "
"na :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Dashboard`, klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) na příslušné kartě POS a poté "
"vyberte :guilabel:`Configure`, abyste provedli následující akce:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:63
msgid ":doc:`Enable multiple employees to log in. <extra/employee_login>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Aktiver flere medarbejdere til at logge ind. <extra/employee_login>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:64
msgid ":doc:`Connect and set up an IoT system. <hardware_network/pos_iot>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Připojte a nastavte systém IoT. <hardware_network/pos_iot>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:65
msgid ":doc:`Connect and set up an ePOS printer. <hardware_network/epos_ssc>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Tilslut og konfigurer en ePOS-printer. <hardware_network/epos_ssc>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:70
msgid "Open the POS register"
msgstr "Åbn POS-kassen"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:72
msgid ""
"The POS register is divided into three sections: the product selector, the "
"cart to visualize the products added to the order, and the numpad for order "
"actions. Once the POS is fully :doc:`configured <hardware_network>`, follow "
"these steps to access the register:"
msgstr ""
"POS-registret er opdelt i tre sektioner: produktvælgeren, kurven til at "
"visualisere produkterne tilføjet til ordren og numerisk tastatur til "
"ordrehandlinger. Når POS er fuldt :doc:`konfigureret <hardware_network>`, "
"skal du følge disse trin for at få adgang til registret:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:76
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Dashboard`."
msgstr "Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:77
msgid "On the relevant POS card, click :guilabel:`Open Register`."
msgstr "På det relevante POS-kort skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Åbn kasse`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:78
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Opening Control` popover, ensure the :guilabel:`Opening "
"cash` amount is correct."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Åbningskontrol` skal du sikre, at beløbet "
"for :guilabel:`Åbne kontanter` er korrekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:80
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Open Register`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Åbn kasse`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:83
msgid ""
"Once the register is open, the :guilabel:`Open Register` button is replaced "
"by the :guilabel:`Continue Selling` button on the :guilabel:`Dashboard's` "
"POS card."
msgstr ""
"Når registret er åbent, erstattes knappen :guilabel:`Åbn register` med "
"knappen :guilabel:`Fortsæt salg` på POS-kortet i :guilabel:`Dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:85
msgid ""
"It is possible to switch between :doc:`multiple users <extra/"
"employee_login>` from an open POS register, provided :ref:`multi-employee "
"management is enabled <pos/employee_login/use>`."
msgstr ""
"Det er muligt at skifte mellem :doc:`flere brugere <extra/employee_login>` "
"fra et åbent POS-register, forudsat at :ref:`administration af flere "
"medarbejdere er aktiveret <pos/employee_login/use>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:88
msgid "From the POS interface header:"
msgstr "Fra POS-interfacets header:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:90
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Register` to access the register for daily POS actions, "
"such as :ref:`sales <pos/use/sell>`, :ref:`refunds <pos/use/refund>`, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Register` for at få adgang til registret til daglige POS-"
"handlinger, såsom :ref:`salg <pos/use/sell>`, :ref:`refusioner <pos/use/"
"refund>` og mere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:92
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Orders` to access the POS :ref:`orders <pos/use/orders>` "
"overview screen and retrieve past or ongoing orders."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Ordrer` for at få adgang til POS-:ref:`ordrer <pos/use/"
"orders>`-oversigtsskærmen og hente tidligere eller igangværende ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:94
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon to put the current "
"order aside and start a new one."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-plus-circle` :guilabel:`(plus)`-ikonet for at lægge den "
"aktuelle ordre til side og starte en ny."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:96
msgid "Click the order numbers to switch between ongoing orders."
msgstr "Klik på ordrenumrene for at skifte mellem igangværende ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:97
msgid "Search for products using the search bar."
msgstr "Søg efter produkter ved hjælp af søgefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:98
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-barcode` (:guilabel:`barcode`) icon to use a webcam as a "
"barcode scanner."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-barcode` (:guilabel:`stregkode`)-ikonet for at bruge et "
"webkamera som stregkodescanner."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:99
msgid ""
"Click the user's avatar to switch between employees, provided :ref:`multi-"
"employee management is enabled <pos/employee_login/use>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på brugerens avatar for at skifte mellem medarbejdere, forudsat "
"at :ref:`administration af flere medarbejdere er aktiveret <pos/"
"employee_login/use>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:101
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon to access more "
"advanced options, as well as to :ref:`close the register <pos/use/register-"
"close>`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`burgermenu`) for at få adgang til "
"mere avancerede indstillinger samt :ref:`lukke registret <pos/use/register-"
"close>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:110
msgid "Sell products"
msgstr "Sælg produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:112
msgid ""
"To sell products in the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-register>`, follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at sælge produkter i :ref:`POS-registret <pos/use/open-register>` skal "
"du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:114
msgid "Click on products to add them to the cart."
msgstr "Klik på produkter for at tilføje dem til kurven."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:116
msgid ""
"To change the quantity, click :guilabel:`Qty`, then enter the number of "
"products using the numpad."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre mængden skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Antal` og derefter "
"indtaste antallet af produkter ved hjælp af det numeriske tastatur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:118
msgid ""
"To add a discount, click :guilabel:`%`, then enter the discount value using "
"the numpad."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en rabat skal du klikke på :guilabel:`%` og derefter indtaste "
"rabatværdien ved hjælp af det numeriske tastatur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:119
msgid ""
"To modify the product price, click :guilabel:`Price`, then enter the new "
"amount using the numpad."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre produktprisen skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Pris` og derefter "
"indtaste det nye beløb ved hjælp af det numeriske tastatur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:121
msgid ""
"Optionally, add a :ref:`customer <pos/use/customers>` or a :ref:`note <pos/"
"use/notes>` to the order."
msgstr ""
"Du kan eventuelt tilføje en :ref:`kunde <pos/use/customers>` eller "
"en :ref:`note <pos/use/notes>` til ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:123
msgid ""
"Once the order is complete, click :guilabel:`Payment` to proceed to the "
"payment screen."
msgstr ""
"Når ordren er fuldført, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Betaling` for at gå "
"videre til betalingsskærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:124
msgid ""
"Select the :doc:`payment method <payment_methods>`, then enter the amount, "
"if needed."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :doc:`betalingsmetoden <payment_methods>`, og indtast derefter beløbet, "
"hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:127
msgid ""
"Once payment is successful, the :doc:`receipt <use/receipts>` can be printed "
"or sent to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Når betalingen er gennemført, kan :doc:`kvitteringen <use/receipts>` "
"udskrives eller sendes til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:130
msgid ""
"To move on to the next order, click :guilabel:`New Order` on the receipt "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"For at gå videre til næste ordre skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Ny ordre` på "
"kvitteringsskærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:133
msgid ":doc:`Issue invoices for registered customers <use/pos_invoices>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Udsted fakturaer til registrerede kunder <use/pos_invoices>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:138
msgid "Register and assign customers"
msgstr "Registrere og tildele kunder"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:140
msgid ""
"Registering customers is necessary to :ref:`collect their loyalty points and "
"grant them rewards <pos/pricing/loyalty>`, automatically apply "
"an :ref:`attributed pricelist <pos/pricing/pricelists>`, or :doc:`generate "
"and print invoices <use/pos_invoices>`."
msgstr ""
"Registrering af kunder er nødvendig for at :ref:`indsamle deres "
"loyalitetspoint og give dem belønninger <pos/pricing/loyalty>`, automatisk "
"anvende en :ref:`tildelt prisliste <pos/pricing/pricelists>` "
"eller :doc:`generere og udskrive fakturaer <use/pos_invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:144
msgid ""
"To create customers from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-register>`:"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette kunder fra :ref:`POS-registret <pos/use/open-register>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:146
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Customer`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Kunde`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:148
msgid "Enter the customer's details, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Indtast kundens oplysninger og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:150
msgid "To create customers from the backend:"
msgstr "Sådan opretter du kunder fra backend:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:152
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Customers`."
msgstr "Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Ordrer --> Kunder`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:153
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:154
msgid "Enter the customer's details and save."
msgstr "Indtast kundens oplysninger og gem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:156
msgid ""
"To assign a customer to an order in the POS register or on the payment "
"screen, click :guilabel:`Customer` and select the desired customer. To "
"select a different customer, click the current customer's name on the "
"numpad, then select another one."
msgstr ""
"For at tildele en kunde til en ordre i POS-registret eller på "
"betalingsskærmen skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Kunde` og vælge den ønskede "
"kunde. For at vælge en anden kunde skal du klikke på den aktuelle kundes "
"navn på nummertastaturet og derefter vælge en anden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:161
msgid ""
"To edit the customer's details, click the customer's name on the numpad, "
"click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon next to the "
"relevant customer, then select :guilabel:`Edit Details`."
msgstr ""
"For at redigere kundens oplysninger skal du klikke på kundens navn på "
"nummertastaturet, klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-bars` "
"(:guilabel:`hamburgermenu`) ved siden af den relevante kunde og derefter "
"vælge :guilabel:`Rediger oplysninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:166
msgid ""
"Creating a new customer in the POS register or on the payment screen "
"automatically assigns them to the current order upon saving."
msgstr ""
"Oprettelse af en ny kunde i POS-registret eller på betalingsskærmen tildeler "
"automatisk kunden til den aktuelle ordre ved lagring."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:170
msgid "Send marketing messages"
msgstr "Send marketingbeskeder"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:172
msgid ""
"Customers' contact details, such as phone numbers or email addresses, are "
"automatically stored when :doc:`receipts <use/receipts>` are sent via email, "
"SMS, or WhatsApp. They can then be used, for example, for marketing purposes."
msgstr ""
"Kunders kontaktoplysninger, såsom telefonnumre eller e-mailadresser, gemmes "
"automatisk, når :doc:`kvitteringer <use/receipts>` sendes via e-mail, SMS "
"eller WhatsApp. De kan derefter bruges f.eks. til marketingformål."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:176
msgid ""
"To send marketing messages manually from the POS backend, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at sende marketingbeskeder manuelt fra POS-backend skal du følge disse "
"trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:178
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:101
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:124
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`."
msgstr "Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Ordrer --> Ordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:179
msgid "Click a POS order and open the :guilabel:`Extra Info` tab."
msgstr "Klik på en POS-ordre og åbn fanen :guilabel:`Ekstra information`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:180
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contact Info` category, click the :icon:`fa-envelope` "
"(:guilabel:`email`) icon or the :icon:`fa-whatsapp` (:guilabel:`WhatsApp`) "
"icon next to the completed :guilabel:`Email` or :guilabel:`Mobile` field."
msgstr ""
"Under kategorien :guilabel:`Kontaktoplysninger` skal du klikke på "
"ikonet :icon:`fa-envelope` (:guilabel:`e-mail`) eller ikonet :icon:`fa-"
"whatsapp` (:guilabel:`WhatsApp`) ved siden af det udfyldte felt :guilabel:`E-"
"mail` eller :guilabel:`Mobil`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:185
msgid ""
"Make sure a customer is assigned to the order to send marketing messages "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at en kunde er tildelt ordren for at sende marketingbeskeder "
"manuelt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:188
msgid ":doc:`../../marketing/email_marketing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../marketing/email_marketing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:189
msgid ":doc:`../../marketing/sms_marketing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../marketing/sms_marketing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:190
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/whatsapp`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/whatsapp`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:195
msgid "Access the orders overview"
msgstr "Få adgang til ordreoversigten"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:197
msgid ""
"The orders overview allows for viewing, searching, and retrieving orders "
"from the POS interface. To access it, click :guilabel:`Orders` in the POS "
"interface header."
msgstr ""
"Ordreoversigten gør det muligt at se, søge og hente ordrer fra POS-"
"grænsefladen. For at få adgang til den skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Ordrer` "
"i POS-grænsefladeheaderen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:200
msgid ""
"To filter orders based on their status, click the :guilabel:`Active` "
"dropdown menu and select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil filtrere ordrer baseret på deres status, skal du klikke på "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Aktiv` og vælge en af følgende muligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active`: Orders currently in progress. This includes orders "
"marked as :guilabel:`Ongoing`, as well as those in the :guilabel:`Payment` "
"or the :guilabel:`Receipt` stages (i.e., orders for which the receipt has "
"been emailed to the customer)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aktiv`: Ordrer, der er i gang. Dette inkluderer ordrer markeret "
"som :guilabel:`Igangværende`, samt dem i faserne :guilabel:`Betaling` "
"eller :guilabel:`Kvittering` (dvs. ordrer, hvor kvitteringen er sendt til "
"kunden via e-mail)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:206
msgid ":guilabel:`Paid`: Paid orders."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Betalt`: Betalte ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:207
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancelled`: Orders cancelled on online platforms "
"through :ref:`UrbanPiper <pos/urban_piper/configuration>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Annulleret`: Ordrer annulleret på onlineplatforme "
"gennem :ref:`UrbanPiper <pos/urban_piper/configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:210
msgid ""
"It is also possible to search for orders based on, for example, "
"the :guilabel:`Receipt Number`, :guilabel:`Date`, or :guilabel:`Customer`."
msgstr ""
"Det er også muligt at søge efter ordrer baseret på "
"f.eks. :guilabel:`Kvitteringsnummer`, :guilabel:`Dato` "
"eller :guilabel:`Kunde`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:213
msgid ""
"To navigate between pages, click the :icon:`fa-caret-left` or :icon:`fa-"
"caret-right` (:guilabel:`caret`) icon."
msgstr ""
"For at navigere mellem sider skal du klikke på :icon:`fa-caret-left` "
"eller :icon:`fa-caret-right` (:guilabel:`caret`) ikonet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:216
msgid ""
"To access an order in the register, click it, then click :guilabel:`Load "
"Order`."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til en ordre i kasseapparatet skal du klikke på den og "
"derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Indlæs ordre`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:219
msgid ":guilabel:`Paid` orders can be :ref:`refunded <pos/use/refund>`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Betalte` ordrer kan :ref:`refunderes <pos/use/refund>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:222
msgid ""
"To define the number of orders visible on a page, click `1-x / x`. Enter a "
"number lower than the total number of pages, and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"For at definere antallet af ordrer, der er synlige på en side, skal du "
"klikke på `1-x / x`. Indtast et tal, der er lavere end det samlede antal "
"sider, og klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:224
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`) icon next to "
"an :guilabel:`Active` order to delete it."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`papirkurv`) ikonet ved siden af "
"en :guilabel:`Aktiv` ordre for at slette den."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:226
msgid ""
"If using :doc:`presets <extra/presets>`, click one to view the related "
"orders. Click it again to return to the main overview."
msgstr ""
"Pokud používáte :doc:`presets <extra/presets>`, klikněte na jeden z nich pro "
"zobrazení souvisejících objednávek. Opětovným kliknutím se vrátíte do "
"hlavního přehledu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:232
msgid "Return and refund products"
msgstr "Returner og refunder produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:234
msgid ""
"The steps to process a refund from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-"
"register>` depend on whether the refund is :ref:`based on an order <pos/use/"
"refund-order-based>` or processed as a :ref:`standalone refund that is not "
"based on an order <pos/use/refund-standalone>`."
msgstr ""
"Trinene til at behandle en refusion fra :ref:`POS-registret <pos/use/open-"
"register>` afhænger af, om refusionen er :ref:`baseret på en ordre <pos/use/"
"refund-order-based>` eller behandles som en :ref:`selvstændig refusion, der "
"ikke er baseret på en ordre <pos/use/refund-standalone>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:238
msgid ""
"In both cases, the amount can be refunded or a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/"
"loyalty>` issued for the refunded amount."
msgstr ""
"I begge tilfælde kan beløbet refunderes, eller der kan udstedes "
"et :ref:`gavekort <pos/pricing/loyalty>` for det refunderede beløb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once the return is validated, a corresponding credit note is generated, "
"referencing the original :doc:`receipt <use/receipts>` or :doc:`invoice <use/"
"pos_invoices>`."
msgstr ""
"Når returneringen er valideret, genereres en tilsvarende kreditnota, der "
"refererer til den oprindelige :doc:`kvittering <use/receipts>` "
"eller :doc:`faktura <use/pos_invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:246
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:251
msgid "Order-based refunds"
msgstr "Ordrebaserede refusioner"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:253
msgid "To process a refund based on an order, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en refusion baseret på en ordre skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:255
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon in the "
"POS register."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v`-ikonet (:guilabel:`lodret ellipse`) i POS-"
"kasseapparatet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:256
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Refund`. The orders overview opens, displaying "
"all :guilabel:`Paid` orders."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Refunder`. Ordreoversigten åbnes og viser "
"alle :guilabel:`Betalte` ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:257
msgid ""
"Select the product(s) to refund, and then enter the quantity to refund if "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Vælg produktet/produkterne, der skal refunderes, og indtast derefter "
"antallet, der skal refunderes, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:258
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Refund` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Refunder` for at åbne betalingsskærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:287
msgid "Choose how to handle the refund:"
msgstr "Vælg, hvordan kreditten skal håndteres:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:261
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:289
msgid ""
"To refund the customer, on the payment screen, select a payment method, then "
"click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"For at refundere kunden skal du på betalingsskærmen vælge en betalingsmetode "
"og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Valider`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:263
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:291
msgid ""
"To issue a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/loyalty>` for the refund amount, on "
"the payment screen, click :guilabel:`Back`. The cart displays the returned "
"product(s) with a negative quantity. Then, add the gift card from the "
"product selector to the order; its value is automatically set to match the "
"total refund amount. Click :guilabel:`Payment`, then :guilabel:`Validate` "
"the refund."
msgstr ""
"For at udstede et :ref:`gavekort <pos/pricing/loyalty>` for refusionsbeløbet "
"skal du på betalingsskærmen klikke på :guilabel:`Tilbage`. Indkøbskurven "
"viser det/de returnerede produkt(er) med et negativt antal. Tilføj derefter "
"gavekortet fra produktvælgeren til ordren; dets værdi indstilles automatisk "
"til at matche det samlede refusionsbeløb. Klik på :guilabel:`Betaling` og "
"derefter :guilabel:`Valider` refusionen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:270
msgid ""
"Alternatively, access the list of paid orders by clicking :guilabel:`Orders` "
"in the POS interface header and selecting :guilabel:`Paid` from "
"the :guilabel:`Active` dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
"Alternativt kan du få adgang til listen over betalte ordrer ved at klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ordrer` i POS-interfacets header og vælge :guilabel:`Betalt` "
"fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Aktiv`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:272
msgid ""
"Refunds can also be initiated and processed from the backend. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`, select an order, "
"then click :guilabel:`Return Products`. Note that this method can only be "
"used to refund the entire order."
msgstr ""
"Refusioner kan også initieres og behandles fra backend. For at gøre dette "
"skal du gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Ordrer --> Ordrer`, vælge en ordre og "
"derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Returner produkter`. Bemærk, at denne metode "
"kun kan bruges til at refundere hele ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:279
msgid "Standalone refunds"
msgstr "Selvstændige refusioner"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:281
msgid ""
"To process a standalone refund that is *not* based on an order, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at behandle en selvstændig refusion, der *ikke* er baseret på en ordre, "
"skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:283
msgid "Select the relevant product from the POS register."
msgstr "Vælg det relevante produkt fra POS-kasseapparatet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:284
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Qty` to enter the quantity to refund, then "
"click :guilabel:`+/-` to set it as a negative quantity."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Antal` for at indtaste antallet, der skal refunderes, og "
"klik derefter på :guilabel:`+/-` for at indstille det som et negativt antal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:286
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Payment` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Betaling` for at åbne betalingsskærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:298
msgid ""
"To facilitate management of standalone returns, create a :doc:`preset <extra/"
"presets>` with only the :guilabel:`Return mode` enabled. When this preset is "
"selected from the POS register, the quantity of any item added to the cart "
"is set to negative."
msgstr ""
"For at lette håndteringen af selvstændige returneringer skal du oprette "
"en :doc:`forudindstilling <extra/presets>` med kun :guilabel:`Returtilstand` "
"aktiveret. Når denne forudindstilling vælges fra POS-kasseapparatet, "
"indstilles antallet af enhver vare, der tilføjes til indkøbskurven, til "
"negativt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:305
msgid "Add and manage notes"
msgstr "Tilføj og administrer noter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:307
msgid ""
"Notes allow for extra information to be added to specific products in an "
"order. There are two types of notes: :ref:`internal notes <pos/use/internal-"
"notes>` and :ref:`customer notes <pos/use/customer-notes>`."
msgstr ""
"Noter gør det muligt at tilføje ekstra information til specifikke produkter "
"i en ordre. Der er to typer noter: :ref:`interne noter <pos/use/internal-"
"notes>` og :ref:`kundenoter <pos/use/customer-notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:312
msgid ""
"If the same content is frequently used, configure a note model to save time. "
"To create or edit note models, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Note Models`, click :guilabel:`New` or click the relevant "
"note model, then complete or edit the :guilabel:`Name` column."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det samme indhold bruges ofte, skal du konfigurere en notemodel for at "
"spare tid. For at oprette eller redigere notemodeller skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`POS --> Konfiguration --> Notemodeller`, klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` eller klikke på den relevante notemodel og derefter "
"udfylde eller redigere kolonnen :guilabel:`Navn`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:318
msgid ""
"Any customer notes added to a product from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/"
"open-register>` are displayed on the :doc:`customer display <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."
msgstr ""
"Eventuelle kundenoter, der tilføjes til et produkt fra :ref:`POS-"
"kasseapparatet <pos/use/open-register>`, vises på :doc:`kundedisplayet <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:324
msgid "Internal notes"
msgstr "Interne noter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:326
msgid ""
"Internal notes provide information intended for staff (e.g., `no tomato` for "
"the kitchen team) and do not appear on the customer's receipt."
msgstr ""
"Interne noter giver information beregnet til personalet (f.eks. `ingen "
"tomat` til køkkenteamet) og vises ikke på kundens kvittering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:329
msgid ""
"To add or edit an internal note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje eller redigere en intern note fra POS-kasseapparatet skal du "
"følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:331
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:349
msgid "If the note applies to:"
msgstr "Hvis notatet gælder for:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:333
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, then "
"click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr ""
"Hele ordren: Sørg for, at ingen vare er valgt i kurven, og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:334
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, then click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr ""
"En specifik vare: Vælg varen i kurven, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:335
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:355
msgid ""
"Add or modify the note's content in the popover or select a previously "
"configured note model."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj eller rediger notatets indhold i pop op-vinduet, eller vælg en "
"tidligere konfigureret notatskabelon."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:336
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:356
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Anvend`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:341
msgid "Customer notes"
msgstr "Kundenoter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:343
msgid ""
"Customer notes appear on :doc:`receipts <use/receipts>` and :doc:`invoices "
"<use/pos_invoices>`. They can be used, for example, to provide warranty "
"details for a high-value item or specific care instructions, such as `Dry "
"clean only`."
msgstr ""
"Kundenotater vises på :doc:`kvitteringer <use/receipts>` og :doc:`fakturaer "
"<use/pos_invoices>`. De kan for eksempel bruges til at give "
"garantioplysninger for en vare af høj værdi eller specifikke "
"plejeinstruktioner, såsom `Renses kun kemisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:347
msgid ""
"To add or edit a customer note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje eller redigere en kundenote fra POS-registret skal du følge "
"disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:351
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Customer Note`."
msgstr ""
"Hele ordren: Sørg for, at ingen vare er valgt i kurven, klik på :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`lodret ellipse`) ikonet, og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Kundenote`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:353
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then click :guilabel:`Customer "
"Note`."
msgstr ""
"En specifik vare: Vælg varen i kurven, klik på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`lodret ellipse`) ikonet, og klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Kundenote`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:359
msgid ""
"Product notes from :ref:`imported sales orders <pos/shop/so>` are displayed "
"in the same way as customer notes."
msgstr ""
"Produktnotater fra :ref:`importerede salgsordrer <pos/shop/so>` vises på "
"samme måde som kundenotater."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer note button and notes (SO and POS register) on products in the cart"
msgstr "Kundenoteknap og noter (SO og POS-kasseapparat) på produkter i kurven"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:368
msgid "Manage the cash register"
msgstr "Håndter kasseapparatet"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:370
msgid ""
"Odoo POS allows accepted coins and bills to be defined. To set up the "
"allowed coins and bills:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo POS giver mulighed for at definere accepterede mønter og sedler. For at "
"konfigurere de tilladte mønter og sedler:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:372
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Coins/Bills`."
msgstr "Gå til :menuselection:`POS --> Konfiguration --> Mønter/sedler`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:373
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` to add a new value."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at tilføje en ny værdi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:374
msgid ""
"Select the POS where this value is accepted in the :guilabel:`Point of "
"Sales` column, or leave the field empty to make it available for all POS."
msgstr ""
"Vælg den POS, hvor denne værdi er accepteret, i kolonnen :guilabel:`Point of "
"Sales`, eller lad feltet være tomt for at gøre den tilgængelig for alle POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:377
msgid ""
"To record a cash-in or cash-out transaction not associated with a sale from "
"the POS register:"
msgstr ""
"For at registrere en indbetaling eller udbetaling, der ikke er knyttet til "
"et salg, fra POS-registret:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:379
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon on the POS "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger-menu`) ikonet på POS-"
"grænsefladen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:380
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Cash In/Out`."
msgstr "Klik på :guilabel:`Indbetal/hæv`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:381
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Cash In` or :guilabel:`Cash Out` in the popover."
msgstr ""
"Vælg :guilabel:`Indbetaling` eller :guilabel:`Udbetaling` i pop op-vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:382
msgid "Enter the amount in the field with the currency symbol."
msgstr "Indtast beløbet i feltet med valutasymbolet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:383
msgid ""
"Specify the reason for the addition or removal of cash, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Angiv årsagen til tilføjelsen eller fjernelsen af kontanter, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:386
msgid ""
"Only employees with :ref:`basic or advanced access rights <pos/"
"employee_login/configuration>` are allowed to perform cash-in/out actions."
msgstr ""
"Kun medarbejdere med :ref:`grundlæggende eller avancerede adgangsrettigheder "
"<pos/employee_login/configuration>` har tilladelse til at udføre indbetaling/"
"udbetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:392
msgid "Close the POS register"
msgstr "Luk POS-kassens session"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:394
msgid ""
"To close the POS register, click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger "
"menu`) icon, then :guilabel:`Close Register`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på ikonet :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`burgermenu`) og derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Luk kasse` for at lukke POS-kassen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:397
msgid "The :guilabel:`Closing Register` popover displays:"
msgstr "Pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Luk kasse` viser:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:399
msgid "The number of orders and the total amount made during the session."
msgstr "Antallet af ordrer og det samlede beløb i sessionen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:400
msgid "The expected amounts grouped by payment method."
msgstr "De forventede beløb grupperet efter betalingsmetode."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:402
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-money` (:guilabel:`money`) icon to specify the number of "
"coins and bills, then click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-money` (:guilabel:`penge`) ikonet for at angive antallet "
"af mønter og sedler, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Bekræft`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:405
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Close Register` to close the register and post accounting "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Luk kasse` for at lukke kassen og bogføre regnskabsposter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:408
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`clone`) icon to automatically fill in "
"the field with the expected cash amount."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`klon`) ikonet for automatisk at udfylde "
"feltet med det forventede kontantbeløb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:412
msgid ""
"After specifying the number of coins and bills, the computed amount is set "
"in the :guilabel:`Cash Count` field, and the :guilabel:`Closing details` are "
"specified in the :guilabel:`Closing note` section."
msgstr ""
"Efter angivelse af antallet af mønter og sedler indstilles det beregnede "
"beløb i feltet :guilabel:`Cash Count`, og :guilabel:`Closing details` "
"specificeres i sektionen :guilabel:`Closing note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:415
msgid ""
"Closing the register of a :doc:`restaurant <restaurant>` POS when orders are "
"still in draft and not scheduled for later is not allowed and opens a "
"popover with options to :guilabel:`Review Orders` or :guilabel:`Cancel "
"Orders`."
msgstr ""
"Lukning af registret for et :doc:`restaurant <restaurant>` POS, når ordrer "
"stadig er i kladde og ikke er planlagt til senere, er ikke tilladt og åbner "
"en popover med muligheder for at :guilabel:`Review Orders` "
"eller :guilabel:`Cancel Orders`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:418
msgid ""
"It is strongly advised to close the POS register at the end of each day."
msgstr "Det anbefales stærkt at lukke POS-kassen ved slutningen af hver dag."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:421
msgid "Set maximum difference"
msgstr "Indstil maksimal difference"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:423
msgid ""
"When the counted money does **not** match the expected amount, "
"a :guilabel:`Payments Difference` window appears, prompting you to "
"acknowledge the discrepancy. Click :guilabel:`Proceed Anyway` to accept the "
"difference and post it to the designated cash difference journal."
msgstr ""
"Når de talte penge **ikke** matcher det forventede beløb, vises "
"et :guilabel:`Payments Difference` vindue, der beder dig om at anerkende "
"uoverensstemmelsen. Klik på :guilabel:`Proceed Anyway` for at acceptere "
"differencen og bogføre den til den udpegede kassedifferencejournal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:427
msgid ""
"To restrict this behavior, you can prevent users from closing the register "
"when a discrepancy occurs by enabling the :guilabel:`Set Maximum Difference` "
"setting in the :guilabel:`Payment` section of the :ref:`POS settings <pos/"
"use/settings>`. Then, specify the allowed limit in the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"Difference` field."
msgstr ""
"For at begrænse denne adfærd kan du forhindre brugere i at lukke registret, "
"når der opstår en uoverensstemmelse, ved at aktivere "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Set Maximum Difference` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Payment` i :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>`. "
"Angiv derefter den tilladte grænse i feltet :guilabel:`Authorized "
"Difference`."

