msgid ""
"Open the dropdown selection menu next to the search bar, and set the filter "
"to :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"Otevřete rozbalovací nabídku vedle vyhledávacího pole a nastavte filtr "
"na :guilabel:`Zaplaceno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/receipts.rst:58
msgid ""
"Select the desired order and click :icon:`fa-print` :guilabel:`Print "
"Receipt`."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte požadovanou objednávku a klikněte na :icon:`fa-"
"print` :guilabel:`Vytisknout účtenku`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/receipts.rst:61
msgid ""
"Filter the list of orders using the search bar: type in your reference and "
"select :guilabel:`Receipt Number`, :guilabel:`Date`, or :guilabel:`Customer`."
msgstr ""
"Filtrer listen over ordrer ved hjælp af søgefeltet: indtast din reference og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Kvitteringsnummer`, :guilabel:`Dato` eller :guilabel:`Kunde`."

