#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:61
msgid ""
"To view all products that can be rented in the database, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Rentals app --> Products`. By default, "
"the :guilabel:`Rental` filter appears in the search bar, and the view is "
"Kanban. Remove the filter, then click the search bar. From the preset "
"filters, select :guilabel:`Services`. All the configured services appear."
msgstr ""
"For at se alle produkter, der kan lejes i databasen, skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Leje-app --> Produkter`. Som standard vises "
"filteret :guilabel:`Leje` i søgelinjen, og visningen er Kanban. Fjern "
"filteret, og klik derefter på søgelinjen. Vælg :guilabel:`Tjenester` fra de "
"forudindstillede filtre. Alle de konfigurerede tjenester vises."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:66
