#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:46
msgid ""
"Select a down payment option and set the desired payment, either as a "
"percentage or a fixed amount, in the :guilabel:`Down Payment Amount` field."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte možnost zálohy a nastavte požadovanou platbu buď jako procento, nebo "
"pevnou částku v poli :guilabel:`Částka zálohy`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:49
msgid ""
"Once all fields are filled in, click the :guilabel:`Create Draft` button. "
"Upon clicking this button, Odoo reveals the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Når alle felter er udfyldt, klik på knappen :guilabel:`Opret udkast`. Ved at "
"klikke på denne knap viser Odoo :guilabel:`Udkast til kundefaktura`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:53
msgid ""
"If an :guilabel:`Invalid Operation` error appears, double-check that "
"the :doc:`invoicing policy <invoicing_policy>` is configured correctly. In "
"some cases, for example, the invoicing policy is configured to require "
"delivery before sending an invoice."
msgstr ""
"Pokud se zobrazí chyba :guilabel:`Neplatná operace`, znovu zkontrolujte, zda "
"je :doc:`pravidlo fakturace <invoicing_policy>` správně nakonfigurováno. V "
"některých případech je například pravidlo fakturace nakonfigurováno tak, aby "
"před odesláním faktury vyžadovalo dodání."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab of the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft`, the down payment that was configured in the *Create invoice(s)* pop-"
"up form appears under a new :guilabel:`Down Payments` section."
msgstr ""
"Under fanen :guilabel:`Fakturalinjer` i :guilabel:`Kundefakturakladde` vises "
"den forudbetaling, der blev konfigureret i *Opret faktura(er)* pop op-"
"formularen, under et nyt afsnit :guilabel:`Forudbetalinger`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:64
msgid "Types of down payments"
msgstr "Typer af forudbetalinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:66
msgid ""
"Odoo offers both fixed amounts and partial down payments (such as 30% of an "
"order's total)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tilbyder både faste beløb og delvise forudbetalinger (såsom 30% af en "
"ordres total)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:68
msgid ""
"A 100% down payment is possible and differs from a full payment of the sales "
"order. A sales order paid through the regular invoice process does not allow "
"any additional invoices to be generated and does not display "
"the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button on the sales order."
msgstr ""
"En 100% forudbetaling er mulig og adskiller sig fra en fuld betaling af "
"salgsordren. En salgsordre betalt gennem den normale fakturaproces tillader "
"ikke, at der genereres yderligere fakturaer, og viser ikke knappen "
":guilabel:`Opret faktura` på salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:72
msgid ""
"With a 100% down payment, the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button is still "
"displayed on the sales Order because the system expects another invoice to "
"be created after the down payment to complete payment of the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Med en 100% forudbetaling vises knappen :guilabel:`Opret faktura` stadig på "
"salgsordren, fordi systemet forventer, at der oprettes endnu en faktura "
"efter forudbetalingen for at fuldføre betalingen af salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:76
msgid "The following are two examples of down payment amounts:"
msgstr "Følgende er to eksempler på forudbetalingsbeløb:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Example 1: 50% down payment <sales/invoicing/50-percent-down-payments>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Eksempel 1: 50% forudbetaling <sales/invoicing/50-percent-down-"
"payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:79
msgid ""
":ref:`Example 2: 100% down payment <sales/invoicing/100-percent-down-"
"payments>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Eksempel 2: 100% forudbetaling <sales/invoicing/100-percent-down-"
"payments>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:84
msgid "Example 1: 50% down payment"
msgstr "Eksempel 1: 50% forudbetaling"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:87
msgid ""
"This flow is also possible with the :guilabel:`Down payment (fixed amount)` "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Dette flow er også muligt med muligheden :guilabel:`Forudbetaling (fast "
"beløb)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:89
msgid ""
"A customer is buying a luxury cabinet from a furniture store. The furniture "
"store has configured the cabinet with an *Invoicing Policy* of *Ordered "
"quantities*. The store requires a 50% down payment on all of its furniture "
"products."
msgstr ""
"En kunde køber et luksuskabinet fra en møbelforretning. Møbelforretningen "
"har konfigureret kabinettet med en *Faktureringspolitik* som *Bestilte "
"mængder*. Forretningen kræver en 50% forudbetaling på alle sine "
"møbelprodukter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:93
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`, and :ref:`create a quotation "
"<sales/create-quotation>` for the cabinet. Once the order is confirmed (via "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button), the quotation turns into a sales order. "
"Create an invoice by clicking :guilabel:`Create Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger til :menuselection:`Salg app --> Ny`, og :ref:`opret et tilbud "
"<sales/create-quotation>` for kabinettet. Når ordren er bekræftet (via "
"knappen :guilabel:`Bekræft`), bliver tilbuddet til en salgsordre. Opret en "
"faktura ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Opret faktura`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"Cabinet with doors sales order that's been confirmed in the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Salgsordre for skab med døre, der er blevet bekræftet i Odoo Salg-"
"applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:101
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, "
"select :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, and type `50` in "
"the :guilabel:`Down Payment` field."
msgstr ""
"I :guilabel:`Opret faktura(er)` pop op-vinduet, der vises, skal du vælge "
":guilabel:`Forudbetaling (procent)` og indtaste `50` i feltet "
":guilabel:`Forudbetaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:105
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Income Account` attached to the :guilabel:`Down payment` can "
"be changed. For more information, check out the documentation "
"on :ref:`income account modification on down payments <sales/invoicing/"
"income-account-modification>`. A :guilabel:`Down payment Account` can also "
"be set on a product category. If set, this account is prioritized for future "
"down payments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Indtægtskontoen`, der er knyttet til :guilabel:`Udbetalingen`, "
"kan ændres. For mere information, se dokumentationen om :ref:`ændring af "
"indtægtskonto ved udbetalinger <sales/invoicing/income-account-"
"modification>`. En :guilabel:`Udbetalingskonto` kan også indstilles på en "
"produktkategori. Hvis den er indstillet, prioriteres denne konto til "
"fremtidige udbetalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:110
msgid ""
"Lastly, click :guilabel:`Create Draft` to create and view the invoice draft, "
"which includes the down payment under the :guilabel:`Down Payments` section "
"of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. Click :guilabel:`Confirm` and the "
"invoice's status changes from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`. It "
"also reveals a new series of buttons at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Nakonec klikněte na :guilabel:`Vytvořit kladde` pro vytvoření a zobrazení "
"návrhu faktury, který zahrnuje zálohu v sekci :guilabel:`Zálohy` na kartě "
":guilabel:`Řádky faktury`. Klikněte na :guilabel:`Potvrdit` a stav faktury "
"se změní z :guilabel:`Kladde` na :guilabel:`Zaúčtováno`. Zobrazí se také "
"nová řada tlačítek v horní části stránky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "A sample draft invoice with down payment mentioned in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Et eksempel på en fakturaudkast med acontobetaling nævnt i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:118
msgid ""
"To begin the payment process, click :guilabel:`Pay`. A :guilabel:`Pay` pop-"
"up form displays with auto-populated information. Confirm the information "
"provided is correct and make any necessary adjustments. When ready, click "
"the :guilabel:`Create Payment` button."
msgstr ""
"Pro zahájení platebního procesu klikněte na :guilabel:`Zaplatit`. Zobrazí se "
"formulář :guilabel:`Zaplatit` s automaticky vyplněnými informacemi. "
"Zkontrolujte, zda jsou poskytnuté informace správné, a proveďte případné "
"úpravy. Až budete připraveni, klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Vytvořit "
"platbu`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "Showcase of the Pay pop-up window with create payment button."
msgstr "Visning af Betal pop op-vinduet med knappen opret betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:125
msgid ""
"The customer invoice changes status with a green :guilabel:`In Payment` "
"or :guilabel:`Paid` banner in the upper-right corner, depending on how the "
"database is configured and if manual confirmation of payments is required."
msgstr ""
"Zákaznická faktura změní stav s zeleným nápisem :guilabel:`V platbě` nebo "
":guilabel:`Zaplaceno` v pravém horním rohu, v závislosti na konfiguraci "
"database a na tom, zda je vyžadováno manuální potvrzení plateb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer Invoice with a green Paid banner located in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Kundefaktura med et grønt Betalt banner placeret i øverste højre hjørne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:132
msgid ""
"On the sales order, a new :guilabel:`Down Payments` section is present in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, along with the down payment that was just "
"invoiced and posted. When the customer wants to pay the remaining amount of "
"the order, another invoice must be created."
msgstr ""
"På salgsordren er der en ny sektion :guilabel:`Udbetalinger` til stede på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`, sammen med den udbetaling, der lige blev "
"faktureret og bogført. Når kunden ønsker at betale det resterende beløb af "
"ordren, skal der oprettes endnu en faktura."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The down payments section in the order lines tab of a sales order."
msgstr "Afsnittet om acontobetalinger under fanen ordrelinjer i en salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:139
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button. On the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoice(s)` pop-up window, there is a new field: :guilabel:`Already "
"invoiced` and :guilabel:`Amount to invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Vytvořit fakturu`. V pop-up okně "
":guilabel:`Vytvořit fakturu(y)` se zobrazí nová pole: :guilabel:`Již "
"fakturováno` a :guilabel:`Částka k fakturaci`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The deduct down payment option on the Create invoice(s) pop up in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Muligheden for at fratrække udbetaling i pop op-vinduet Opret faktura(er) i "
"Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:145
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` option. Odoo creates an invoice for "
"the exact amount needed to complete the total payment, as shown in "
"the :guilabel:`Amount to invoice` field."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte možnost :guilabel:`Běžná faktura`. Odoo vytvoří fakturu na přesnou "
"částku potřebnou k dokončení celkové platby, jak je uvedeno v poli "
":guilabel:`Částka k fakturaci`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:148
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create Draft` to create a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft` page. The draft lists all the invoices for that specific sales order "
"in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. Each invoice line item displays all "
"the necessary information related to each invoice."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Vytvořit kladde` pro vytvoření stránky "
":guilabel:`Návrh zákaznické faktury`. Návrh obsahuje všechny faktury pro "
"danou salgsordre na kartě :guilabel:`Řádky faktury`. Každý řádek faktury "
"zobrazuje všechny potřebné informace související s každou fakturou."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:152
msgid ""
"To complete the flow, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to change the status of the "
"invoice from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Pay`. The :guilabel:`Pay` form appears, with all fields "
"auto-populated with the necessary information, including the remaining "
"amount left to be paid on the order."
msgstr ""
"For at fuldføre flowet skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at ændre "
"status for fakturaen fra :guilabel:`Udkast` til :guilabel:`Bogført`. Klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Betal`. :guilabel:`Betal`-formularen vises med alle "
"felter automatisk udfyldt med de nødvendige oplysninger, herunder det "
"resterende beløb, der skal betales på ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The second Pay pop-up form in Odoo sales."
msgstr "Den anden Betal pop op-formular i Odoo salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:160
msgid ""
"After confirming that information, click :guilabel:`Create Payment`. Doing "
"so reveals the final :guilabel:`Customer Invoice` with a green :guilabel:`In "
"Payment` or :guilabel:`Paid` banner in the upper-right corner, depending on "
"how the database has configured and if manual confirmation of payments is "
"required. Upon returning to the sales order, both down payments are present "
"in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Efter bekræftelse af disse oplysninger skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret "
"betaling`. Dette viser den endelige :guilabel:`Kundefaktura` med et "
"grønt :guilabel:`Under betaling` eller :guilabel:`Betalt` banner i øverste "
"højre hjørne, afhængigt af hvordan databasen er konfigureret, og om manuel "
"bekræftelse af betalinger er påkrævet. Når du vender tilbage til "
"salgsordren, er begge udbetalinger til stede på "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The second down payment invoice with Paid banner in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Den anden udbetalingsfaktura med Betalt banner i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:169
msgid "At this point, the flow is complete."
msgstr "V tomto okamžiku je proces dokončen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:172
msgid ""
"If a down payment is used with a product that has a :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities` invoicing policy, and the cost of the product exceeds the 50% "
"down payment, a regular invoice is created. However, for products that cost "
"less than the 50% down payment, the down payments will not be able to be "
"deducted when it comes time to invoice the customer."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je záloha použita u produktu, který má zásadu fakturace "
":guilabel:`Dodané množství`, a náklady na produkt přesahují 50% zálohu, "
"vytvoří se běžná faktura. U produktů, které stojí méně než 50% záloha, však "
"nebude možné zálohy odečíst, když přijde čas fakturovat zákazníkovi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:177
msgid ""
"This is because the product(s) would have to be delivered *before* creating "
"the final invoice due to Odoo not allowing negative totals for invoices. If "
"nothing has been delivered, a :guilabel:`Credit Note` is created, which "
"cancels the draft invoice that was created after the down payment."
msgstr ""
"Je to proto, že produkt(y) by musely být dodány *před* vytvořením konečné "
"faktury, protože Odoo neumožňuje záporné součty pro faktury. Pokud nebylo "
"nic dodáno, vytvoří se :guilabel:`Dobropis`, který zruší návrh faktury "
"vytvořený po záloze."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:182
msgid ""
"To utilize the :guilabel:`Credit Note` option, the **Inventory** application "
"must be installed in order to confirm the delivery. Otherwise, the delivered "
"quantity can be entered manually directly on the sales order."
msgstr ""
"For at bruge muligheden :guilabel:`Kreditnota` skal **Lager**-applikationen "
"være installeret for at bekræfte leveringen. Ellers kan den leverede mængde "
"indtastes manuelt direkte på salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:189
msgid "Example 2: 100% down payment"
msgstr "Příklad 2: 100% záloha"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:191
msgid ""
"A solar panel company sells an installation service for residential homes. "
"All installation services require a 100% down payment to cover labor costs. "
"The company prefers down payments as customers often require customization "
"add-ons for the service."
msgstr ""
"Společnost zabývající se solárními panely prodává instalační služby pro "
"obytné domy. Všechny instalační služby vyžadují 100% zálohu na pokrytí "
"nákladů na práci. Společnost preferuje zálohy, protože zákazníci často "
"vyžadují doplňky přizpůsobení služby."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:195
msgid ""
"To configure a 100% down payment, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"New`, and :ref:`create a quotation <sales/create-quotation>` for the "
"product. Upon clicking the :guilabel:`Confirm` button, the quotation turns "
"into a sales order. At that point, an invoice can now be created by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Create Invoice` in the top-left corner. On "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, "
"select :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, and type `100` in "
"the :guilabel:`Down Payment` field."
msgstr ""
"Pro konfiguraci 100% zálohy přejděte na :menuselection:`Aplikace Salg --> "
"Nový` a :ref:`vytvořte nabídku <sales/create-quotation>` pro produkt. Po "
"kliknutí na tlačítko :guilabel:`Potvrdit` se nabídka změní na salgsordre. V "
"tomto okamžiku lze vytvořit fakturu kliknutím na :guilabel:`Vytvořit "
"fakturu` v levém horním rohu. V pop-up okně :guilabel:`Vytvořit fakturu(y)`, "
"které se zobrazí, vyberte :guilabel:`Záloha (procento)` a do pole "
":guilabel:`Záloha` zadejte `100`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Down payment (percentage) option selected with 100% set as the Down "
"Payment."
msgstr ""
"Muligheden Acontobetaling (procent) valgt med 100 % angivet som "
"acontobetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:205
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Create Draft` to create an invoice draft. This will "
"also bring the draft invoice into view, which includes the :guilabel:`Down "
"payment` under the :guilabel:`Down Payments` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. The invoice can now be confirmed and "
"posted by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`. Confirming the invoice changes the "
"status from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`. It also reveals a new "
"series of buttons at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Dále klikněte na :guilabel:`Vytvořit kladde` pro vytvoření návrhu faktury. "
"Zobrazí se také návrh faktury, který zahrnuje :guilabel:`Zálohu` v sekci "
":guilabel:`Zálohy` na kartě :guilabel:`Řádky faktury`. Fakturu lze nyní "
"potvrdit a zaúčtovat kliknutím na :guilabel:`Potvrdit`. Potvrzením faktury "
"se změní stav z :guilabel:`Kladde` na :guilabel:`Zaúčtováno`. Zobrazí se "
"také nová řada tlačítek v horní části stránky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:211
msgid ""
"The payment can be registered by clicking the :guilabel:`Pay` button. This "
"brings up the :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up form, which is auto-populated with the "
"necessary information. When ready, click the :guilabel:`Create Payment` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Betalingen kan registreres ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Betal`. Dette "
"åbner formularen :guilabel:`Betal`, som automatisk udfyldes med de "
"nødvendige oplysninger. Når du er klar, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Opret betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:215
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Create Payment`, Odoo reveals the customer "
"invoice, now with a green :guilabel:`In Payment` or :guilabel:`Paid` banner "
"in the upper-right corner, depending on how the database has configured and "
"if manual confirmation of payments is required. The process is now complete, "
"and the 100% down payment has been successfully applied."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have klikket på :guilabel:`Opret betaling` viser Odoo "
"kundefakturaen, nu med et grønt banner :guilabel:`I betaling` "
"eller :guilabel:`Betalt` i øverste højre hjørne, afhængigt af hvordan "
"databasen er konfigureret, og om manuel bekræftelse af betalinger er "
"påkrævet. Processen er nu fuldført, og 100% forudbetalingen er blevet "
"anvendt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:223
msgid "Income account modification on down payments"
msgstr "Ændring af indtægtskonto på acontobetalinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:226
msgid ""
"To change or adjust the income account attached to down payments, the "
"**Accounting** app must be installed. With the **Accounting** app installed, "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` column becomes available on the draft invoice."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre indkomstkontoen knyttet til forudbetalinger skal appen "
"**Regnskab** være installeret. Med appen **Regnskab** installeret bliver "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Regnskab` tilgængelig på fakturakladden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:230
msgid ""
"Navigate to the invoice to be modified by going to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Orders --> Orders`. Open an order, then click the :guilabel:`Invoices` "
"smart button. Open an invoice, click the drop-down arrow on the entry in "
"the :guilabel:`Account` column and click :guilabel:`Search more...` to bring "
"up the :guilabel:`Search: Account` form. In this form, a different account "
"can be chosen from the list of pre-existing accounts. A new account can also "
"be created by clicking the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Gå til fakturaen, der skal ændres, ved at gå til :menuselection:`Salg app --"
"> Ordrer --> Ordrer`. Åbn en ordre, og klik derefter på den smarte "
"knap :guilabel:`Fakturaer`. Åbn en faktura, klik på rullepilen ved posten i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Konto`, og klik på :guilabel:`Søg mere...` for at åbne "
"formularen :guilabel:`Søg: Konto`. I denne formular kan der vælges en anden "
"konto fra listen over eksisterende konti. Der kan også oprettes en ny konto "
"ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Search:Account form with existing accounts displayed and a button to "
"create a new\n"
"account."
msgstr ""
"Formularen Søg: Konto med eksisterende konti vist og en knap til at oprette "
"en ny konto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:242
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:71
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:166
msgid ":doc:`invoicing_policy`"
msgstr ":doc:`invoicing_policy`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:243
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/payment_terms`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing policies"
msgstr "Faktureringspolitikker"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:5
msgid ""
"Depending on business needs, it may be advantageous to choose whether to "
"invoice customers based on the goods and services that they order or when "
"those goods and services are delivered to them. To allow businesses maximum "
"flexibility to best meet their needs, Odoo offers two invoicing policies "
"that can be enabled in the **Sales** app: :ref:`Invoice what is ordered "
"<invoice-on-order>` and :ref:`Invoice what is delivered <invoice-on-"
"delivery>`."
msgstr ""
"Afhængigt af forretningsbehov kan det være fordelagtigt at vælge, om man vil "
"fakturere kunder baseret på de varer og tjenester, de bestiller, eller når "
"disse varer og tjenester leveres til dem. For at give virksomheder maksimal "
"fleksibilitet til bedst muligt at opfylde deres behov tilbyder Odoo to "
"faktureringspolitikker, der kan aktiveres i **Salg**-appen: :ref:`Fakturer "
"det bestilte <invoice-on-order>` og :ref:`Fakturer det leverede <invoice-on-"
"delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:11
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is ordered* rule is used as the default mode in Odoo "
"**Sales**, which means customers are invoiced once the sales order is "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Reglen *Fakturer det, der er bestilt* bruges som standardtilstand i Odoo "
"**Salg**, hvilket betyder, at kunder faktureres, når salgsordren er "
"bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:13
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is delivered* rule invoices customers once the delivery is "
"done. This rule is often used for businesses that sell materials, liquids, "
"or food in large quantities. In these cases, the ordered quantity may differ "
"slightly from the delivered quantity, making it preferable to invoice the "
"quantity actually delivered. When the delivery order is validated, Odoo will "
"automatically decrease the on-hand quantity in the inventory."
msgstr ""
"Reglen *Fakturer det, der er leveret* fakturerer kunder, når leveringen er "
"udført. Denne regel bruges ofte af virksomheder, der sælger materialer, "
"væsker eller fødevarer i store mængder. I disse tilfælde kan den bestilte "
"mængde afvige lidt fra den leverede mængde, hvilket gør det at foretrække at "
"fakturere den faktisk leverede mængde. Når leveringsordren valideres, vil "
"Odoo automatisk reducere beholdningen på lageret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure an invoicing policy, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and under the :guilabel:`Invoicing` heading, "
"select an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` option: :guilabel:`Invoice what is "
"ordered` or :guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered`."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere en faktureringspolitik, gå til :menuselection:`Salg-app --"
"> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Fakturering`, vælg "
"en :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik`-mulighed: :guilabel:`Fakturer det "
"bestilte` eller :guilabel:`Fakturer det leverede`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:23
msgid ""
"Activating an invoicing policy option automatically applies the chosen "
"option to all newly created products. Existing products **must** have their "
"invoicing policy manually updated on their product forms."
msgstr ""
"Aktivering af en faktureringspolitik-mulighed anvender automatisk den valgte "
"mulighed på alle nyoprettede produkter. Eksisterende produkter **skal** have "
"deres faktureringspolitik manuelt opdateret på deres produktformularer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "Choosing an invoicing policy in the Sales app."
msgstr "Valg af en faktureringspolitik i Salg-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:31
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered` option is chosen, it is **not** "
"possible to activate the :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice` feature, which "
"automatically generates invoices when an online payment is confirmed. "
"Regular draft invoices can only be created once the delivery order has been "
"processed and validated."
msgstr ""
"Hvis :guilabel:`Fakturer det leverede`-muligheden vælges, er det **ikke** "
"muligt at aktivere :guilabel:`Automatisk faktura`-funktionen, som automatisk "
"genererer fakturaer, når en onlinebetaling bekræftes. Almindelige "
"kladdefakturaer kan kun oprettes, når leveringsordren er blevet behandlet og "
"valideret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:37
msgid "Changing the invoicing policy for existing products"
msgstr "Ændring af faktureringspolitikken for eksisterende produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:39
msgid ""
"After the invoicing policy has been configured in *Settings*, navigate to a "
"product's form through :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` "
"and choosing a product. Locate the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` option "
"located under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab. Use the drop-down "
"menu to change the policy."
msgstr ""
"Efter faktureringspolitikken er blevet konfigureret i *Indstillinger*, "
"naviger til en produktformular via :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Produkter --"
"> Produkter` og vælg et produkt. Find :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik`-"
"muligheden under fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger`. Brug rullemenuen "
"til at ændre politikken."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "How to change invoicing policy on a product form in the **Sales** app."
msgstr ""
"Sådan ændres faktureringspolitik på en produktformular i **Salg**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:50
msgid "Invoicing what is ordered"
msgstr "Fakturering af det bestilte"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:52
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is ordered* option is used as the default mode in the "
"**Sales** app, which means customers are invoiced once a quotation has been "
"sent to the customer and confirmed. The creation of a quotation in turn "
"leads to the creation and confirmation of a sales order. An invoice can then "
"be created as soon as the sales order is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Indstillingen *Fakturer det, der er bestilt* bruges som standardtilstand i "
"appen **Salg**, hvilket betyder, at kunder faktureres, når et tilbud er "
"blevet sendt til kunden og bekræftet. Oprettelsen af et tilbud fører til "
"gengæld til oprettelsen og bekræftelsen af en salgsordre. En faktura kan "
"derefter oprettes, så snart salgsordren er bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:57
msgid "This invoicing policy has no impact on the basic Odoo sales flow."
msgstr ""
"Denne faktureringspolitik har ingen indvirkning på det grundlæggende Odoo-"
"salgsflow."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:60
msgid "Invoice ordered quantity workflow"
msgstr "Fakturer bestilt mængde workflow"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:62
msgid ""
"Confirm that the product's invoicing policy is set to :guilabel:`Ordered "
"quantities` in the product form. :ref:`Create a quotation and sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` as normal. After the sales order has been "
"confirmed, create an invoice by clicking the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` "
"button on the sales order form. Choose the type of invoice to be sent, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`, confirm the invoice when ready, and "
"proceed with the payment flow as normal."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft, at produktets faktureringspolitik er sat til :guilabel:`Bestilte "
"mængder` i produktformularen. :ref:`Opret et tilbud og en salgsordre <sales/"
"create-quotation>` som normalt. Efter salgsordren er blevet bekræftet, opret "
"en faktura ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Opret faktura` på "
"salgsordreformularen. Vælg den type faktura, der skal sendes, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Opret udkast til faktura`, bekræft fakturaen, når den er klar, "
"og fortsæt med betalingsflowet som normalt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:69
msgid ""
"A independent artisan with a small business sells handmade jewelery "
"nationwide online. Because they have direct control over their inventory "
"levels and ship with 3rd party carriers, they invoice their customers after "
"a sales order has been confirmed."
msgstr ""
"En uafhængig håndværker med en lille virksomhed sælger håndlavet smykker på "
"landsplan online. Da de har direkte kontrol over deres lagerniveauer og "
"sender med tredjepartsleverandører, fakturerer de deres kunder, efter at en "
"salgsordre er blevet bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:73
msgid ""
"The artisan receives an order for a necklace. They send their customer a "
"quotation, confirm it, and create a sales order. After the sales order has "
"been confirmed, an invoice can be created and sent to the customer for "
"payment without any additional steps be taken. The invoice gets paid, the "
"necklace is shipped and delivered, and the transaction is complete."
msgstr ""
"Håndværkeren modtager en ordre på en halskæde. De sender deres kunde et "
"tilbud, bekræfter det og opretter en salgsordre. Efter salgsordren er blevet "
"bekræftet, kan en faktura oprettes og sendes til kunden til betaling uden "
"yderligere trin. Fakturaen bliver betalt, halskæden bliver afsendt og "
"leveret, og transaktionen er fuldført."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:81
msgid "Invoicing what is delivered"
msgstr "Fakturering af det, der er leveret"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:83
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is delivered* option invoices customers as different "
"amounts of the ordered goods are delivered. This option is often used for "
"businesses that sell large quantities of physical goods in each sales order, "
"but may not always be able to completely fulfill a given order all at once. "
"In these cases, the ordered quantity may differ slightly from the delivered "
"quantity based on product availability. Once a quotation is confirmed, and "
"the status changes from :guilabel:`Quotation sent` to :guilabel:`Sales "
"order`, Odoo automatically adds both the delivered and invoiced quantities "
"to the invoice and sales order. Both partial and complete deliveries are "
"tracked. :ref:`Backorders <inventory/shipping/backorders>` can be created "
"for partial orders that will be completed at a later time."
msgstr ""
"Indstillingen *Fakturer det, der er leveret* fakturerer kunder, efterhånden "
"som forskellige mængder af de bestilte varer leveres. Denne indstilling "
"bruges ofte af virksomheder, der sælger store mængder fysiske varer i hver "
"salgsordre, men måske ikke altid er i stand til at opfylde en given ordre "
"helt på én gang. I disse tilfælde kan den bestilte mængde afvige lidt fra "
"den leverede mængde baseret på produkttilgængelighed. Når et tilbud er "
"bekræftet, og status ændres fra :guilabel:`Tilbud sendt` "
"til :guilabel:`Salgsordre`, tilføjer Odoo automatisk både de leverede og "
"fakturerede mængder til fakturaen og salgsordren. Både delvise og komplette "
"leveringer spores. :ref:`Restordrer <inventory/shipping/backorders>` kan "
"oprettes for delvise ordrer, der vil blive fuldført på et senere tidspunkt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:93
msgid ""
"This invoicing policy has a minor impact on the sales flow because the "
"delivered quantity of a product needs to be manually entered on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Denne faktureringspolitik har en mindre indvirkning på salgsflowet, fordi "
"den leverede mængde af et produkt skal indtastes manuelt på salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "How to see delivered and invoiced quantities on Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Sådan ser du leverede og fakturerede mængder i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:100
msgid "Invoice delivered quantity workflow"
msgstr "Fakturer leveret mængde workflow"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:102
msgid ""
"Confirm that the product's invoicing policy is set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities` in the product form. :ref:`Create a quotation and sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` as normal. After the sales order has been "
"confirmed, the product must be delivered before an invoice can be created."
msgstr ""
"Bekræft, at produktets faktureringspolitik er sat til :guilabel:`Leverede "
"mængder` i produktformularen. :ref:`Opret et tilbud og en salgsordre <sales/"
"create-quotation>` som normalt. Efter salgsordren er blevet bekræftet, skal "
"produktet leveres, før en faktura kan oprettes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once the product has been shipped and delivery has been confirmed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button on the sales order screen and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the delivery order. Once at least a "
"partial delivery has been confirmed, return to the sales order form. "
"The :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button is now purple to indicate that an "
"invoice can be created and confirmed, and that it is possible to proceed "
"with the payment flow as normal."
msgstr ""
"Når produktet er blevet afsendt, og leveringen er bekræftet, klik på den "
"smarte knap :guilabel:`Levering` på salgsordre-skærmen, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Valider` for at validere leveringsordren. Når mindst en delvis "
"levering er blevet bekræftet, vend tilbage til salgsordreformularen. "
"Knappen :guilabel:`Opret faktura` er nu lilla for at indikere, at en faktura "
"kan oprettes og bekræftes, og at det er muligt at fortsætte med "
"betalingsflowet som normalt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:113
msgid ""
"If a user attempts to create an invoice without validating the delivered "
"quantity, the system returns an error message alerting them to the issue."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en bruger forsøger at oprette en faktura uden at validere den leverede "
"mængde, returnerer systemet en fejlmeddelelse, der gør dem opmærksomme på "
"problemet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:0
msgid ""
"If Delivered Quantities invoicing policy is chosen, ensure a quantity has "
"been\n"
"delivered."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der vælges fakturering af leverede mængder, skal du sikre dig, at en "
"mængde er blevet leveret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:121
msgid ""
"A produce distributor using the invoice what is delivered option sells 50 "
"heads of lettuce to a local restaurant. At the time the delivery is made, "
"only 40 heads are available. The distributor delivers the available heads of "
"lettuce and creates an invoice for what was delivered. Later, when more "
"supply comes in, the distributor delivers the remaning 10 heads of lettuce "
"and creates a second invoice to complete the order."
msgstr ""
"En grøntsagsdistributør, der bruger indstillingen fakturer det, der er "
"leveret, sælger 50 salathoveder til en lokal restaurant. På det tidspunkt, "
"leveringen foretages, er kun 40 hoveder tilgængelige. Distributøren leverer "
"de tilgængelige salathoveder og opretter en faktura for det, der blev "
"leveret. Senere, når mere forsyning kommer ind, leverer distributøren de "
"resterende 10 salathoveder og opretter en anden faktura for at fuldføre "
"ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:128
msgid ":doc:`../sales_quotations/create_quotations`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales_quotations/create_quotations`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:129
msgid ":doc:`down_payment`"
msgstr ":doc:`down_payment`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:131
msgid ""
":doc:`../../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:3
msgid "Invoice project milestones"
msgstr "Fakturere projektmilepæle"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:8
msgid ""
"Milestone-based invoicing is designed for companies that deliver work in "
"clearly defined phases. Instead of invoicing an entire service upfront or at "
"the very end, businesses can bill customers progressively as each stage of "
"work is completed. This approach provides customers clearer visibility into "
"progress and value delivered over time."
msgstr ""
"Fakturace založená na milnících je navržena pro společnosti, které dodávají "
"práci v jasně definovaných fázích. Místo fakturace celé služby předem nebo "
"úplně na konci mohou podniky účtovat zákazníkům postupně při dokončení každé "
"fáze práce. Tento přístup poskytuje zákazníkům jasnější přehled o pokroku a "
"hodnotě dodané v průběhu času."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo, milestone invoicing is configured at the product level in the "
"**Sales** app, with milestone progress and completion managed in the "
"**Projects** app. When a milestone is marked as reached, the delivered "
"quantity on the sales order (SO) is updated and can be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo je fakturace milníků nakonfigurována na úrovni produktu v aplikaci "
"**Salg**, přičemž pokrok a dokončení milníků jsou spravovány v aplikaci "
"**Projekty**. Když je milník označen jako dosažený, dodané množství na "
"salgsordre (SO) se aktualizuje a lze jej fakturovat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:18
msgid "How milestone invoicing works"
msgstr "Jak funguje fakturace milníků"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:20
msgid ""
"Milestone invoicing follows a clear workflow involving multiple applications "
"in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Fakturace milníků sleduje jasný pracovní postup zahrnující více aplikací v "
"Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:22
msgid ""
"A product is created in the **Sales** application, configured to be invoiced "
"based on milestones."
msgstr ""
"Produkt je vytvořen v aplikaci **Salg**, nakonfigurován tak, aby byl "
"fakturován na základě milníků."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:23
msgid "A |SO| is created with the product."
msgstr "|SO| je vytvořena s produktem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:24
msgid ""
"A project in the **Projects** app is created with multiple milestones "
"included."
msgstr ""
"Projekt v aplikaci **Projekty** je vytvořen s několika zahrnutými milníky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:25
msgid ""
"A milestone is reached, and marked complete, causing the *Delivered* "
"quantity on the |SO| line to update."
msgstr ""
"Milník je dosažen a označen jako dokončený, což způsobí aktualizaci množství "
"*Dodáno* na řádku |SO|."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:27
msgid ""
"An invoice is created for the completed milestone, which can be sent to the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Je vytvořena faktura za dokončený milník, kterou lze odeslat zákazníkovi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:30
msgid ""
"This document covers the **Sales** app configuration and invoicing flow for "
"invoicing based on project milestones. For more information on creating, "
"managing, and marking milestones as complete, and how to link them to tasks, "
"see :doc:`Project milestones <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_milestones>`."
msgstr ""
"Tento dokument pokrývá konfiguraci aplikace **Salg** a proces fakturace "
"založený na milnících projektu. Další informace o vytváření, správě a "
"označování milníků jako dokončených a jak je propojit s úkoly najdete "
"v :doc:`Milníky projektu <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_milestones>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:36
msgid "Create milestone products"
msgstr "Oprette milepælprodukter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:38
msgid ""
"To begin, a service product must be configured specifically for milestone-"
"based invoicing. Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter the necessary information, "
"including the product title and :guilabel:`Sales Price`."
msgstr ""
"Pro začátek musí být služební produkt nakonfigurován speciálně pro fakturaci "
"založenou na milnících. Přejděte na :menuselection:`Salg app --> Produkter --"
"> Produkter` a klikněte na :guilabel:`Ny`. Vyplňte potřebné informace včetně "
"názvu produktu a :guilabel:`Salgspris`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:42
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Product Type`, select :guilabel:`Service`. Doing so "
"reveals the :guilabel:`Create on Order` field. Select "
"either :guilabel:`Project`, :guilabel:`Project and Task`, "
"or :guilabel:`Task`, depending on how the product is to be tracked in the "
"**Project** app."
msgstr ""
"Pro :guilabel:`Produkttype` vyberte :guilabel:`Service`. Tím se zobrazí "
"pole :guilabel:`Opret ved ordre`. Vyberte "
"buď :guilabel:`Projekt`, :guilabel:`Projekt og opgave`, "
"nebo :guilabel:`Opgave`, v závislosti na tom, jak má být produkt sledován v "
"aplikaci **Projekt**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:47
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Project Template` can also be selected for the product. "
"See :doc:`Project templates <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_templates>` for more information. Project templates can have "
"milestones defined, however, the *Quantity (%)* field must be manually "
"updated on each newly created project."
msgstr ""
"Pro produkt lze také vybrat :guilabel:`Projektskabelon`. Další informace "
"najdete v :doc:`Projektskabeloner <../../../services/project/"
"project_management/project_templates>`. Projektové šablony mohou mít "
"definované milníky, avšak pole *Procent (%)* musí být u každého nově "
"vytvořeného projektu aktualizováno ručně."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:52
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`, select :guilabel:`Based on "
"Milestones`. This option ensures that the product's delivered quantities "
"update automatically once a milestone is completed."
msgstr ""
"Pro :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik` vyberte :guilabel:`Baseret på milepæle`. "
"Tato možnost zajistí, že dodaná množství produktu se automaticky aktualizují "
"po dokončení milníku."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:56
msgid ""
"*Based on Milestones* is only available if there is at least one project "
"with *Milestones* enabled."
msgstr ""
"*Baseret på milepæle* je dostupné pouze v případě, že existuje alespoň jeden "
"projekt se zapnutými *Milepæle*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:60
msgid "Defining milestones"
msgstr "Definování milníků"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:63
msgid ""
"This document focuses on the process of selling and invoicing a milestone "
"product in the **Sales** app. For more information on creating milestones in "
"the **Project** app, see :doc:`Project milestones <../../../services/project/"
"project_management/project_milestones>`."
msgstr ""
"Tento dokument se zaměřuje na proces prodeje a fakturace produktu milníku v "
"aplikaci **Salg**. Další informace o vytváření milníků v aplikaci "
"**Projekt** najdete v :doc:`Milníky projektu <../../../services/project/"
"project_management/project_milestones>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:67
msgid ""
"After the milestone product has been sold, a  *Milestones* smart button is "
"added to the |SO|. Click the smart button to view, edit, or create new "
"milestones."
msgstr ""
"Po prodeji produktu milníku je k |SO| přidáno chytré tlačítko *Milepæle*. "
"Kliknutím na chytré tlačítko zobrazíte, upravíte nebo vytvoříte nové milníky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:70
msgid ""
"From here, the :guilabel:`Delivered %` can be altered. This amount equates "
"to the total cost of the |SO| that is billed when the milestone is reached."
msgstr ""
"Odtud lze změnit :guilabel:`Leveret %`. Tato částka odpovídá celkovým "
"nákladům |SO|, které jsou fakturovány po dosažení milníku."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:74
msgid ""
"A company that provides pool installation services bills based on predefined "
"milestones as the work is completed. Each milestone equates to 25% of the "
"total services:"
msgstr ""
"Společnost poskytující služby instalace bazénů fakturuje na základě "
"předdefinovaných milníků v průběhu dokončování práce. Každý milník odpovídá "
"25 % celkových služeb:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:77
msgid "Site Preparation & Excavation"
msgstr "Příprava a výkop místa"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:78
msgid "Structural Installation"
msgstr "Stavební instalace"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:79
msgid "Plumbing & Equipment Installation"
msgstr "Instalace potrubí a zařízení"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:80
msgid "Finishing & Final Inspection"
msgstr "Dokončovací práce a závěrečná kontrola"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:None
msgid "The milestones for a sales order line."
msgstr "Milníky pro řádek salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:85
msgid ""
"The team uses a project template, called *Pool installation*, with these "
"milestones defined. A new project is created whenever a |SO| with the *Pool "
"installation services* product is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Tým používá projektovou šablonu nazvanou *Instalace bazénu* s těmito "
"definovanými milníky. Nový projekt je vytvořen vždy, když je potvrzen |SO| s "
"produktem *Služby instalace bazénu*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:90
msgid "Invoicing a completed milestone"
msgstr "Fakturering af en gennemført milepæl"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:92
msgid ""
"Milestones can be tracked through the **Project** app (see :ref:`Using "
"milestones <project/using-milestones>`). Additionally, a milestone can be "
"marked complete by navigating to the |SO|, and clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Milestones` smart button. On the *Milestones* page, enable "
"the checkbox in the :guilabel:`Reached` column for the milestone."
msgstr ""
"Milepæle kan spores gennem **Projekt**-appen (se :ref:`Brug af milepæle "
"<project/using-milestones>`). Desuden kan en milepæl markeres som gennemført "
"ved at navigere til |SO| og klikke på den smarte knap :guilabel:`Milepæle`. "
"På siden *Milepæle* skal du aktivere afkrydsningsfeltet i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Nået` for milepælen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:97
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`View Sales Order` or use the breadcrumbs to return to "
"the |SO|. The :guilabel:`Delivered` column will be updated to reflect the "
"*Delivered %* for the milestone reached."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Vis salgsordre`, eller brug brødkrummerne til at "
"vende tilbage til |SO|. Kolonnen :guilabel:`Leveret` opdateres for at "
"afspejle *Leveret %* for den nåede milepæl."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:100
msgid ""
"These steps can be repeated as additional milestones are reached until the |"
"SO| has been fulfilled."
msgstr ""
"Disse trin kan gentages, efterhånden som yderligere milepæle nås, indtil |"
"SO| er opfyldt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:103
msgid ""
"Reaching a milestone does *not* automatically create an invoice. Instead, it "
"updates the |SO| to reflect the amount of the total that is ready for "
"invoicing."
msgstr ""
"At nå en milepæl opretter *ikke* automatisk en faktura. I stedet opdaterer "
"det |SO| for at afspejle det beløb af totalen, der er klar til fakturering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once one or more milestones have been reached, navigate to the |SO|, and "
"confirm the :guilabel:`Delivered` column has updated correctly. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Når en eller flere milepæle er nået, skal du navigere til |SO| og bekræfte, "
"at kolonnen :guilabel:`Leveret` er opdateret korrekt. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Opret faktura`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:109
msgid ""
"Additional milestones can be invoiced as they are completed, until all "
"services are complete."
msgstr ""
"Yderligere milepæle kan faktureres, efterhånden som de gennemføres, indtil "
"alle serviceydelser er færdige."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:112
msgid ":doc:`time_materials`"
msgstr ":doc:`time_materials`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:113
msgid ":doc:`proforma`"
msgstr ":doc:`proforma`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:3
msgid "Pro-forma invoices"
msgstr "Proformafakturaer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *pro-forma invoice* is an abridged or estimated invoice sent in advance of "
"a delivery of goods. It notes the kind and quantity of goods, their value, "
"and other important information, such as weight and transportation charges."
msgstr ""
"En *proformafaktura* er en forkortet eller estimeret faktura, der sendes "
"forud for en levering af varer. Den angiver type og antal af varer, deres "
"værdi og andre vigtige oplysninger, såsom vægt og transportomkostninger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:9
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices are commonly used as preliminary invoices with a "
"quotation. They are also used during importation for customs purposes. They "
"differ from a normal invoice, in that they are *not* a demand (or request) "
"for payment."
msgstr ""
"Proformafakturaer bruges almindeligvis som foreløbige fakturaer med et "
"tilbud. De bruges også under import til toldformål. De adskiller sig fra en "
"normal faktura ved, at de *ikke* er en anmodning om betaling."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:16
msgid ""
"In order to utilize pro-forma invoices, the *Pro-Forma Invoice* feature "
"**must** be activated."
msgstr ""
"For at kunne bruge proformafakturaer *skal* funktionen *Proformafaktura* "
"aktiveres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:18
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& Orders` "
"section, click the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere denne funktion skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Salg-app "
"--> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, og i afsnittet :guilabel:`Tilbud & "
"ordrer` skal du markere afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Proformafaktura`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem` for at "
"gemme alle ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid "The Pro-Forma Invoice feature setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr ""
"Indstillingen for funktionen Proformafaktura i Odoo Salg-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:27
msgid "Send pro-forma invoice"
msgstr "Send proformafaktura"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:29
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice` feature activated, the option to send "
"a pro-forma invoice is now available on any quotation or sales order, via "
"the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"Med funktionen :guilabel:`Proformafaktura` aktiveret er muligheden for at "
"sende en proformafaktura nu tilgængelig på ethvert tilbud eller salgsordre "
"via knappen :guilabel:`Send proformafaktura`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Send Pro-Forma Invoice button on a typical sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Knappen Send Pro-Forma Invoice på en typisk salgsordre i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:37
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices can **not** be sent for a sales order or quotation if an "
"invoice for a down payment has already been sent, or for a recurring "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Pro-forma fakturaer kan **ikke** sendes for en salgsordre eller et tilbud, "
"hvis der allerede er sendt en faktura for en forudbetaling, eller for et "
"tilbagevendende abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:40
msgid ""
"In either case, the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Froma Invoice` button does **not** "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"I begge tilfælde vises knappen :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` **ikke**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:42
msgid ""
"However, pro-forma invoices **can** be sent for services, event "
"registrations, courses, and/or new subscriptions. Pro-forma invoices are not "
"limited to physical, consumable, or storable goods."
msgstr ""
"Pro-forma fakturaer **kan** dog sendes for tjenester, eventregistreringer, "
"kurser og/eller nye abonnementer. Pro-forma fakturaer er ikke begrænset til "
"fysiske, forbrugsvarer eller lagerbare varer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:45
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button is clicked, a pop-up "
"window appears, from which an email can be sent."
msgstr ""
"Når der klikkes på knappen :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice`, vises et pop "
"op-vindue, hvorfra der kan sendes en e-mail."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:48
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Recipients` field is auto-populated "
"with the customer from the sales order or quotation. The :guilabel:`Subject` "
"field and the body of the email can be modified, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet udfyldes feltet :guilabel:`Recipients` automatisk med "
"kunden fra salgsordren eller tilbuddet. Feltet :guilabel:`Subject` og "
"brødteksten i e-mailen kan om nødvendigt ændres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:52
msgid ""
"The pro-forma invoice is automatically added as an attachment to the email."
msgstr ""
"Pro-forma fakturaen tilføjes automatisk som en vedhæftet fil til e-mailen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:54
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Send`, and Odoo instantly sends the email, with "
"the attached pro-forma invoice, to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Send`, og Odoo sender straks e-"
"mailen med den vedhæftede pro-forma faktura til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The email pop-up window that appears with pro-forma invoice attached in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Pop op-vinduet med e-mail, der vises med vedhæftet pro-forma faktura i Odoo "
"Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:62
msgid ""
"To preview what the pro-forma invoice looks like, click on the PDF at the "
"bottom of the email pop-up window *before* clicking :guilabel:`Send`. When "
"clicked, the pro-forma invoice is downloaded instantly. Open that PDF to "
"view (and review) the pro-forma invoice."
msgstr ""
"For at få vist en forhåndsvisning af, hvordan pro-forma fakturaen ser ud, "
"skal du klikke på PDF-filen nederst i pop op-vinduet med e-mailen *før* du "
"klikker på :guilabel:`Send`. Når der klikkes, downloades pro-forma fakturaen "
"øjeblikkeligt. Åbn PDF-filen for at se (og gennemgå) pro-forma fakturaen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:0
msgid "Sample pro-forma invoice PDF from Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Eksempel på pro-forma faktura PDF fra Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing based on time and materials"
msgstr "Fakturering baseret på tid og materialer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:5
msgid ""
"Invoicing based on time and/or materials is typically used when accurately "
"estimating the size of a project isn't possible, or when the requirements of "
"a project may change."
msgstr ""
"Fakturering baseret på tid og/eller materialer bruges typisk, når det ikke "
"er muligt at estimere størrelsen af et projekt nøjagtigt, eller når kravene "
"til et projekt kan ændre sig."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is different from a fixed-price contract, when a customer agrees to pay "
"a specified total for the fulfillment of the contract---no matter what needs "
"to be paid to the employees, sub-contractors, vendors, suppliers, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Dette er anderledes end en fastpriskontrakt, hvor en kunde accepterer at "
"betale et specificeret totalbeløb for opfyldelsen af kontrakten – uanset "
"hvad der skal betales til medarbejdere, underentreprenører, leverandører osv."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app can invoice for time and various other expenses (e.g. "
"transport, lodging), as well as purchases needed to fulfill an order."
msgstr ""
"Odoo *Salg*-appen kan fakturere for tid og forskellige andre udgifter "
"(f.eks. transport, logi) samt indkøb, der er nødvendige for at opfylde en "
"ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:16
msgid "App and settings configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af app og indstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:18
msgid ""
"First, in order to accurately keep track of the progress of a project, the "
"Odoo *Project* and *Accounting* apps **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"For det første skal Odoo *Projekt*- og *Regnskab*-appene **være** "
"installeret for at kunne holde nøjagtigt styr på fremskridtene i et projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install the *Project* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Project` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where the "
"*Project* app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"For at installere *Projekt*-appen skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Odoo-"
"hovedmenu --> Apps`. Derefter skal du på siden :guilabel:`Apps` finde "
"blokken :guilabel:`Projekt` og klikke på :guilabel:`Activate`. Siden "
"opdateres automatisk og vender tilbage til Odoo-hovedmenuen, hvor *Projekt*-"
"appen nu er tilgængelig."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:26
msgid "Repeat the same process to install the *Accounting* application."
msgstr "Gentag den samme proces for at installere *Regnskab*-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:28
msgid ""
"After installation, click the :guilabel:`Accounting` app icon from the main "
"Odoo dashboard, and navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. "
"On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Analytics` "
"section, and ensure the box next to :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Efter installationen skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Regnskab`-appikonet fra "
"Odoo-hovedmenuen og navigere til :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings`. På siden :guilabel:`Settings` skal du rulle ned til "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Analytics` og sikre, at boksen ved siden "
"af :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` er markeret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How it looks to activate the Analytic Accounting setting in Odoo Accounting "
"Setting page."
msgstr ""
"Sådan ser det ud at aktivere indstillingen Analytisk regnskab på siden med "
"indstillinger for Odoo Regnskab."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:43
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr "Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem` for at gemme alle ændringer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:39
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main dashboard --> Project app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, in "
"the :guilabel:`Time Management` section, ensure the box beside "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` feature is checked."
msgstr ""
"Gå derefter til :menuselection:`Odoo hovedoversigt --> Projekt-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. På siden :guilabel:`Indstillinger` i "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Tidsstyring` skal du sikre dig, at boksen ved siden af "
"funktionen :guilabel:`Timesedler` er markeret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"What the Timesheets feature looks like on the Odoo Project settings page."
msgstr ""
"Sådan ser funktionen Timesedler ud på siden med indstillinger for Odoo "
"Projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:52
msgid "Service product configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af tjenesteprodukt"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:54
msgid ""
"With the *Timesheets* feature activated in the *Project* app, it is now "
"possible to invoice for time spent on a project, but **only** when the "
"following product configurations have been made."
msgstr ""
"Med funktionen *Timesedler* aktiveret i *Projekt*-appen er det nu muligt at "
"fakturere for tid brugt på et projekt, men **kun** når følgende "
"produktkonfigurationer er foretaget."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:58
msgid ""
"Invoicing for time spent on a project is **only** possible with products "
"that have *Service* set as the *Product Type* on their product form."
msgstr ""
"Fakturering for tid brugt på et projekt er **kun** muligt med produkter, der "
"har *Tjeneste* angivet som *Produkttype* på deres produktformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a service product, first navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Products`. On the :guilabel:`Products` page, select the "
"desired service product to be configured, or click :guilabel:`New` to create "
"a new product."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere et tjenesteprodukt skal du først gå "
"til :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Produkter --> Produkter`. På "
"siden :guilabel:`Produkter` skal du vælge det ønskede tjenesteprodukt, der "
"skal konfigureres, eller klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette et nyt "
"produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:65
msgid ""
"From the product form, in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Service`. Then, open the drop-"
"down menu in the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Based on Timesheets`."
msgstr ""
"Fra produktformularen i fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger` skal du "
"indstille :guilabel:`Produkttype` til :guilabel:`Tjeneste`. Åbn derefter "
"rullelisten i feltet :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik`, og "
"vælg :guilabel:`Baseret på timesedler`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:69
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Create on Order` drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Project \\& Task`. That setting indicates that, when a "
"sales order is created with this specific service product, a new project and "
"task is created in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter :guilabel:`Projekt \\& opgave` fra "
"rullelisten :guilabel:`Opret ved ordre`. Den indstilling angiver, at når en "
"salgsordre oprettes med dette specifikke tjenesteprodukt, oprettes et nyt "
"projekt og en opgave i *Projekt*-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"The correct settings for Invoicing Policy and Create on Order fields for "
"service product."
msgstr ""
"De korrekte indstillinger for felterne Faktureringspolitik og Opret ved "
"ordre for tjenesteprodukt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:78
msgid ""
"The option :guilabel:`Task` can be chosen instead from the :guilabel:`Create "
"on Order` drop-down menu. If :guilabel:`Task` is chosen, select an existing "
"project that the task will appear in from :guilabel:`Project` field, which "
"only appears if :guilabel:`Task` is chosen in the :guilabel:`Create on "
"Order` field."
msgstr ""
"Muligheden :guilabel:`Opgave` kan i stedet vælges fra "
"rullelisten :guilabel:`Opret ved ordre`. Hvis :guilabel:`Opgave` vælges, "
"skal du vælge et eksisterende projekt, som opgaven skal vises i, fra "
"feltet :guilabel:`Projekt`, som kun vises, hvis :guilabel:`Opgave` er valgt "
"i feltet :guilabel:`Opret ved ordre`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:84
msgid "Add time spent to sales order"
msgstr "Tilføj tid brugt til salgsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:86
msgid ""
"After properly configuring a service product with the correct *Invoicing "
"Policy* and *Create on Order* options, it is possible to add time spent to a "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"Efter korrekt konfiguration af et tjenesteprodukt med de korrekte "
"indstillinger for *Faktureringspolitik* og *Opret ved ordre* er det muligt "
"at tilføje tid brugt til en salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:89
msgid ""
"To see that in action, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New` to "
"open a blank quotation form. Then, proceed to add a :guilabel:`Customer`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select the properly :ref:`configured service product <sales/invoicing/"
"configured-service-product>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"For at se det i aktion skal du gå til :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Ny` for "
"at åbne en tom tilbudsformular. Fortsæt derefter med at tilføje "
"en :guilabel:`Kunde`, og i fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt` og vælge det korrekt :ref:`konfigurerede "
"tjenesteprodukt <sales/invoicing/configured-service-product>` fra "
"rullelisten."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:94
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the order."
msgstr "Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at bekræfte ordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:96
msgid ""
"After confirming the sales order, two smart buttons appear at the top of the "
"order form: :guilabel:`Projects` and :guilabel:`Tasks`."
msgstr ""
"Efter bekræftelse af salgsordren vises to smart-knapper øverst på "
"ordreformularen: :guilabel:`Projekter` og :guilabel:`Opgaver`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How the Projects and Tasks smart buttons look on a Sales Order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Sådan ser smart-knapperne Projekter og Opgaver ud på en salgsordre i Odoo "
"Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Projects` smart button is clicked, it reveals the specific "
"project related to this sales order. If the :guilabel:`Tasks` smart button "
"is clicked, it reveals the specific project task related to this sales "
"order. Both are also accessible in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der klikkes på smart-knappen :guilabel:`Projekter`, vises det "
"specifikke projekt relateret til denne salgsordre. Hvis der klikkes på smart-"
"knappen :guilabel:`Opgaver`, vises den specifikke projektopgave relateret "
"til denne salgsordre. Begge er også tilgængelige i *Projekt*-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:107
msgid ""
"In order to add time spent on a sales order, click the :guilabel:`Tasks` "
"smart button."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje tid brugt på en salgsordre skal du klikke på smart-"
"knappen :guilabel:`Opgaver`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:109
msgid ""
"On the task form, select the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. From "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab, employees can be assigned to work on the "
"project, and the time they spend working on the task can be added by the "
"employees or by the person who created the sales order."
msgstr ""
"På opgaveformularen vælges fanen :guilabel:`Timesedler`. Fra "
"fanen :guilabel:`Timesedler` kan medarbejdere tildeles til at arbejde på "
"projektet, og den tid de bruger på opgaven kan tilføjes af medarbejderne "
"selv eller af personen, der oprettede salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:113
msgid ""
"To add an employee, and the time spent working on the task, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. Then, select "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Date` and :guilabel:`Employee`. There is also the "
"option to add a brief description of the work done during this time in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` column, but it's not required."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en medarbejder og den tid der er brugt på opgaven, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` i fanen :guilabel:`Timesedler`. Vælg derefter "
"den relevante :guilabel:`Dato` og :guilabel:`Medarbejder`. Der er også "
"mulighed for at tilføje en kort beskrivelse af det udførte arbejde i denne "
"periode i kolonnen :guilabel:`Beskrivelse`, men det er ikke påkrævet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:118
msgid ""
"Lastly, enter the amount of time worked on the task in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` column, and click away to complete that line in "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Til sidst indtastes den tid der er arbejdet på opgaven i "
"kolonnen :guilabel:`Brugte timer`, og klik uden for linjen for at færdiggøre "
"den i fanen :guilabel:`Timesedler`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:122
msgid ""
"The time entered in the :guilabel:`Hours Spent` column is immediately "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` field (located near the top of "
"the task form) as a percentage, which reflects how much of the total "
"allocated work hours have been done so far."
msgstr ""
"Den tid der indtastes i kolonnen :guilabel:`Brugte timer` afspejles "
"øjeblikkeligt i feltet :guilabel:`Allokeret tid` (placeret nær toppen af "
"opgaveformularen) som en procentdel, der viser hvor meget af de samlede "
"allokerede arbejdstimer der er udført indtil nu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:126
msgid ""
"That same information is found as numerical hours in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` and :guilabel:`Remaining Hours` fields, located at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Den samme information findes som numeriske timer i "
"felterne :guilabel:`Brugte timer` og :guilabel:`Resterende timer`, placeret "
"i bunden af fanen :guilabel:`Timesedler`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"How the Timesheets tab appears on a task form in Odoo Sales and Odoo Project."
msgstr ""
"Sådan ser fanen Timesedler ud på en opgaveformular i Odoo Salg og Odoo "
"Projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:133
msgid ""
"Repeat this process for however many employees and hours have been worked on "
"the project."
msgstr ""
"Gentag denne proces for alle de medarbejdere og timer der er blevet arbejdet "
"på projektet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:136
msgid "Invoice time spent"
msgstr "Fakturer brugt tid"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:138
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary employees and time spent have been added to the "
"project task, return to the sales order to invoice the customer for those "
"hours. To do that, either click the :guilabel:`Sales Order` smart button at "
"the top of the task form, or return to the sales order via the breadcrumb "
"links, located in the upper-left of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Når alle nødvendige medarbejdere og brugt tid er blevet tilføjet til "
"projektopgaven, vend tilbage til salgsordren for at fakturere kunden for "
"disse timer. For at gøre det, klik enten på "
"smartknappen :guilabel:`Salgsordre` øverst på opgaveformularen, eller vend "
"tilbage til salgsordren via brødkrummelinkene i øverste venstre hjørne af "
"skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:143
msgid ""
"Back on the sales order form, the time that was added to the task is "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab (in the :guilabel:`Delivered` "
"column) and in the new :guilabel:`Recorded Hours` smart button at the top of "
"the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Tilbage på salgsordreformularen afspejles den tid der blev tilføjet til "
"opgaven i fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` (i kolonnen :guilabel:`Leveret`) og "
"i den nye smartknap :guilabel:`Registrerede timer` øverst på salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:147
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for time spent on the project, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and select :guilabel:`Regular invoice` "
"from the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"For at fakturere kunden for tid brugt på projektet, klik på :guilabel:`Opret "
"faktura`, og vælg :guilabel:`Almindelig faktura` fra pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Opret fakturaer`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Opret "
"fakturakladde`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:151
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, clearly showing all "
"the work that's been done in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dette viser en :guilabel:`Kundefakturakladde`, der tydeligt viser alt det "
"arbejde der er blevet udført i fanen :guilabel:`Fakturalinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:155
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice`, as that information is necessary to ensure "
"other time/material invoicing tasks are completed properly and accurately."
msgstr ""
"Vær opmærksom på kolonnen :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` "
"i :guilabel:`Kundefakturaen`, da den information er nødvendig for at sikre "
"at andre faktureringsopgaver for tid/materialer gennemføres korrekt og "
"præcist."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid "Invoice draft showing time spent on sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Fakturakladde der viser brugt tid på salgsordre i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the invoice and continue with the "
"invoicing process."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at bekræfte fakturaen og fortsætte med "
"faktureringsprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:169
msgid "Expenses configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af øvrige omkostninger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:171
msgid ""
"In order to track and invoice expenses related to a sales order, the Odoo "
"*Expenses* app **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"For at spore og fakturere omkostninger relateret til en salgsordre **skal** "
"Odoo-appen *Øvrige omkostninger* være installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:174
msgid ""
"To install the *Expenses* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`."
msgstr ""
"For at installere appen *Øvrige omkostninger*, naviger "
"til :menuselection:`Odoo hovedmenu --> Apps`. Find derefter "
"blokken :guilabel:`Øvrige omkostninger` på siden :guilabel:`Apps`, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Aktiver`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:178
msgid ""
"The page automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, "
"where the :guilabel:`Expenses` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Siden opdateres automatisk og vender tilbage til Odoos hoveddashboard, hvor "
"appen :guilabel:`Øvrige omkostninger` nu er tilgængelig."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:184
msgid "Add expenses to sales order"
msgstr "Tilføj omkostninger til salgsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:186
msgid ""
"To add an expense to a sales order, first navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. Then, from the main *Expenses* dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, which reveals a blank expense form."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje en omkostning til en salgsordre, naviger først "
"til :menuselection:`Øvrige omkostninger`-appen. Klik derefter "
"på :guilabel:`Ny` fra hovedoversigten i *Øvrige omkostninger*, hvilket viser "
"en tom omkostningsformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:189
msgid ""
"On the expense form, add a :guilabel:`Description` of the expense (e.g. "
"`Hotel Stay`, `Plane Ticket`). Next, in the :guilabel:`Category` field, "
"select the appropriate option from the drop-down menu "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, :guilabel:`Travel \\& "
"Accommodation`)."
msgstr ""
"I udgifsformularen skal du tilføje en :guilabel:`Beskrivelse` af udgiften "
"(f.eks. `Hotelophold`, `Flybillet`). Vælg derefter den relevante mulighed i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kategori` fra rullemenuen "
"(f.eks. :guilabel:`Måltider`, :guilabel:`Kilometer`, :guilabel:`Rejse & "
"indkvartering`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:194
msgid ""
"Expense categories can be added and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Udgiftskategorier kan tilføjes og ændres ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Expenses-app --> Konfiguration --> Udgiftskategorier`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:197
msgid ""
"Then, enter the total amount of the expense in the :guilabel:`Total` field, "
"as well as any :guilabel:`Included Taxes` that may apply. Next, ensure that "
"the correct :guilabel:`Employee` is selected, and designate who paid for the "
"expense in the :guilabel:`Paid By` field: the :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or the :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Indtast derefter det samlede udgiftsbeløb i feltet :guilabel:`Total`, samt "
"eventuelle :guilabel:`Inkluderede moms`, der måtte være relevante. "
"Kontrollér dernæst, at den korrekte :guilabel:`Medarbejder` er valgt, og "
"angiv, hvem der har betalt udgiften i feltet :guilabel:`Betalt "
"af`: :guilabel:`Medarbejder (til refusion)` eller :guilabel:`Virksomhed`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:202
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, select the appropriate "
"sales order from the drop-down menu. Then, select that same sales order "
"information from the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field, as well."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter den relevante salgsordre fra rullemenuen i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Kunde til viderefakturering`. Vælg derefter de samme "
"salgsordreoplysninger i feltet :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:207
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field will **only** have the "
"corresponding sales order as an option if the sales order contains a service "
"product that is billed based on *Timesheets*, *Milestones*, or *Delivered "
"Quantities*."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` vil **kun** have den tilsvarende "
"salgsordre som mulighed, hvis salgsordren indeholder et serviceprodukt, der "
"faktureres baseret på *Timesedler*, *Milepæle* eller *Leverede mængder*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to properly fill out an expense form that's attached to a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Sådan udfyldes en udgifsformular, der er knyttet til en salgsordre i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:215
msgid ""
"If there are any receipts that should be uploaded and attached to the "
"expense, click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and upload the "
"necessary documents to the expense. This is **not** required, but it may "
"affect whether or not an expense is approved."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er kvitteringer, der skal uploades og vedhæftes udgiften, skal du "
"klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Vedhæft kvittering` og uploade de nødvendige "
"dokumenter til udgiften. Dette er **ikke** påkrævet, men det kan påvirke, om "
"en udgift godkendes eller ej."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:219
msgid ""
"When all the information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Create Report` "
"to create an expense report detailing all the expense information that was "
"just entered."
msgstr ""
"Når alle oplysninger er indtastet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Opret "
"rapport` for at oprette en udgiftsrapport med alle de udgiftsoplysninger, "
"der lige er indtastet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid "How an Expense Report Summary looks in Odoo Expenses."
msgstr "Sådan ser et udgiftsrapportoverblik ud i Odoo Expenses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, there's the option to :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` for approval. Once "
"approved, the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` appears."
msgstr ""
"Derefter er der mulighed for at :guilabel:`Indsend til leder` til "
"godkendelse. Når den er godkendt, vises :guilabel:`Rapport i næste "
"lønseddel`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:229
msgid ""
"To showcase a complete flow in this example, select :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Then, the manager would click :guilabel:`Approve` to approve this "
"expense, and click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` to post this expense to "
"the accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"For at vise et komplet forløb i dette eksempel skal du "
"vælge :guilabel:`Indsend til leder`. Derefter ville lederen klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Godkend` for at godkende denne udgift og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Bogfør kladdeposter` for at bogføre denne udgift i "
"regnskabskladden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:234
msgid "Invoice expenses"
msgstr "Fakturer udgifter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:236
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for an :ref:`expense on a sales order <sales/invoicing/"
"add-expenses-sales-order>`, navigate to the related sales order, either from "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app or from the expense report in "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. From the expense report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"For at fakturere en kunde for en :ref:`udgift på en salgsordre <sales/"
"invoicing/add-expenses-sales-order>` skal du navigere til den relaterede "
"salgsordre, enten fra :menuselection:`Salg`-appen eller fra udgiftsrapporten "
"i :menuselection:`Expenses`-appen. Fra udgiftsrapporten skal du klikke på "
"den smarte knap :guilabel:`Salgsordrer` øverst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:241
msgid ""
"If the expense report was linked to the sales order, the newly-configured "
"expense now has its own line in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and can be "
"invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Hvis udgiftsrapporten blev knyttet til salgsordren, har den nyligt "
"konfigurerede udgift nu sin egen linje i fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` og "
"kan faktureres til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"An expense appearing on Order Lines tab of a Sales Order in Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"En udgift, der vises i fanen Ordrelinjer på en salgsordre i Odoo Salg-"
"applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:248
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the expense on the sales order, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"For at fakturere kunden for udgiften på salgsordren skal du klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Opret faktura`, vælge :guilabel:`Almindelig faktura` fra pop "
"op-vinduet :guilabel:`Opret fakturaer` og derefter klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Opret faktura som kladde`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:252
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` for the expense. Then, "
"the invoicing process can be completed as usual."
msgstr ""
"Dette viser en :guilabel:`Kundefaktura som kladde` for udgiften. Derefter "
"kan faktureringsprocessen fuldføres som sædvanligt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample customer invoice for an expense generated from a sales order in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Eksempel på kundefaktura for en udgift genereret fra en salgsordre i Odoo "
"Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:260
msgid "Purchase configuration"
msgstr "Indkøbskonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:262
msgid ""
"In order to invoice a customer for purchases made on a sales order, the "
"*Purchase* application **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"For at kunne fakturere en kunde for indkøb foretaget på en salgsordre "
"**skal** *Purchase*-applikationen være installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:265
msgid ""
"To install the *Purchase* application, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"For at installere *Indkøb*-applikationen skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Odoo hovedoversigt --> Apps`. På siden :guilabel:`Apps` "
"skal du finde :guilabel:`Indkøb`-appblokken og klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Aktiver`. Siden opdateres automatisk og vender tilbage til "
"Odoo-hovedoversigten, hvor :guilabel:`Indkøb`-appen nu er tilgængelig."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:273
msgid "Add purchase to sales order"
msgstr "Tilføj køb til salgsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:275
msgid ""
"To add a purchase to a sales order, a purchase order must first be created. "
"To create a purchase order, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"New` to reveal a blank purchase order form."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje et køb til en salgsordre skal der først oprettes en "
"indkøbsordre. For at oprette en indkøbsordre skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Indkøb-app --> Ny` for at få vist en tom "
"indkøbsordreformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:278
msgid ""
"First, add a :guilabel:`Vendor` to the purchase order. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`extra column options` "
"drop-down menu, represented by two horizontal lines with dots on them, "
"located to the far-right of the column headers. From that drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj først en :guilabel:`Leverandør` til indkøbsordren. Under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` skal du derefter klikke på "
"rullemenu :guilabel:`ekstra kolonneindstillinger`, repræsenteret ved to "
"vandrette linjer med prikker på, som findes yderst til højre for "
"kolonneoverskrifterne. Vælg :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to add analytic distribution column on purchase order form in Odoo "
"Purchase."
msgstr ""
"Hvordan man tilføjer kolonnen for analytisk fordeling på "
"indkøbsordreformular i Odoo Indkøb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:287
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column to the headers on "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the purchase order form, proceed to add the "
"product(s) to the purchase order. To do that, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"product`, and select the desired product from the drop-down menu. Repeat for "
"all the products to add."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have tilføjet kolonnen :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` til "
"overskrifterne på fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` i indkøbsordreformularen skal "
"du fortsætte med at tilføje produkt(er) til indkøbsordren. For at gøre det "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt` og vælge det ønskede produkt "
"fra rullemenuen. Gentag for alle produkter, der skal tilføjes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:293
msgid ""
"In order for a purchase to be properly invoiced on a sales order, the "
"product on the purchase order **must** be marked as :guilabel:`Can be "
"Expensed`, have an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`, and have the :guilabel:`At cost` option selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses` field on its product form."
msgstr ""
"For at et køb kan blive korrekt faktureret på en salgsordre, **skal** "
"produktet på indkøbsordren være markeret som :guilabel:`Kan udgiftsføres`, "
"have en :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik` indstillet til :guilabel:`Leverede "
"mængder` og have indstillingen :guilabel:`Til kostpris` valgt i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Refakturer udgifter` på produktformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"Product settings for a purchase order to be invoiced on a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Produktindstillinger for at en indkøbsordre kan faktureres på en salgsordre "
"i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:302
msgid ""
"Then, select the appropriate :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` associated "
"with the sales order to which this purchase order is related. To do that, "
"click the empty :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to reveal "
"an :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter den relevante :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling`, som er knyttet "
"til den salgsordre, som denne indkøbsordre er relateret til. For at gøre det "
"skal du klikke på det tomme felt :guilabel:`Analytisk fordeling` for at få "
"vist et pop op-vindue :guilabel:`Analytisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:306
msgid ""
"Then, from the :guilabel:`Departments` drop-down menu, select the analytic "
"distribution associated with the desired sales order to be invoiced for the "
"purchase."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter fra rullemenuen :guilabel:`Afdelinger` den analytiske "
"fordeling, der er knyttet til den ønskede salgsordre, som skal faktureres "
"for købet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to select the Analytic Distribution department from a purchase order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Hvordan man vælger Analytisk fordeling-afdeling fra en indkøbsordre i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:313
msgid ""
"Once all the information is entered in the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the "
"purchase order, confirm the order by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Receive Products` when the products have been "
"received. This creates a receipt form."
msgstr ""
"Når alle oplysninger er indtastet på fanen :guilabel:`Produkter` i "
"indkøbsordren, skal du bekræfte ordren ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft "
"ordre`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Modtag produkter`, når produkterne er "
"modtaget. Dette opretter en modtagelsesformular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:318
msgid ""
"If any serial/lot numbers must be entered before validating the receipt of "
"products, then on the receipt form, click the :guilabel:`details` icon "
"represented by four horizontal lines located to the far-right of the product "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der skal indtastes serie-/lotnumre, før modtagelsen af produkter "
"valideres, skal du på modtagelsesformularen klikke på "
"ikonet :guilabel:`detaljer`, repræsenteret ved fire vandrette linjer, som "
"findes yderst til højre for produktlinjen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:322
msgid ""
"This reveals a :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` tab, in which the "
"necessary :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number(s)` and :guilabel:`Done` quantity can "
"be added. When ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the data."
msgstr ""
"Dette viser en fane :guilabel:`Detaljerede operationer`, hvor de "
"nødvendige :guilabel:`Lot-/serienumre` og mængden :guilabel:`Udført` kan "
"tilføjes. Når du er klar, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at "
"bekræfte dataene."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:326
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the purchase order."
msgstr "Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Valider` for at validere indkøbsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:328
msgid ""
"Next, return to the purchase order, via the breadcrumb links at the top of "
"the page, and click :guilabel:`Create Bill` to create a vendor bill that can "
"be invoiced to the customer on the attached sales order."
msgstr ""
"Gå derefter tilbage til indkøbsordren via brødkrummelinkene øverst på siden, "
"og klik på :guilabel:`Opret faktura` for at oprette en leverandørfaktura, "
"som kan faktureres til kunden på den tilknyttede salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Vendor bill draft for a purchase order to be invoiced to a customer in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kladde til leverandørfaktura for en indkøbsordre, der skal faktureres til en "
"kunde i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:337
msgid ""
"Make sure to enter a :guilabel:`Bill Date` on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill "
"Draft` before confirming. If a :guilabel:`Bill Date` is *not* entered, an "
"error window appears, requesting that information to be entered before "
"confirmation can occur."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for at indtaste en :guilabel:`Fakturadato` "
"på :guilabel:`Leverandørfakturakladde`, før du bekræfter. Hvis der *ikke* "
"indtastes en :guilabel:`Fakturadato`, vises et fejlvindue, der anmoder om, "
"at disse oplysninger indtastes, før bekræftelse kan finde sted."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:341
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the vendor bill, which is then "
"automatically added to the sales order, where it can be invoiced directly to "
"the customer attached to it."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Bekræft` for at bekræfte leverandørfakturaen, "
"som derefter automatisk tilføjes til salgsordren, hvor den kan faktureres "
"direkte til den kunde, der er knyttet til den."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:345
msgid "Invoice purchase"
msgstr "Fakturer køb"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:347
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for a purchase on a sales order, first :ref:`add the "
"purchase to the sales order <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-sales-order>`, "
"then navigate to the desired sales order in the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr ""
"For at fakturere en kunde for et køb på en salgsordre, skal du "
"først :ref:`tilføje købet til salgsordren <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-"
"sales-order>`, og derefter navigere til den ønskede salgsordre "
"i :menuselection:`Salg`-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:351
msgid ""
"On the sales order that was attached to the purchase order, the purchased "
"product now has its own product line under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, "
"and it is ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"På salgsordren, der var tilknyttet indkøbsordren, har det købte produkt nu "
"sin egen produktlinje under fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`, og det er klar "
"til at blive faktureret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Purchase order product on sales order to be invoiced to customer via Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Indkøbsordreprodukt på salgsordre, der skal faktureres til kunde via Odoo "
"Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:358
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the purchase, simply click :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"For at fakturere kunden for købet skal du blot klikke på :guilabel:`Opret "
"faktura`, vælge :guilabel:`Almindelig faktura` fra pop op-"
"vinduet :guilabel:`Opret fakturaer`, og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Opret "
"kladdefaktura`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:362
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` with the newly-added "
"purchase order product in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dette viser en :guilabel:`Kundefakturakladde` med det nyligt tilføjede "
"indkøbsordreprodukt under fanen :guilabel:`Fakturalinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer invoice draft with purchase product attached to sales order in Odoo."
msgstr "Kundefakturakladde med købsprodukt tilknyttet salgsordre i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:369
msgid ""
"To complete the invoicing process, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the "
"invoice, and then click :guilabel:`Register Payment` in "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"For at fuldføre faktureringsprocessen skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Bekræft` "
"for at bekræfte fakturaen og derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Registrer "
"betaling` i pop op-formularen :guilabel:`Registrer betaling`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector.rst:5
msgid "Lazada Connector"
msgstr "Lazada Connector"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:3
msgid "Lazada Connector features"
msgstr "Lazada Connector-funktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Lazada Connector** synchronizes orders, products, and inventory "
"between Lazada and Odoo, streamlining your operations across Southeast "
"Asia's marketplaces. It reduces manual data entry between systems and "
"enhances order management, enabling efficient tracking of Lazada sales "
"within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Lazada Connector** synkroniserer ordrer, produkter og lager mellem Lazada "
"og Odoo, hvilket strømliner dine operationer på tværs af Sydøstasiens "
"markedspladser. Det reducerer manuel dataindtastning mellem systemer og "
"forbedrer ordrehåndtering, hvilket muliggør effektiv sporing af Lazada-salg "
"i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:13
