msgstr ":guilabel:`Salgspris`: indtast top-up-beløbet"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:38
msgid ""
"In order to have eWallet top-ups of different amounts, create multiple top-"
