msgstr ""
"Konfigurer og brug tilbudsskabeloner til at sende skræddersyede tilbud "
"hurtigere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:52
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:3
msgid "Optional products"
msgstr "Valgfrie produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:52
msgid "Offer useful and related products to customers to increase sales."
msgstr "Tilbyd nyttige og relaterede produkter til kunder for at øge salget."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:3
msgid "Online signatures for order confirmations"
msgstr "Onlineunderskrifter til ordrebekræftelser"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:57
msgid ""
"Customers have the ability to confirm orders via online signatures, directly "
"on sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Kunder har mulighed for at bekræfte ordrer via online-signaturer direkte på "
"salgsordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:62
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:3
msgid "Online payment order confirmation"
msgstr "Bekræftelse af ordre ved onlinebetaling"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:62
msgid ""
"Customers have the ability to confirm orders via online payment, directly on "
"sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Kunder har mulighed for at bekræfte ordrer via online-betaling direkte på "
"salgsordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:67
msgid "Quotation Deadlines"
msgstr "Tilbudsfrister"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:67
msgid ""
"Set deadlines on quotations to encourage customers to act in a timely manner "
"when closing business deals."
msgstr ""
"Indstil frister på tilbud for at tilskynde kunder til at handle rettidigt "
"ved afslutning af forretningsaftaler."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:73
msgid "Deliver orders and invoices to different addresses"
msgstr "Lever ordrer og fakturaer til forskellige adresser"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:73
msgid ""
"Specify separate customer delivery and invoicing addresses on quotations."
msgstr ""
"Angiv separate kunde leveringsadresser og faktureringsadresser på tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:78
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:3
msgid "Product variants on quotations and sales orders"
msgstr "Produktvarianter på tilbud og salgsordrer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:78
msgid ""
"Add product variants to sales orders to provide additional options for "
"single products."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj produktvarianter til salgsordrer for at give yderligere muligheder "
"for enkelte produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:83
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:6
msgid "PDF quote builder"
msgstr "PDF-tilbudsgenerator"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:83
msgid ""
"Add custom PDF files to quotations to elevate the document's headers and "
"designs."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj tilpassede PDF-filer til tilbud for at forbedre dokumentets "
"sidehoveder og design."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:89
msgid "Sales quotations in business deals"
msgstr "Salgstilbud i forretningsaftaler"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:91
msgid ""
"Sales quotations serve as a key step in the sales process, bridging the gap "
"between a customer's initial inquiry about goods and services and the final "
"contractual agreement for payment and delivery. The quotation also provides "
"transparency in pricing, helping both parties negotiate and finalize the "
"terms before making a commitment."
msgstr ""
"Salgstilbud fungerer som et vigtigt trin i salgsprocessen og bygger bro "
"mellem en kundes indledende forespørgsel om varer og tjenester og den "
"endelige kontraktlige aftale om betaling og levering. Tilbuddet giver også "
"gennemsigtighed i prissætningen og hjælper begge parter med at forhandle og "
"fastlægge vilkårene, før de indgår en forpligtelse."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:96
msgid ""
"Sales quotations play a crucial role in business transactions by defining "
"the scope and cost of what is being sold to the end-customer; setting clear "
"expectations on pricing, delivery, tax, and payment terms; and providing a "
"documented stage where the business deal can be negotiated before agreed "
"upon."
msgstr ""
"Salgstilbud spiller en afgørende rolle i forretningstransaktioner ved at "
"definere omfanget og omkostningerne for det, der sælges til slutkunden, "
"fastlægge klare forventninger til prissætning, levering, skat og "
"betalingsvilkår samt tilvejebringe en dokumenteret fase, hvor "
"forretningsaftalen kan forhandles, før den accepteres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:102
msgid "Key components of a sales quotation"
msgstr "Nøglekomponenter i et salgstilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:104
msgid "A well-structured sales quotation comprises the following:"
msgstr "Et velstruktureret salgstilbud omfatter følgende:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:106
msgid ""
"Quotation number and date: A unique identifier for tracking and reference, "
"as well as the :doc:`dates of issue and expiration <sales_quotations/"
"deadline>`. In Odoo **Sales** app, the quotation number is assigned under a "
"standard naming convention once it is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Tilbudsnummer og -dato: En unik identifikator til sporing og reference "
"samt :doc:`udstedelses- og udløbsdatoer <sales_quotations/deadline>`. I Odoo-"
"appen **Salg** tildeles tilbudsnummeret under en standard "
"navngivningskonvention, når det er bekræftet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:109
msgid ""
"Customer information: Customer name and contact information, as well "
"as :doc:`invoicing and delivery address <sales_quotations/"
"different_addresses>`."
msgstr ""
"Kundeoplysninger: Kundenavn og kontaktoplysninger samt :doc:`fakturerings- "
"og leveringsadresse <sales_quotations/different_addresses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:111
msgid ""
"Products and services: Itemized listing of items to be purchased, including "
"quantity, specifications (as needed), and unit price."
msgstr ""
"Produkter og tjenester: Specificeret liste over varer, der skal købes, "
"inklusive antal, specifikationer (efter behov) og enhedspris."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:113
msgid ""
"Payment terms and :doc:`pricelists <products_prices/prices/pricing>`: "
"Configured agreements and rules for the pricing and payment of this "
"particular sales quotation."
msgstr ""
"Betalingsvilkår og :doc:`prislister <products_prices/prices/pricing>`: "
"Konfigurerede aftaler og regler for prissætning og betaling af dette særlige "
"salgstilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:115
msgid ""
"Special pricing: Optional :doc:`discounts and promotional pricing "
"<products_prices/prices/pricing>` to update and/or modify individual product "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"Særlig prissætning: Valgfri :doc:`rabatter og kampagnepriser "
"<products_prices/prices/pricing>` til opdatering og/eller ændring af "
"individuelle produktlinjer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:117
msgid ""
"Total cost and currency: Summary totals of product or service and shipping "
"prices, including relevant taxes."
msgstr ""
"Samlet omkostning og valuta: Samlede totaler for produkt- eller "
"tjenestepriser og forsendelse, inklusive relevante skatter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:120
msgid ""
"In Odoo's **Sales** app, quotations can include additional details and "
"configurations that add more detail and information, such as :doc:`quotation "
"templates <sales_quotations/quote_template>`, :doc:`subscription plans "
"<../../sales/subscriptions>`, and :doc:`sales team referrer name "
"<sales_quotations/create_quotations>`."
msgstr ""
"I Odoós **Salg**-app kan tilbud indeholde yderligere detaljer og "
"konfigurationer, der tilføjer mere detalje og information, "
"såsom :doc:`tilbudsskabeloner <sales_quotations/"
"quote_template>`, :doc:`abonnementsplaner <../../sales/subscriptions>` "
"og :doc:`salgsteamets henvisernavn <sales_quotations/create_quotations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations.rst:None
msgid "Unconfirmed sales quotation in Odoo **Sales** app."
msgstr "Ubekræftet salgstilbud i Odoo-appen **Salg**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo **Sales**, quotations can be created and sent to customers. Once a "
"quotation has been confirmed, it officially turns into a *sales order*, "
"which can then be invoiced and paid for."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo **Salg** kan tilbud oprettes og sendes til kunder. Når et tilbud er "
"blevet bekræftet, bliver det officielt til en *salgsordre*, som derefter kan "
"faktureres og betales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:11
msgid "Quotation settings"
msgstr "Tilbudsindstillinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:13
msgid ""
"To access these setting options, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll to the :guilabel:`Quotations & "
"Orders` section."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til disse indstillingsmuligheder skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger` og rulle "
"ned til afsnittet :guilabel:`Tilbud & ordrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid "The Quotations and Orders section on the Odoo Sales app Settings page."
msgstr "Afsnittet Tilbud og Ordrer på indstillingssiden for Odoo Salg-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:20
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotation Templates`: Enable this option to create quotation "
"templates featuring standard product offers, which are then selectable on "
"quotation forms. When this checkbox is ticked, an additional "
"field, :guilabel:`Default Template`, appears, along with a link to "
"the :guilabel:`Quotation Templates` page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilbudsskabeloner`: Aktivér denne mulighed for at oprette "
"tilbudsskabeloner med standardprodukttilbud, som derefter kan vælges på "
"tilbudsformularer. Når dette afkrydsningsfelt er markeret, vises et ekstra "
"felt, :guilabel:`Standardskabelon`, sammen med et link til "
"siden :guilabel:`Tilbudsskabeloner`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:24
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online Signature`: Request an online signature to confirm orders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Onlineunderskrift`: Anmod om en onlineunderskrift for at bekræfte "
"ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:25
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online Payment`: Request an online prepayment from customers to "
"confirm orders. Request a full or partial payment (via down payment). When "
"this checkbox is ticked, an additional field, :guilabel:`Prepayment amount "
"(%)`, appears. There is also a link to the :guilabel:`Payment Providers` "
"page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Onlinebetaling`: Anmod om en online forudbetaling fra kunder for "
"at bekræfte ordrer. Anmod om fuld eller delvis betaling (via depositum). Når "
"dette afkrydsningsfelt er markeret, vises et ekstra "
"felt, :guilabel:`Forudbetalingsbeløb (%)`. Der er også et link til "
"siden :guilabel:`Betalingsudbydere`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Quotation Validity`: Determine a set amount "
"(in :guilabel:`days`) that quotations can remain valid for."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardtilbudsgyldighed`: Fastlæg et bestemt beløb "
"(i :guilabel:`dage`), som tilbud kan forblive gyldige i."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:31
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Recurrence`: Select a default period from the drop-down "
"menu to use as a recurrence period for a new quotation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Standardgentagelse`: Vælg en standardperiode fra rullemenuen til "
"brug som gentagelsesperiode for et nyt tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sale Warnings`: Get warning messages about orders that include "
"specific products or customers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salgsadvarsler`: Få advarselsmeddelelser om ordrer, der "
"inkluderer bestemte produkter eller kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PDF Quote builder`: Customize the look of quotations with header "
"pages, product descriptions, footer pages, and more."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PDF-tilbudsbygger`: Tilpas udseendet af tilbud med sidehoved, "
"produktbeskrivelser, sidefødder og mere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Lock Confirmed Sales`: Ensure no further edits can be made to "
"confirmed orders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lås bekræftede salg`: Sikr, at der ikke kan foretages yderligere "
"redigeringer af bekræftede ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:38
msgid ":guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice`: Send pro-forma invoices to customers."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Proformafaktura`: Send proformafakturaer til kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:40
msgid ""
"To activate any of these settings, tick the checkbox beside the desired "
"option(s). Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere nogen af disse indstillinger skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden af den ønskede mulighed/de ønskede muligheder. "
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:44
msgid "Quotations dashboard"
msgstr "Tilbudsoversigt"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:46
msgid ""
"The *Quotations* dashboard is the page that appears when "
"the :menuselection:`Sales app` is opened."
msgstr ""
"Oversigten *Tilbud* er den side, der vises, når :menuselection:`Salg-appen` "
"åbnes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:48
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Quotations` dashboard displays all quotations in "
"the database related to the current user, as indicated by the "
"default :guilabel:`My Quotations` filter present in the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Som standard viser :guilabel:`Tilbud`-oversigten alle tilbud i databasen "
"relateret til den aktuelle bruger, som angivet af "
"standardfilteret :guilabel:`Mine tilbud`, der er til stede i søgefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid "The Quotations dashboard present in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Tilbudsoversigten i Odoo Salg-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:57
msgid ""
"To view *all* quotations in the database, remove the :guilabel:`My "
"Quotations` filter from the search bar."
msgstr ""
"For at se *alle* tilbud i databasen skal du fjerne filteret :guilabel:`Mine "
"tilbud` fra søgefeltet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:60
msgid ""
"Quotations on this page appear in a default list view, but can also be "
"viewed in a :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`Kanban` view, :icon:`fa-"
"calendar` :guilabel:`Calendar`, :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` "
"table, :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`Graph`, or :icon:`fa-clock-"
"o` :guilabel:`Activity` view."
msgstr ""
"Tilbud på denne side vises som standard i listevisning, men kan også ses i "
"en :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`Kanban`-visning, :icon:`fa-"
"calendar` :guilabel:`Kalender`, :icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot`-"
"tabel, :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`Graf` eller :icon:`fa-clock-"
"o` :guilabel:`Aktivitet`-visning."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:65
msgid ""
"To view and/or modify any listed quotation from the :guilabel:`Quotations` "
"dashboard, click on the desired quotation line from the list, and Odoo "
"reveals the specific form for that selected quotation."
msgstr ""
"For at se og/eller ændre et hvilket som helst tilbud fra :guilabel:`Tilbud`-"
"oversigten skal du klikke på den ønskede tilbudslinje fra listen, så åbner "
"Odoo den specifikke formular for det valgte tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:72
msgid "Create quotation"
msgstr "Opret tilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:74
msgid ""
"To create a quotation, open the :menuselection:`Sales app`, and click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button, located in the upper-left corner of the "
"main :guilabel:`Quotations` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et tilbud skal du åbne :menuselection:`Salg-appen` og klikke "
"på knappen :guilabel:`Ny`, der findes i øverste venstre hjørne af "
"hovedoversigten :guilabel:`Tilbud`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:78
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`New` button is **only** present if the :guilabel:`Quotations` "
"dashboard is in list or Kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Ny` er **kun** til stede, hvis :guilabel:`Tilbud` "
"dashboardet er i liste- eller Kanban-visning."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:81
msgid ""
"Clicking the :guilabel:`New` button reveals a blank quotation form, with "
"various fields and tabs to configure."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Ny` for at åbne en tom tilbudsformular med "
"forskellige felter og faner, der kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid "A typical quotation form in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "En typisk tilbudsformular i Odoo Salg-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:88
msgid ""
"Begin by entering the customer's name in the :guilabel:`Customer` field at "
"the top of the form. This is a **required** field."
msgstr ""
"Begynd med at indtaste kundens navn i feltet :guilabel:`Kunde` øverst i "
"formularen. Dette er et **påkrævet** felt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:91
msgid ""
"If the customer's information is already in the database, "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Address` and :guilabel:`Delivery Address` fields auto-"
"populate with the saved information for those respective fields, based on "
"the data from that customer's contact record (found in the **Contacts** "
"application)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kundens oplysninger allerede findes i databasen, udfyldes "
"felterne :guilabel:`Fakturaadresse` og :guilabel:`Leveringsadresse` "
"automatisk med de gemte oplysninger for disse respektive felter baseret på "
"data fra kundens kontaktpost (findes i **Adressebog**-applikationen)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:96
msgid ""
"If the customer was referred by another customer or contact, enter their "
"name in the :guilabel:`Referrer` field."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kunden blev henvist af en anden kunde eller kontakt, skal du indtaste "
"deres navn i feltet :guilabel:`Henviser`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:99
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Referrer` is selected, a new field, :guilabel:`Commission "
"Plan` appears, in which a commission can be selected from the drop-down "
"menu. This commission is rewarded to the contact selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Referrer` field."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en :guilabel:`Henviser` er valgt, vises et nyt "
"felt, :guilabel:`Kommissionsplan`, hvor en kommission kan vælges fra "
"rullemenuen. Denne kommission tildeles den kontakt, der er valgt i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Henviser`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:103
msgid ""
"Next, if they have not already been auto-populated with the customer's "
"information, enter the appropriate addresses in the :guilabel:`Invoice "
"Address` and :guilabel:`Delivery Address` fields. Both of these fields are "
"**required**."
msgstr ""
"Hvis de ikke allerede er blevet automatisk udfyldt med kundens oplysninger, "
"skal du derefter indtaste de relevante adresser i "
"felterne :guilabel:`Fakturaadresse` og :guilabel:`Leveringsadresse`. Begge "
"disse felter er **påkrævede**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:107
msgid ""
"Then, if desired, choose a :guilabel:`Quotation Template` from the drop-down "
"field to apply to this quotation. It should be noted that some additional "
"fields may appear, depending on the template selected."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter eventuelt en :guilabel:`Tilbudsskabelon` fra rullefeltet, der "
"skal anvendes på dette tilbud. Det skal bemærkes, at nogle yderligere felter "
"kan vises afhængigt af den valgte skabelon."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:111
msgid ""
"The default date that appears in the :guilabel:`Expiration` field is based "
"on the number configured in the :ref:`Default Quotation Validity setting "
"<sales/quotation-settings>` (in :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration "
"--> Settings`)."
msgstr ""
"Standarddatoen, der vises i feltet :guilabel:`Udløb`, er baseret på det "
"antal, der er konfigureret i :ref:`Standard gyldighed af tilbud-"
"indstillingen <sales/quotation-settings>` (i :menuselection:`Salg app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:116
msgid ""
"When using a quotation template, the date in the :guilabel:`Expiration` "
"field is based off the :guilabel:`Quotation Validity` figure on the template "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Når du bruger en tilbudsskabelon, er datoen i feltet :guilabel:`Udløb` "
"baseret på tallet :guilabel:`Tilbudsgyldighed` på skabelonformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:119
msgid ""
"If the quotation is for a recurring product or subscription, select the "
"desired :guilabel:`Recurring Plan` from that specific drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Hvis tilbuddet er til et tilbagevendende produkt eller abonnement, skal du "
"vælge den ønskede :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende plan` fra den specifikke "
"rullemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:122
msgid ""
"If desired, select a specific :guilabel:`Pricelist` to be applied to this "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
"Vælg eventuelt en bestemt :guilabel:`Prisliste`, der skal anvendes på dette "
"tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:124
msgid ""
"Lastly, select any specific :guilabel:`Payment Terms` to be used for this "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
"Vælg til sidst eventuelle specifikke :guilabel:`Betalingsbetingelser`, der "
"skal bruges til dette tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:127
msgid "Order Lines tab"
msgstr "Fanen Ordrelinjer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:129
msgid "The first tab on the quotation form is the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr "Den første fane på tilbudsformularen er fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:131
msgid ""
"In this tab, select products, and quantities of those products, to add them "
"to the quotation."
msgstr ""
"I denne fane skal du vælge produkter og mængder af disse produkter for at "
"føje dem til tilbuddet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:133
msgid "There are two ways to add products to the quotation from this tab."
msgstr "Der er to måder at tilføje produkter til tilbuddet fra denne fane."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:135
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a product`, select the desired item from "
"the :guilabel:`Product` drop-down field, and proceed to adjust the quantity "
"of that selected product, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt`, vælg det ønskede element fra "
"rullefeltet :guilabel:`Produkt`, og juster om nødvendigt mængden af det "
"valgte produkt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:138
msgid ""
"Or, click :guilabel:`Catalog` to reveal a separate page, showcasing every "
"item (and every potential product variant) in an organized catalog display, "
"with items organizable by :guilabel:`Product Category` "
"and :guilabel:`Attributes`."
msgstr ""
"Eller klik på :guilabel:`Katalog` for at åbne en separat side, der viser "
"hvert element (og hver potentiel produktvariant) i en organiseret "
"katalogvisning med elementer, der kan organiseres "
"efter :guilabel:`Produktkategori` og :guilabel:`Attributter`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid ""
"A product catalog accessible via a quotation in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr ""
"Et produktkatalog tilgængeligt via et tilbud i Odoo Salg-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:146
msgid ""
"From here, simply locate the desired items, click the :icon:`fa-shopping-"
"cart` :guilabel:`Add` button on the product card, and adjust the quantity, "
"if needed. When complete, click the :guilabel:`Back to Quotation` button in "
"the upper-left corner to return to the quotation, where the newly-selected "
"catalog items can be found in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Herfra skal du blot finde de ønskede varer, klikke på :icon:`fa-shopping-"
"cart` :guilabel:`Tilføj` knappen på produktkortet og justere antallet, hvis "
"det er nødvendigt. Når det er færdigt, klik på :guilabel:`Tilbage til "
"tilbud` knappen i øverste venstre hjørne for at vende tilbage til tilbuddet, "
"hvor de nyvalgte katalogvarer kan findes under fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:151
msgid ""
"If multiple items should be presented in a more organized way on the "
"quotation, click :guilabel:`Add a section`, enter a name for the section, "
"and drag-and-drop that section heading in the desired location amongst the "
"items in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab. The section heading appears in "
"bold and a sub-total for all products in a section is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Hvis flere varer skal præsenteres på en mere organiseret måde på tilbuddet, "
"skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en sektion`, indtaste et navn til "
"sektionen og trække og slippe den sektionsoverskrift på den ønskede "
"placering blandt varerne i fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`. "
"Sektionsoverskriften vises med fed skrift, og en subtotal for alle produkter "
"i en sektion vises."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:156
msgid ""
"If needed, click :guilabel:`Add a note` beneath a certain product line to "
"add a custom note about that specific product. The note appears in italics. "
"Then, if needed, proceed to drag-and-drop the note beneath the desired "
"product line."
msgstr ""
"Hvis det er nødvendigt, klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj en note` under en bestemt "
"produktlinje for at tilføje en tilpasset note om det specifikke produkt. "
"Noten vises med kursiv. Hvis det er nødvendigt, kan du fortsætte med at "
"trække og slippe noten under den ønskede produktlinje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:160
msgid ""
"Beneath the product lines, there are buttons that can be clicked to apply "
"any of the following: :guilabel:`Coupon "
"Code`, :guilabel:`Promotions`, :guilabel:`Discount`, and/or :guilabel:`Add "
"shipping`."
msgstr ""
"Under produktlinjerne er der knapper, der kan klikkes for at anvende en af "
"følgende: :guilabel:`Kuponkode`, :guilabel:`Kampagner`, :guilabel:`Rabat` og/"
"eller :guilabel:`Tilføj levering`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:165
msgid ":doc:`../products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products_prices/ewallets_giftcards`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:166
msgid ":doc:`../products_prices/loyalty_discount`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products_prices/loyalty_discount`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:167
msgid ":doc:`../products_prices/prices/pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products_prices/prices/pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:168
msgid ":doc:`../../../essentials/product_catalog`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../essentials/product_catalog`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:171
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:148
msgid "Optional Products tab"
msgstr "Fanen Valgfrie produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:173
msgid ""
"Open the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab to select related products that "
"can be presented to the customer, which may result in an increased sale."
msgstr ""
"Åbn fanen :guilabel:`Valgfrie produkter` for at vælge relaterede produkter, "
"der kan præsenteres for kunden, hvilket kan resultere i øget salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:176
msgid ""
"For example, if the customer wants to buy a car, an optional product that "
"could be offered is a *Trailer Hitch*."
msgstr ""
"For eksempel, hvis kunden ønsker at købe en bil, kunne et valgfrit produkt, "
"der kunne tilbydes, være en *Anhængertræk*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:180
msgid ":doc:`optional_products`"
msgstr ":doc:`optional_products`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:183
msgid "Other Info tab"
msgstr "Fanen Øvrige oplysninger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:185
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, there are various quotation-related "
"configurations separated into four different "
"sections: :guilabel:`Sales`, :guilabel:`Delivery`, :guilabel:`Invoicing`, "
"and :guilabel:`Tracking`."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Øvrige oplysninger` er der forskellige tilbudsrelaterede "
"konfigurationer opdelt i fire forskellige "
"sektioner: :guilabel:`Salg`, :guilabel:`Levering`, :guilabel:`Fakturering` "
"og :guilabel:`Sporing`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:190
msgid ""
"Some fields **only** appear if specific settings and options have been "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Nogle felter vises **kun**, hvis specifikke indstillinger og muligheder er "
"blevet konfigureret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:193
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:92
msgid "Sales section"
msgstr "Sektionen Salg"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:195
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Sales` section of the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, there "
"are sales specific fields that can be configured."
msgstr ""
"I sektionen :guilabel:`Salg` under fanen :guilabel:`Øvrige oplysninger` er "
"der salgsspecifikke felter, der kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Sales section of the Other Info tab of a quotation form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Sektionen Salg i fanen Øvrige oplysninger på en tilbudsformular i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:202
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: Assign a salesperson from the drop-down menu to be "
"associated with this quotation. The user who originally created the "
"quotation is selected in this field, by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sælger`: Tildel en sælger fra rullemenuen til at være tilknyttet "
"dette tilbud. Brugeren, der oprindeligt oprettede tilbuddet, er valgt i "
"dette felt som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:204
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: Assign a specific sales team to this quotation. If "
"the selected :guilabel:`Salesperson` is a member of a sales team, that team "
"is auto-populated in the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salgsteam`: Tildel et specifikt salgsteam til dette tilbud. Hvis "
"den valgte :guilabel:`Sælger` er medlem af et salgsteam, vil dette team "
"automatisk blive udfyldt i feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: Select a company from the drop-down menu this quotation "
"should be associated with. This field only appears when working in a multi-"
"company environment."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virksomhed`: Vælg en virksomhed fra rullemenuen, som dette tilbud "
"skal være tilknyttet. Dette felt vises kun, når du arbejder i et miljø med "
"flere virksomheder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:208
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online signature`: Tick this checkbox to request an online "
"signature from the customer to confirm the order. This field only appears if "
"the *Online Signature* setting has been enabled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Online signatur`: Markér dette afkrydsningsfelt for at anmode om "
"en online signatur fra kunden for at bekræfte ordren. Dette felt vises kun, "
"hvis indstillingen *Online signatur* er blevet aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Online payment`: Tick this checkbox, and enter a desired "
"percentage in the adjacent field, to request an online payment from the "
"customer (for that designated percentage of the total amount) to confirm the "
"order. This field only appears if the *Online Payment* setting has been "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Online betaling`: Markér dette afkrydsningsfelt, og indtast en "
"ønsket procentdel i det tilstødende felt, for at anmode om en online "
"betaling fra kunden (for den angivne procentdel af det samlede beløb) for at "
"bekræfte ordren. Dette felt vises kun, hvis indstillingen *Online betaling* "
"er blevet aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:214
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Reference`: Enter a custom reference ID for this "
"customer. The entered reference ID can contain letters, numbers, or a mix of "
"both."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kundereference`: Indtast et brugerdefineret reference-ID for "
"denne kunde. Det indtastede reference-ID kan indeholde bogstaver, tal eller "
"en blanding af begge."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:216
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Add specific tags to the quotation for added organization "
"and enhanced searchability in the Odoo **Sales** application. Multiple tags "
"can be added, if necessary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Tilføj specifikke tags til tilbuddet for bedre "
"organisering og forbedret søgemulighed i Odoo **Salg**-applikationen. Flere "
"tags kan tilføjes, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:220
msgid "Delivery section"
msgstr "Leveringsafsnit"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:222
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Delivery` section of the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, there "
"are delivery-specific fields that can be configured."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Levering` på fanen :guilabel:`Anden info` er der "
"leveringsspecifikke felter, der kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Delivery section of the Other Info tab of a quotation form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Leveringsafsnittet på fanen Anden info i en tilbudsformular i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:229
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Weight`: Displays the weight of the items being shipped. "
"This field is not modifiable. Product weight is configured on individual "
"product forms."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forsendelsesvægt`: Viser vægten af de varer, der sendes. Dette "
"felt kan ikke ændres. Produktvægt konfigureres på individuelle "
"produktformularer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:231
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Incoterm`: Select an Incoterm (International Commerical Term) to "
"use as predefined commerical terms for international transactions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Incoterm`: Vælg en Incoterm (International Commercial Term) til "
"brug som foruddefinerede kommercielle vilkår for internationale "
"transaktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:233
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Incoterm Location`: If an Incoterm is being used, enter the "
"international location in this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Incoterm-lokation`: Hvis en Incoterm bruges, skal du indtaste den "
"internationale lokation i dette felt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:235
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Policy`: Select a desired shipping policy from the drop-"
"down menu. If all products are delivered at once, the delivery order is "
"scheduled, based on the greatest product lead time. Otherwise, it is based "
"on the shortest lead time. The available options are: :guilabel:`As soon as "
"possible` or :guilabel:`When all products are ready`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forsendelsespolitik`: Vælg en ønsket forsendelsespolitik fra "
"rullemenuen. Hvis alle produkter leveres på én gang, planlægges "
"leveringsordren baseret på den længste produktleveringstid. Ellers er den "
"baseret på den korteste leveringstid. De tilgængelige muligheder "
"er: :guilabel:`Så hurtigt som muligt` eller :guilabel:`Når alle produkter er "
"klar`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Date`: Click into the empty field to reveal a calendar "
"popover, from which a customer delivery date can be selected. If no custom "
"date is required, refer to the :guilabel:`Expected` date listed to the right "
"of that field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Leveringsdato`: Klik i det tomme felt for at få vist en "
"kalenderpopover, hvorfra en kundeleveringsdato kan vælges. Hvis der ikke "
"kræves en brugerdefineret dato, se den :guilabel:`Forventet` dato angivet "
"til højre for feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:244
msgid "Invoicing section"
msgstr "Faktureringsafsnit"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:246
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section of the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, "
"there are invoicing specific fields that can be configured."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Fakturering` på fanen :guilabel:`Anden info` er der "
"faktureringsspecifikke felter, der kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Invoicing section of the Other Info tab of a quotation form in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Faktureringsafsnittet på fanen Anden info i en tilbudsformular i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:253
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Fiscal Position`: Select a fiscal position to be used to adapt "
"taxes and accounts for particular customers or sales orders/invoices. The "
"default value comes from the customer. If a selection is made in this field, "
"an :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Update Taxes` clickable link and icon "
"appear. When clicked, the taxes for this partiuclar customer and quotation "
"are updated. A confirmation window appears, as well."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skatteposition`: Vælg en skatteposition, der skal bruges til at "
"tilpasse skatter og konti for bestemte kunder eller salgsordrer/fakturaer. "
"Standardværdien kommer fra kunden. Hvis der foretages et valg i dette felt, "
"vises et :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Opdater skatter` klikbart link og "
"ikon. Når der klikkes, opdateres skatterne for denne bestemte kunde og dette "
"tilbud. Et bekræftelsesvindue vises også."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:258
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Analytic Account`: Select an analytic account to apply to this "
"customer/quotation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Omkostningssted`: Vælg et omkostningssted, der skal anvendes på "
"denne kunde/dette tilbud."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:261
msgid "Tracking section"
msgstr "Sporingsafsnit"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:263
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Tracking` section of the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, there "
"are tracking specific fields that can be configured."
msgstr ""
"I afsnittet :guilabel:`Sporing` på fanen :guilabel:`Anden info` er der "
"sporingsspecifikke felter, der kan konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Tracking section of the Other Info tab of a quotation form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Sporingsafsnittet på fanen Anden info i en tilbudsformular i Odoo Salg."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:270
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Source Document`: Enter the reference of the document that "
"generated the quotation/sales order, if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kildedokument`: Indtast referencen til det dokument, der "
"genererede tilbuddet/salgsordren, hvis relevant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:272
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Opportunity`: Select the specific opportunity (from the **CRM** "
"app) related to this quotation, if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mulighed`: Vælg den specifikke mulighed (fra **CRM**-appen) "
"relateret til dette tilbud, hvis relevant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:274
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Campaign`: Select the marketing campaign related to this "
"quotation, if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kampagne`: Vælg marketingkampagnen relateret til dette tilbud, "
"hvis relevant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:275
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Medium`: Select the method by which this quotation originated "
"(e.g. *Email*), if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Medie`: Vælg metoden, hvorved dette tilbud opstod (f.eks. *E-"
"mail*), hvis relevant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:277
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Source`: Select the source of the link used to generate this "
"quotation (e.g. *Facebook*), if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kilde`: Vælg kilden til det link, der blev brugt til at generere "
"dette tilbud (f.eks. *Facebook*), hvis relevant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:281
msgid ":doc:`../../../websites/website/reporting/link_tracker`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../websites/website/reporting/link_tracker`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:284
msgid "Notes tab"
msgstr "Karta poznámek"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:286
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Notes` tab of the quotation form, enter any specific "
"internal notes about the quotation and/or customer, if desired."
msgstr ""
"I fanen :guilabel:`Noter` på tilbudsformularen kan du indtaste eventuelle "
"specifikke interne noter om tilbuddet og/eller kunden, hvis ønsket."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:292
msgid "Sending and confirming quotations"
msgstr "Afsendelse og bekræftelse af tilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:294
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary fields and tabs have been configured, it is time to "
"send the quotation to the customer for confirmation. Upon confirmation, the "
"quotation turns into an official sales order."
msgstr ""
"Når alle nødvendige felter og faner er konfigureret, er det tid til at sende "
"tilbuddet til kunden til bekræftelse. Ved bekræftelse bliver tilbuddet til "
"en officiel salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:297
msgid "At the top of the form, there is a series of buttons:"
msgstr "Øverst på formularen er der en række knapper:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:299
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send by Email`: When clicked, a pop-up window appears with the "
"customer's name and email address in the :guilabel:`Recipients` field, the "
"quotation (and reference ID) in the :guilabel:`Subject` field, and a brief "
"default message in the body of the email, which can be modified, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send via e-mail`: Når der klikkes, vises et pop op-vindue med "
"kundens navn og e-mailadresse i feltet :guilabel:`Modtagere`, tilbuddet (og "
"reference-ID) i feltet :guilabel:`Emne` og en kort standardbesked i e-"
"mailens brødtekst, som kan ændres efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:304
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:312
msgid ""
"Below that, a PDF copy of the quotation is attached. When ready, "
"click :guilabel:`Send` to send the quotation, via email, to the customer, so "
"they can review and confirm it."
msgstr ""
"Nedenfor er en PDF-kopi af tilbuddet vedhæftet. Når du er klar, klik "
"på :guilabel:`Send` for at sende tilbuddet via e-mail til kunden, så de kan "
"gennemgå og bekræfte det."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:306
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Send PRO-FORMA Invoice`: This button **only** appears if the *Pro-"
"Forma Invoice* setting has been enabled. When clicked, a pop-up window "
"appears with the customer's name and email address in "
"the :guilabel:`Recipients` field, the *Proforma* invoice (and reference ID) "
"in the :guilabel:`Subject` field, and a brief default message in the body of "
"the email, which can be modified, if needed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Send PRO-FORMA-faktura`: Denne knap vises **kun**, hvis "
"indstillingen *Pro-forma-faktura* er aktiveret. Når der klikkes, vises et "
"pop op-vindue med kundens navn og e-mailadresse i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Modtagere`, *Proforma*-fakturaen (og reference-ID) i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Emne` og en kort standardbesked i e-mailens brødtekst, som "
"kan ændres efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:314
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Confirm`: When clicked, the quotation is confirmed, and the "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Sales Order`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bekræft`: Når der klikkes, bekræftes tilbuddet, og status ændres "
"til :guilabel:`Salgsordre`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Preview`: When clicked, Odoo reveals a preview of the quotation "
"the customer sees when they log into their customer portal. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Back to edit mode` link at the top of "
"the preview page, in the blue banner, to return to the quotation form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forhåndsvisning`: Når der klikkes, viser Odoo en forhåndsvisning "
"af det tilbud, som kunden ser, når de logger ind på deres kundeportal. Klik "
"på linket :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Tilbage til redigeringstilstand` "
"øverst på forhåndsvisningssiden i det blå banner for at vende tilbage til "
"tilbudsformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:319
msgid ":guilabel:`Cancel`: When clicked, the quotation is canceled."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Annuller`: Når der klikkes, annulleres tilbuddet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:322
msgid ""
"If the *Lock Confirmed Sales* setting is enabled, the sales order "
"becomes :guilabel:`Locked`, and is indicated as such on the sales order form."
msgstr ""
"Hvis indstillingen *Lås bekræftede salg* er aktiveret, bliver "
"salgsordren :guilabel:`Låst`, og dette angives som sådan på "
"salgsordreformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:325
msgid ""
"At this point, the quotation has been confirmed, turned into a sales order, "
"and is now ready to be invoiced and paid for."
msgstr ""
"På dette tidspunkt er tilbuddet blevet bekræftet, gjort til en salgsordre og "
"er nu klar til at blive faktureret og betalt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations.rst:328
msgid ""
"For more information about invoicing, refer to the :doc:`Invoice based on "
"delivered or ordered quantities <../invoicing/invoicing_policy>`"
msgstr ""
"For mere information om fakturering, se :doc:`Fakturer baseret på leverede "
"eller bestilte mængder <../invoicing/invoicing_policy>`"

