#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:3
msgid "Shopee order management"
msgstr "Shopee ordrehåndtering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:11
msgid ""
"If you are starting a new Odoo database and your products are only on "
"Shopee, you can import your Shopee product catalog into Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du starter en ny Odoo database, og dine produkter kun findes på Shopee, "
"kan du importere dit Shopee-produktkatalog til Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Export Shopee catalog:** Use the *Mass Function* drop-down to export the "
"product catalog from Shopee, ensuring it includes the Shopee SKUs."
msgstr ""
"**Eksportér Shopee-katalog:** Brug rullelisten *Mass Function* til at "
"eksportere produktkataloget fra Shopee, og sørg for at inkludere Shopee "
"SKU'erne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:0
msgid "Mass Function drop-down in Shopee."
msgstr "Rullelisten Mass Function i Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Import into Odoo:** :doc:`Import <../../../essentials/export_import_data>` "
"the exported catalog into Odoo. During the import process, it is *crucial* "
"to map the Shopee SKU to the *Internal Reference* field in Odoo. This field "
"will serve as the link between your Shopee and Odoo products."
msgstr ""
"**Importér til Odoo:** :doc:`Importér <../../../essentials/"
"export_import_data>` det eksporterede katalog til Odoo. Under "
"importprocessen er det *afgørende* at tilknytte Shopee SKU til feltet "
"*Intern reference* i Odoo. Dette felt fungerer som forbindelsen mellem dine "
"Shopee- og Odoo-produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:28
msgid ""
"If you already have products in your Odoo database, you'll need to map your "
"Shopee listings to your existing Odoo products."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du allerede har produkter i din Odoo database, skal du tilknytte dine "
"Shopee-lister til dine eksisterende Odoo-produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Export Shopee catalogs:** Use the *Mass Function* drop-down to export the "
"product catalog from Shopee (including Shopee SKUs) and :doc:`export "
"<../../../essentials/export_import_data>` your product catalog from Odoo "
"(including *Internal References*)."
msgstr ""
"**Eksportér Shopee-kataloger:** Brug rullelisten *Mass Function* til at "
"eksportere produktkataloget fra Shopee (inklusiv Shopee SKU'er) "
"og :doc:`eksportér <../../../essentials/export_import_data>` dit "
"produktkatalog fra Odoo (inklusiv *Interne referencer*)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Map in a spreadsheet:** Use a spreadsheet to map the products. Match the "
"Shopee SKU from the Shopee export with the corresponding *Internal "
"Reference* from the Odoo export. Create a column that links the Shopee SKU "
"with the Odoo *Internal Reference*."
msgstr ""
"**Tilknyt i et regneark:** Brug et regneark til at tilknytte produkterne. "
"Match Shopee SKU fra Shopee-eksporten med den tilsvarende *Interne "
"reference* fra Odoo-eksporten. Opret en kolonne, der forbinder Shopee SKU "
"med Odoo *Intern reference*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Update Odoo products:** Import the updated spreadsheet back into Odoo. Use "
"the mapping you created in the spreadsheet to update the *Internal "
"Reference* field of your existing Odoo products with the corresponding "
"Shopee SKU. This establishes the link between your Odoo and Shopee products."
msgstr ""
"**Opdater Odoo-produkter:** Importer det opdaterede regneark tilbage i Odoo. "
"Brug den mapping, du oprettede i regnearket, til at opdatere feltet *Intern "
"reference* for dine eksisterende Odoo-produkter med den tilsvarende Shopee "
"SKU. Dette etablerer forbindelsen mellem dine Odoo- og Shopee-produkter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:43
msgid ""
"Product catalog synchronization between Odoo and Shopee is **not "
"automatic**. It is a **manual operation** that you must initiate. The "
"process differs depending on whether your products already exist in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Produktkatalogssynkronisering mellem Odoo og Shopee er **ikke automatisk**. "
"Det er en **manuel operation**, som du skal igangsætte. Processen varierer "
"afhængigt af, om dine produkter allerede eksisterer i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:50
msgid ""
"Orders are automatically fetched from Shopee, and synchronized in Odoo, at "
"**regular intervals**."
msgstr ""
"Ordrer hentes automatisk fra Shopee og synkroniseres i Odoo med **jævne "
"mellemrum**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:52
msgid ""
"The synchronization is based on the Shopee orders status: only orders whose "
"status has changed since the last synchronization are fetched from Shopee. "
"This includes changes on Shopee only."
msgstr ""
"Synkroniseringen er baseret på Shopee-ordrernes status: kun ordrer, hvis "
"status er ændret siden sidste synkronisering, hentes fra Shopee. Dette "
"inkluderer kun ændringer på Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:55
msgid ""
"When an order is canceled on Shopee, it will update the order's status in "
"Odoo. On the other hand, if an order is canceled on Odoo, the change won't "
"be reflected on Shopee."
msgstr ""
"Når en ordre annulleres på Shopee, opdateres ordrens status i Odoo. Hvis en "
"ordre derimod annulleres i Odoo, vil ændringen ikke blive afspejlet på "
"Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:58
msgid ""
"For every synchronized order, Odoo creates a sales order and a customer "
"(contact), as long as the customer hasn't been previously imported from "
"Shopee or doesn't already exist in the database."
msgstr ""
"For hver synkroniseret ordre opretter Odoo en salgsordre og en kunde "
"(kontakt), så længe kunden ikke tidligere er blevet importeret fra Shopee "
"eller ikke allerede eksisterer i databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:62
msgid ""
"The principal of the synchronization is to *only fetch orders that needs to "
"be shipped* (i.e., `SHIPPED`, `CANCEL`, `UNPAID`, `COMPLETED`)."
msgstr ""
"Princippet for synkroniseringen er *kun at hente ordrer, der skal afsendes* "
"(dvs. `SHIPPED`, `CANCEL`, `UNPAID`, `COMPLETED`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:68
msgid ""
"In order to force the synchronization of an order, whose status has **not** "
"changed since the previous synchronization:"
msgstr ""
"For at gennemtvinge synkronisering af en ordre, hvis status **ikke** er "
"ændret siden forrige synkronisering:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:71
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to the Shopee account in Odoo :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Shopee --> Account --> Shop`. Modify the date "
"for :guilabel:`Last Order Sync` under :guilabel:`Orders Follow-up`."
msgstr ""
"Naviger derefter til Shopee-kontoen i Odoo :menuselection:`Salg-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Shopee --> Konto --> Butik`. Rediger datoen "
"for :guilabel:`Seneste ordresynkronisering` "
"under :guilabel:`Ordreopfølgning`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:79
msgid "Manage deliveries in :abbr:`FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant)`"
msgstr "Håndter leveringer i :abbr:`FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant)`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:81
msgid ""
"Whenever an FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant) order is synchronized in Odoo, a "
"picking is instantly created in the **Inventory** app, along with a sales "
"order and customer record."
msgstr ""
"Når en FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant) ordre synkroniseres i Odoo, oprettes en "
"plukning øjeblikkeligt i **Lager**-appen sammen med en salgsordre og "
"kunderegistrering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:84
msgid ""
"When a picking related to the order is confirmed, you also have to click "
"on :guilabel:`Arrange Shipment` in your Shopee Seller Account in order to be "
"able to generate and fetch the :guilabel:`Shipping Label` "
"and :guilabel:`Tracking Number`."
msgstr ""
"Når en plukning relateret til ordren bekræftes, skal du også klikke "
"på :guilabel:`Arrangér forsendelse` i din Shopee-sælgerkonto for at kunne "
"generere og hente :guilabel:`Forsendelsesetiket` "
"og :guilabel:`Sporingsnummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:89
msgid "Shopee delivery statuses"
msgstr "Shopee-leveringsstatusser"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:91
msgid ""
"Understanding the different Shopee delivery statuses is crucial for managing "
"your orders effectively. Here's a breakdown:"
msgstr ""
"Forståelse af de forskellige Shopee-leveringsstatusser er afgørende for at "
"håndtere dine ordrer effektivt. Her er en oversigt:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:94
msgid "**Ready to ship:** The seller can now arrange shipment for this order."
msgstr ""
"**Klar til afsendelse:** Sælgeren kan nu arrangere forsendelse for denne "
"ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:95
msgid ""
"**Shipment arranged:** The seller has arranged shipment online and received "
"a tracking number from the third-party logistics (3PL) provider."
msgstr ""
"**Forsendelse arrangeret:** Sælgeren har arrangeret forsendelse online og "
"modtaget et sporingsnummer fra tredjepartslogistikudbyderen (3PL)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:97
msgid ""
"**Shipped:** The parcel has been dropped off at the 3PL location or picked "
"up by the 3PL provider."
msgstr ""
"**Afsendt:** Pakken er blevet afleveret på 3PL-stedet eller hentet af 3PL-"
"udbyderen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:99
msgid "**Cancelled:** The order has been canceled."
msgstr "**Annulleret:** Ordren er blevet annulleret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:100
msgid ""
"**Pickup failed:** The 3PL parcel pickup attempt failed. The seller needs to "
"rearrange shipment, and the rest of the order fulfillment content."
msgstr ""
"**Afhentning mislykkedes:** 3PL-pakkeafhentningen mislykkedes. Sælgeren skal "
"omarrangere forsendelse og resten af ordrebehandlingsindholdet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:None
msgid "Shopee delivery status in Odoo."
msgstr "Shopee-leveringsstatus i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:107
msgid "Unsupported for Non-Shopee Supported Logistics (NSSL)"
msgstr "Ikke understøttet for ikke-Shopee-understøttet logistik (NSSL)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:109
msgid ""
"This feature is not available for :abbr:`NSSL (Non-Shopee Supported "
"Logistics)`, you have to manually create shipping label and tracking number "
"via the logistics provider's website/app. Check your region for list of "
"supported logistics (e.g. `Malaysia <https://seller.shopee.com.my/edu/"
"article/388>`_)."
msgstr ""
"Denne funktion er ikke tilgængelig for :abbr:`NSSL (Non-Shopee Supported "
"Logistics)`. Du skal manuelt oprette fragtetiket og sporingsnummer via "
"logistikudbyderens hjemmeside/app. Tjek din region for liste over "
"understøttede logistikudbydere (f.eks. `Malaysia <https://"
"seller.shopee.com.my/edu/article/388>`_)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:114
msgid ""
"Shopee requires users to provide a tracking reference with each delivery. "
"This is needed to assign a carrier."
msgstr ""
"Shopee kræver, at brugere angiver en sporingsreference for hver levering. "
"Dette er nødvendigt for at tildele en fragtudbyder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:117
msgid ""
"If the carrier doesn't automatically provide a tracking reference, one must "
"be set manually. This rule applies to all Shopee marketplaces."
msgstr ""
"Hvis fragtudbyderen ikke automatisk leverer en sporingsreference, skal en "
"angives manuelt. Denne regel gælder for alle Shopee-markedspladser."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:121
msgid "Follow deliveries in Odoo"
msgstr "Følg leveringer i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:123
msgid ""
"For :abbr:`FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant)` orders, the stock move is "
"automatically created in Odoo by the Shopee connector, thanks to the "
"shipping status of Shopee."
msgstr ""
"For :abbr:`FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant)`-ordrer oprettes lagerbevægelsen "
"automatisk i Odoo af Shopee-connectoren takket være forsendelsesstatus fra "
"Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:None
msgid "Stock move created for Shopee order in Odoo."
msgstr "Lagerbevægelse oprettet for Shopee-ordre i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:132
msgid ""
"This section describes the process of fulfilling Shopee orders within Odoo, "
"from order creation to inventory updates."
msgstr ""
"Dette afsnit beskriver processen med at eksekvere Shopee-ordrer i Odoo, fra "
"ordreoprettelse til lageropdateringer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:135
msgid ""
"**New order creation:** When a new order is placed on Shopee, it is "
"automatically created in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Oprettelse af ny ordre:** Når en ny ordre afgives på Shopee, oprettes den "
"automatisk i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:137
msgid ""
"**Arrange shipment on Shopee:** Before the order can be shipped, you "
"**must** arrange the shipment through the Shopee platform itself. This "
"usually involves selecting a shipping provider, generating a shipping label, "
"and scheduling pickup or drop-off. Odoo does *not* handle the physical "
"shipping arrangements; this is managed entirely within Shopee."
msgstr ""
"**Arranger forsendelse på Shopee:** Inden ordren kan afsendes, **skal** du "
"arrangere forsendelsen gennem selve Shopee-platformen. Dette involverer "
"normalt at vælge en fragtudbyder, generere en fragtetiket og planlægge "
"afhentning eller aflevering. Odoo håndterer *ikke* de fysiske forsendelses-"
"arrangementer; dette administreres udelukkende i Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:141
msgid ""
"**Fetch Shopee shipping label (delivery note):** Once the shipment is "
"arranged on Shopee, Odoo fetches the generated shipping label (which serves "
"as the delivery note). This label contains crucial information like the "
"tracking number and is essential for printing and attaching to the package. "
"The shipping label is imported into Odoo and associated with the "
"corresponding sales order."
msgstr ""
"**Hent Shopee-fragtetiket (følgeseddel):** Når forsendelsen er arrangeret på "
"Shopee, henter Odoo den genererede fragtetiket (som fungerer som "
"følgeseddel). Denne etiket indeholder vigtige oplysninger som "
"sporingsnummeret og er essentiel til udskrivning og påsætning af pakken. "
"Fragtetiketten importeres til Odoo og knyttes til den tilsvarende salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:146
msgid ""
"**Validate stock out in Odoo:** After the shipping label is retrieved, you "
"need to validate the stock movement in Odoo. This confirms that the ordered "
"items have left your warehouse or inventory. Validating the stock out will "
"decrease the stock levels in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Valider lagerafgang i Odoo:** Efter fragtetiketten er hentet, skal du "
"validere lagerbevægelsen i Odoo. Dette bekræfter, at de bestilte varer har "
"forladt dit lager. Validering af lagerafgangen reducerer lagerniveauerne i "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:149
msgid ""
"**Inventory update on Shopee:** Finally, Odoo pushes the updated stock "
"levels back to Shopee. This ensures that your Shopee listings reflect the "
"current inventory, preventing overselling and keeping your product "
"availability accurate. This synchronization keeps your Shopee storefront up-"
"to-date with your Odoo inventory."
msgstr ""
"**Lageropdatering på Shopee:** Endelig sender Odoo de opdaterede "
"lagerniveauer tilbage til Shopee. Dette sikrer, at dine Shopee-annoncer "
"afspejler den aktuelle lagerbeholdning, hvilket forhindrer oversalg og "
"holder din produkttilgængelighed præcis. Denne synkronisering holder din "
"Shopee-butik opdateret med dit Odoo-lager."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:157
msgid ""
"Since customers pay Shopee as an intermediary, creating a dedicated *Bank* "
"journal (e.g. named `Shopee Payments`), with a dedicated *Bank and Cash* "
"intermediary account is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Da kunder betaler Shopee som mellemmand, anbefales det at oprette en "
"dedikeret *Bank*-journal (f.eks. med navnet `Shopee Payments`) med en "
"dedikeret *Bank og kontanter* mellemmandskonto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:160
msgid ""
"Additionally, as Shopee makes a single weekly or monthly payment, selecting "
"all the invoices linked to a single payment is necessary when registering "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Da Shopee desuden foretager en enkelt ugentlig eller månedlig betaling, er "
"det nødvendigt at vælge alle fakturaer knyttet til en enkelt betaling ved "
"registrering af betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:163
msgid ""
"To do that, use the appropriate :guilabel:`Journal` dedicated to Shopee "
"payments, and select :guilabel:`Batch Deposit` as the :guilabel:`Payment "
"Method`."
msgstr ""
"For at gøre dette skal du bruge den passende :guilabel:`Journal` dedikeret "
"til Shopee-betalinger og vælge :guilabel:`Batch Deposit` "
"som :guilabel:`Betalingsmetode`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:170
msgid ""
"This same action can be performed with vendor bills from Shopee dedicated to "
"fees/commissions."
msgstr ""
"Samme handling kan udføres med kreditorfakturaer fra Shopee dedikeret til "
"gebyrer/kommissioner."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:172
msgid ""
"When the balance is received in the bank account at the end of the week/"
"month, and the bank statements are recorded, credit the Shopee intermediary "
"account by the amount received."
msgstr ""
"Når saldoen modtages på bankkontoen ved slutningen af ugen/måneden, og "
"bankkontoudtogene er registreret, skal du kreditere Shopee-"
"mellemmandskontoen med det modtagne beløb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:176
msgid "Analyzing Shopee sales with Odoo's reporting"
msgstr "Analysere Shopee-salg med Odoos rapportering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:178
msgid ""
"Odoo's dashboard consolidates sales data from all your connected sales "
"channels, providing a comprehensive overview of your business performance. "
"To specifically analyze your Shopee sales, you will need to configure sales "
"teams for your Shopee shops. This setup enables you to filter and isolate "
"Shopee sales data within the Odoo dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Odoos dashboard konsoliderer salgsdata fra alle dine forbundne salgskanaler "
"og giver et omfattende overblik over din forretningsperformance. For "
"specifikt at analysere dit Shopee-salg skal du konfigurere salgsteams for "
"dine Shopee-butikker. Denne opsætning gør det muligt at filtrere og isolere "
"Shopee-salgsdata i Odoo-dashboardet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:184
msgid "Setting up sales teams for Shopee reporting"
msgstr "Opsætning af salgsteams til Shopee-rapportering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:186
msgid ""
"By default, the Shopee account's sales team is shared across all of your "
"company's accounts. To generate separate reports for specific Shopee shops "
"or marketplaces, you'll need to assign dedicated sales teams."
msgstr ""
"Som standard deles Shopee-kontoens salgsteam på tværs af alle din "
"virksomheds konti. For at generere separate rapporter for specifikke Shopee-"
"butikker eller markedspladser skal du tildele dedikerede salgsteams."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:190
msgid ""
"**Assign a sales team to your Shopee shop:** Navigate to the Shopee account "
"configuration (typically found under :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration "
"--> Accounts`).  Within the account details, assign a specific sales team to "
"your Shopee shop."
msgstr ""
"**Tildel et salgsteam til din Shopee-butik:** Naviger til Shopee-"
"kontokonfigurationen (typisk fundet under :menuselection:`Salg --> "
"Konfiguration --> Konti`). Inden for kontodetaljer tildeles et specifikt "
"salgsteam til din Shopee-butik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:193
msgid ""
"**Filtering Shopee sales on the dashboard:** Once sales teams are assigned, "
"you can use the dashboard filters to view sales data specifically for your "
"Shopee shops. Select the appropriate sales team to isolate and analyze your "
"Shopee performance."
msgstr ""
"**Filtrering af Shopee-salg på dashboardet:** Når salgsteams er tildelt, kan "
"du bruge dashboardfiltrene til at se salgsdata specifikt for dine Shopee-"
"butikker. Vælg det passende salgsteam for at isolere og analysere din Shopee-"
"performance."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/manage.rst:198
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:231
msgid ":doc:`Shopee supported features and marketplaces <../shopee_connector>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Shopee understøttede funktioner og markedspladser <../"
"shopee_connector>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:3
msgid "Shopee Connector configuration"
msgstr "Shopee Connector-konfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo allows users to synchronize with Shopee Seller account in the database, "
"but users **must** have a registered **Shopee Seller account** and a "
"**Shopee Open account** prior to completing the configuration."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver brugere mulighed for at synkronisere med Shopee Seller-konto i "
"databasen, men brugere **skal** have en registreret **Shopee Seller-konto** "
"og en **Shopee Open-konto** før konfigurationen kan fuldføres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:9
msgid ""
"Set up an Open Shopee account by first going to the `Shopee Open Platform "
"<https://open.shopee.com/>`_, and click the :guilabel:`Get Access (Now)` "
"button located in the middle of the page."
msgstr ""
"Opret en Open Shopee-konto ved først at gå til `Shopee Open Platform "
"<https://open.shopee.com/>`_ og klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Få adgang "
"(nu)`, som findes midt på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:13
msgid ""
"Use the `Open Shopee Developer Guide <https://open.shopee.com/developer-"
"guide/12>`_, and follow the registration process. Once all done, proceed to "
"follow the instructions below to register and link the Open Shopee account "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Brug `Open Shopee Developer Guide <https://open.shopee.com/developer-guide/"
"12>`_ og følg registreringsprocessen. Når alt er færdigt, fortsæt med at "
"følge nedenstående instruktioner for at registrere og linke Open Shopee-"
"kontoen i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:18
msgid ""
"Shopee Open Platform access and seller account requirements are **regionally "
"specific**. This means the rules, qualifications, and processes differ from "
"country to country. Before proceeding with Odoo's Shopee Connector setup, "
"verify the requirements for *your* specific Shopee region."
msgstr ""
"Adgang til Shopee Open Platform og krav til sælgerkonto er "
"**regionsspecifikke**. Dette betyder, at reglerne, kvalifikationerne og "
"processerne er forskellige fra land til land. Før du fortsætter med Odoos "
"Shopee Connector-opsætning, skal du verificere kravene for *din* specifikke "
"Shopee-region."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:22
msgid "**Key Considerations:**"
msgstr "**Vigtige overvejelser:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:24
msgid ""
"**Shopee Seller Status & Business Type:** You must have an active Shopee "
"seller account (Individual or Registered Business). Your eligibility depends "
"on your region and business registration."
msgstr ""
"**Shopee-sælgerstatus og virksomhedstype:** Du skal have en aktiv Shopee-"
"sælgerkonto (individuel eller registreret virksomhed). Din berettigelse "
"afhænger af din region og forretningsregistrering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Order Volume/Seller Tier (If Applicable):** Many regions require a minimum "
"number of orders within a specific time frame or a certain seller tier "
"(e.g., Mall, Preferred, Managed) to access the Open Platform."
msgstr ""
"**Ordrevolumen/sælgerniveau (hvis relevant):** Mange regioner kræver et "
"minimumsantal ordrer inden for en specifik tidsramme eller et bestemt "
"sælgerniveau (f.eks. Mall, Preferred, Managed) for at få adgang til Open "
"Platform."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:31
msgid "**Action Required:**"
msgstr "**Nødvendig handling:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:33
msgid "Identify your Shopee region."
msgstr "Identificer din Shopee-region."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:34
msgid ""
"Locate the official Shopee documentation for your region. `Open Shopee "
"Developer Guide <https://open.shopee.com/developer-guide/12>`_"
msgstr ""
"Find den officielle Shopee-dokumentation for din region. `Open Shopee "
"Developer Guide <https://open.shopee.com/developer-guide/12>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:36
msgid ""
"Carefully review the requirements for seller accounts and Open Platform "
"access in your region."
msgstr ""
"Gennemgå omhyggeligt kravene til sælgerkonti og Open Platform-adgang i din "
"region."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:38
msgid ""
"Ensure your Shopee account meets all the necessary criteria *before* "
"proceeding with the Odoo Shopee Connector configuration."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for, at din Shopee-konto opfylder alle nødvendige kriterier, *før* du "
"fortsætter med Odoo Shopee Connector-konfigurationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:44
msgid "Connect Shopee seller account to Odoo"
msgstr "Forbind Shopee-sælgerkonto til Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:46
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`Shopee Connector` "
"(`sale_shoppe`) by going to :menuselection:`Apps`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Installer <general/install>` :guilabel:`Shopee Connector` "
"(`sale_shoppe`) ved at gå til :menuselection:`Apps`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:49
msgid ""
"Then connect your Shopee Open account by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Configuration --> Shopee --> Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"Forbind derefter din Shopee Open-konto ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Salg --> Konfiguration --> Shopee --> Konti`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:52
msgid ""
"From here, click :guilabel:`New` to create to link a new Shopee account."
msgstr ""
"Klik herfra på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette en forbindelse til en ny Shopee-"
"konto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:54
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Credentials` tab, select the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`API Endpoint` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter det relevante :guilabel:`API-endepunkt` fra rullemenuen under "
"fanen :guilabel:`Legitimationsoplysninger`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:58
msgid ""
"Shopee offers several API endpoints for production and testing. Selecting "
"the correct endpoint is crucial for successful integration. Choose the "
"endpoint that corresponds to your marketplace location."
msgstr ""
"Shopee tilbyder flere API-endepunkter til produktion og test. Valg af det "
"korrekte endepunkt er afgørende for vellykket integration. Vælg det "
"endepunkt, der svarer til din markedspladsplacering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:62
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shopee Production Endpoint (Singapore)`: This is the primary "
"endpoint for sellers in most APAC countries. Select this option unless you "
"are specifically operating within mainland China or Brazil."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shopee produktionsendepunkt (Singapore)`: Dette er det primære "
"endepunkt for sælgere i de fleste APAC-lande. Vælg denne indstilling, "
"medmindre du specifikt opererer i det kinesiske fastland eller Brasilien."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shopee Production Endpoint (China)`: This endpoint is exclusively "
"for sellers operating within mainland China. It is designed to comply with "
"local regulations and business practices."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shopee produktionsendepunkt (Kina)`: Dette endepunkt er "
"udelukkende for sælgere, der opererer i det kinesiske fastland. Det er "
"designet til at overholde lokale regler og forretningspraksis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shopee Production Endpoint (Brazil)`: This endpoint is dedicated "
"to sellers operating within Brazil. Select this option if your Shopee store "
"is based in Brazil."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shopee produktionsendepunkt (Brasilien)`: Dette endepunkt er "
"dedikeret til sælgere, der opererer i Brasilien. Vælg denne indstilling, "
"hvis din Shopee-butik er baseret i Brasilien."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shopee Testing Endpoint`: This endpoint is for development and "
"testing purposes only. Use it to simulate interactions with the Shopee API "
"without affecting your live data. **Do not use this endpoint for "
"production.**"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shopee testendepunkt`: Dette endepunkt er kun til udviklings- og "
"testformål. Brug det til at simulere interaktioner med Shopee API uden at "
"påvirke dine livedata. **Brug ikke dette endepunkt til produktion.**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shopee Testing Endpoint (China)`:  Similar to the general testing "
"endpoint, this one is specifically for testing integrations related to the "
"China-specific production endpoint. **Do not use this endpoint for "
"production.**"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Shopee testendepunkt (Kina)`: Svarende til det generelle "
"testendepunkt er dette specifikt til test af integrationer relateret til det "
"Kina-specifikke produktionsendepunkt. **Brug ikke dette endepunkt til "
"produktion.**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:77
msgid ""
"After selecting the correct API Endpoint in the :guilabel:`Credentials` "
"form, input your Open Shopee :guilabel:`Partner ID` and :guilabel:`Partner "
"Key` in the corresponding fields. Then click :guilabel:`Save And Authorize`."
msgstr ""
"Efter valg af det korrekte API-endepunkt i "
"formularen :guilabel:`Legitimationsoplysninger` skal du indtaste dit Open "
"Shopee :guilabel:`Partner-id` og :guilabel:`Partnernøgle` i de tilsvarende "
"felter. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem og godkend`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:82
msgid ""
"You'll need your Open Shopee :guilabel:`Partner ID` and :guilabel:`Partner "
"Key` to complete this step. Here's how to find them in the Shopee Open "
"Platform:"
msgstr ""
"Du skal bruge dit Open Shopee :guilabel:`Partner-id` "
"og :guilabel:`Partnernøgle` for at fuldføre dette trin. Sådan finder du dem "
"på Shopee Open Platform:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:85
msgid ""
"**Log in to the Shopee Open Platform:** `Log in <https://open.shopee.com/>`_ "
"with the credentials you used to register your Open Shopee account."
msgstr ""
"**Log ind på Shopee Open Platform:** `Log ind <https://open.shopee.com/>`_ "
"med de legitimationsoplysninger, du brugte til at registrere din Open Shopee-"
"konto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:87
msgid ""
"**Navigate to App Management:** Go to the :guilabel:`App Management` "
"section, then select :guilabel:`App List`."
msgstr ""
"**Naviger til appstyring:** Gå til afsnittet :guilabel:`Appstyring`, og vælg "
"derefter :guilabel:`Appliste`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:89
msgid ""
"**Select your app:** Choose the specific app you want to synchronize with "
"Odoo (either your test app or your production app)."
msgstr ""
"**Vælg din app:** Vælg den specifikke app, du vil synkronisere med Odoo "
"(enten din testapp eller din produktionsapp)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:91
msgid ""
"**Find your credentials:** Within the app details, you'll find your Partner "
"ID and Partner Key. These are the values you'll need to copy and paste into "
"the corresponding fields in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Find dine legitimationsoplysninger:** I appdetaljerne finder du dit "
"partner-id og partnernøgle. Dette er de værdier, du skal kopiere og indsætte "
"i de tilsvarende felter i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:96
msgid ""
"**Copy carefully:** Copy the Partner ID and Partner Key accurately, without "
"any extra spaces or characters. These are case-sensitive."
msgstr ""
"**Kopier omhyggeligt:** Kopier partner-id'et og partnernøglen nøjagtigt uden "
"ekstra mellemrum eller tegn. Der skelnes mellem store og små bogstaver."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:98
msgid ""
"**Keep your key secure:** Your Partner Key is sensitive information. Do not "
"share it with anyone. Treat it like a password."
msgstr ""
"**Hold din nøgle sikker:** Din partnernøgle er følsom information. Del den "
"ikke med nogen. Behandl den som en adgangskode."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:102
msgid "Authorization and account registration"
msgstr "Godkendelse og kontoregistrering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:104
msgid ""
"After entering connecting the :ref:`Shoppe Seller account to Odoo <shopee/"
"setup>`, the authorization process begins."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have forbundet :ref:`Shopee-sælgerkontoen til Odoo <shopee/setup>` "
"begynder godkendelsesprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:108
msgid "Shopee seller account selection/login"
msgstr "Valg/login af Shopee-sælgerkonto"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:110
msgid ""
"Upon clicking :guilabel:`Save and Authorize`, Odoo redirects to the Shopee "
"seller account selection page."
msgstr ""
"Når du klikker på :guilabel:`Gem og godkend`, omdirigerer Odoo til Shopees "
"side for valg af sælgerkonto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:113
msgid ""
"**Already logged in:** If you are already logged in to a Shopee account, "
"your email address or username will be displayed. Click on your account to "
"proceed."
msgstr ""
"**Allerede logget ind:** Hvis du allerede er logget ind på en Shopee-konto, "
"vises din e-mailadresse eller dit brugernavn. Klik på din konto for at "
"fortsætte."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:115
msgid ""
"**Not logged in:** If you are not logged in, you will be prompted to enter "
"the credentials (email/username and password) of the Shopee seller account "
"you wish to connect to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Ikke logget ind:** Hvis du ikke er logget ind, bliver du bedt om at "
"indtaste legitimationsoplysningerne (e-mail/brugernavn og adgangskode) for "
"den Shopee-sælgerkonto, du ønsker at forbinde til Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:119
msgid "Granting access to Odoo"
msgstr "Tildeling af adgang til Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:121
msgid ""
"After selecting or logging into your Shopee seller account, you will be "
"directed to the authorization (or consent) page. Here, confirm that you "
"allow Shopee to grant Odoo access to your account and related data. This "
"step is essential for the integration to function correctly."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have valgt eller logget ind på din Shopee-sælgerkonto, bliver du "
"dirigeret til godkendelsessiden (eller samtykkesiden). Her bekræfter du, at "
"du tillader Shopee at give Odoo adgang til din konto og relaterede data. "
"Dette trin er essentielt for, at integrationen fungerer korrekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:126
msgid "Account registration and Shopee shop creation"
msgstr "Kontoregistrering og oprettelse af Shopee-butik"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:128
msgid ""
"Upon confirming access, Shopee redirects you back to Odoo. An indicator "
"appears, confirming that your Shopee account has been successfully "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have bekræftet adgang omdirigerer Shopee dig tilbage til Odoo. En "
"indikator vises, som bekræfter, at din Shopee-konto er blevet registreret "
"succesfuldt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:132
msgid "Post-synchronization configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration efter synkronisering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:134
msgid ""
"After the redirection, you should perform the following steps within Odoo:"
msgstr "Efter omdirigeringen bør du udføre følgende trin i Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:136
msgid ""
"**Rename the Shopee Account (Optional):** The newly created Shopee account "
"in Odoo will likely have a default name. You can rename it to something more "
"descriptive (e.g., the name of your Shopee shop) for easier management."
msgstr ""
"**Omdøb Shopee-kontoen (valgfrit):** Den nyoprettede Shopee-konto i Odoo vil "
"sandsynligvis have et standardnavn. Du kan omdøbe den til noget mere "
"beskrivende (f.eks. navnet på din Shopee-butik) for lettere administration."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:139
msgid ""
"**Set the Last Order Synchronization Date:** This setting determines the "
"starting point for fetching orders from Shopee. Choose a date from which you "
"want Odoo to retrieve past orders."
msgstr ""
"**Indstil dato for sidste ordresynkronisering:** Denne indstilling bestemmer "
"startpunktet for hentning af ordrer fra Shopee. Vælg en dato, hvorfra du "
"ønsker, at Odoo skal hente tidligere ordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:141
msgid ""
"**Configure Inventory Synchronization:**  Decide whether you want to "
"synchronize your product inventory between Odoo and Shopee. Enable "
"the :guilabel:`Synchronize Inventory` option to automatically push stock "
"updates from Odoo to Shopee. Disabling this option prevents automatic "
"inventory updates."
msgstr ""
"**Konfigurer lagersynkronisering:** Beslut, om du vil synkronisere dit "
"produktlager mellem Odoo og Shopee. Aktiver "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Synkroniser lager` for automatisk at skubbe "
"lageropdateringer fra Odoo til Shopee. Deaktivering af denne indstilling "
"forhindrer automatiske lageropdateringer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:145
msgid ""
"**Assign a Default Sales Team:** Assign a default sales team to your Shopee "
"account in Odoo. This helps with reporting and order management."
msgstr ""
"**Tildel et standard salgsteam:** Tildel et standard salgsteam til din "
"Shopee-konto i Odoo. Dette hjælper med rapportering og ordrestyring."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:148
msgid ""
"With the Shopee account successfully registered, the marketplaces available "
"with this specific account can later be synchronized the exact same way, and "
"listed under the :guilabel:`Shops` button."
msgstr ""
"Med Shopee-kontoen succesfuldt registreret kan de markedspladser, der er "
"tilgængelige med denne specifikke konto, senere synkroniseres på nøjagtig "
"samme måde og vises under knappen :guilabel:`Butikker`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:153
msgid "Shopee orders in Odoo"
msgstr "Shopee-ordrer i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:155
msgid ""
"When a Shopee order is synchronized, only lines for items are created on the "
"sales order in Odoo. Each one represents one for the product that was sold "
"on Shopee."
msgstr ""
"Når en Shopee-ordre synkroniseres, oprettes kun linjer for varer på "
"salgsordren i Odoo. Hver enkelt repræsenterer én for det produkt, der blev "
"solgt på Shopee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:None
msgid "Shopee synchronized sale order in Odoo."
msgstr "Shopee-synkroniseret salgsordre i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:161
msgid ""
"Any necessary price reconciliation related to shipping or income versus fees "
"can be managed later using Shopee's weekly / monthly financial reports, "
"which can then be imported into the Odoo **Accounting** app."
msgstr ""
"Enhver nødvendig prisafstemning relateret til forsendelse eller indtægter "
"versus gebyrer kan håndteres senere ved hjælp af Shopees ugentlige/månedlige "
"finansielle rapporter, som derefter kan importeres i Odoo **Regnskab**-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:165
msgid ""
"The selection of a database product for a sales order item is done by "
"matching its :guilabel:`Internal Reference` (a customizable product "
"reference identifier in Odoo, like `FURN001`) with the Shopee *SKU*."
msgstr ""
"Valget af et databaseprodukt til en salgsordrevare foretages ved at matche "
"dets :guilabel:`Intern reference` (en tilpasselig produktreference-"
"identifikator i Odoo, som `FURN001`) med Shopee-*SKU*'en."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:169
msgid ""
"If no database product with a matching internal reference is found for a "
"given :guilabel:`Shopee SKU`, then a default database product, *Shopee Item*."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der ikke findes et databaseprodukt med en matchende intern reference "
"for en given :guilabel:`Shopee SKU`, anvendes et standarddatabaseprodukt, "
"*Shopee Item*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:173
msgid ""
"To modify default products, activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Connectors` section, under :guilabel:`Shopee "
"Sync`, find the :guilabel:`Default Products`."
msgstr ""
"For at ændre standardprodukter skal du aktivere :ref:`udviklertilstand "
"<developer-mode>` og navigere til :menuselection:`Salg --> Konfiguration --> "
"Indstillinger`. I sektionen :guilabel:`Connectors` under :guilabel:`Shopee "
"Sync` finder du :guilabel:`Standardprodukter`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:180
msgid ""
"To allow for tax reporting of Shopee sales with Odoo, the taxes applied to "
"the sales order items are those set on the product, or determined by "
"the :doc:`fiscal position <../../../finance/fiscal_localizations>`."
msgstr ""
"For at muliggøre momsrapportering af Shopee-salg med Odoo er de afgifter, "
"der anvendes på salgsordreposterne, dem, der er angivet på produktet, eller "
"dem, der bestemmes af :doc:`skattepositionen <../../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:184
msgid ""
"Make sure to have the correct taxes set on your products in Odoo, or have it "
"done by a fiscal position, to avoid discrepancies in the subtotals between "
"*Shopee Seller Central* and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for at have de korrekte afgifter indstillet på dine produkter i Odoo, "
"eller få det gjort af en skatteposition, for at undgå uoverensstemmelser i "
"subtotaler mellem *Shopee Seller Central* og Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:188
msgid ""
"As shopee does not necessarily apply the same taxes as those configured in "
"Odoo, it may happen that order totals differ by a few cents between Odoo and "
"*Shopee Seller Central*. Those differences can be resolved with a write-off "
"when reconciling the payments in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Da Shopee ikke nødvendigvis anvender de samme afgifter som dem, der er "
"konfigureret i Odoo, kan det ske, at ordretotaler afviger med nogle få ører "
"mellem Odoo og *Shopee Seller Central*. Disse forskelle kan løses med en "
"afskrivning ved afstemning af betalingerne i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:197
msgid "To add a new marketplace, follow these steps:"
msgstr "For at tilføje en ny markedsplads skal du følge disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:199
msgid ""
"**Navigate to Shopee Accounts:** Go to :menuselection:`Sales --> "
"Configuration --> Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"**Naviger til Shopee-konti:** Gå til :menuselection:`Salg --> Konfiguration "
"--> Konti`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:200
msgid ""
"**Create a New Shopee Account:** Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new "
"Shopee marketplace account."
msgstr ""
"**Opret en ny Shopee-konto:** Klik på :guilabel:`Ny` for at oprette en ny "
"Shopee-markedspladskonto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:202
msgid ""
"**Select the API Endpoint:** Choose the appropriate API endpoint for your "
"local market. (Typically, this will be :guilabel:`Shopee Production Endpoint "
"(Singapore)` unless you are operating in mainland China or Brazil. Refer to "
"the documentation for details on endpoint selection)."
msgstr ""
"**Vælg API-endepunkt:** Vælg det passende API-endepunkt for dit lokale "
"marked. (Typisk vil dette være :guilabel:`Shopee produktionsendepunkt "
"(Singapore)`, medmindre du opererer i det kinesiske fastland eller "
"Brasilien. Se dokumentationen for detaljer om valg af endepunkt)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:206
msgid ""
"**Enter Credentials:** Your :guilabel:`Partner ID` and :guilabel:`Partner "
"Key` are the same as those linked to your unique Open Shopee account. Enter "
"these values in the corresponding fields."
msgstr ""
"**Indtast legitimationsoplysninger:** Dit :guilabel:`Partner-id` og "
"din :guilabel:`Partnernøgle` er de samme som dem, der er knyttet til din "
"unikke Open Shopee-konto. Indtast disse værdier i de tilsvarende felter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:208
msgid ""
"**Name Your Shop:** Give the new shop a descriptive name (e.g., `Shopee "
"Philippines`) to identify it later."
msgstr ""
"**Navngiv din butik:** Giv den nye butik et beskrivende navn (f.eks. `Shopee "
"Filippinerne`) for at identificere den senere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:210
msgid ""
"**Assign a Sales Team:** Assign a relevant sales team (e.g., `Shopee Sales "
"Philippines`) to enable advanced reporting capabilities."
msgstr ""
"**Tildel et salgsteam:** Tildel et relevant salgsteam (f.eks. `Shopee Salg "
"Filippinerne`) for at muliggøre avancerede rapporteringsfunktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:212
msgid ""
"**Synchronize Your Account:** If none of your existing marketplaces are "
"listed, click :guilabel:`Log in with another account` to synchronize a new "
"one. This will initiate the Shopee authorization process."
msgstr ""
"**Synkroniser din konto:** Hvis ingen af dine eksisterende markedspladser er "
"angivet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Log ind med en anden konto` for at "
"synkronisere en ny. Dette starter Shopee-godkendelsesprocessen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:217
msgid "Automatic synchronization"
msgstr "Automatisk synkronisering"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:219
msgid ""
"Newly added marketplaces are automatically added to the list of synchronized "
"marketplaces. If a new marketplace does *not* appear in the list after "
"synchronization, it indicates that the marketplace is either incompatible "
"with the Shopee Open Platform or unavailable for your specific seller "
"account. Consult the Shopee Open Platform documentation or contact their "
"support for further assistance."
msgstr ""
"Nyligt tilføjede markedspladser tilføjes automatisk til listen over "
"synkroniserede markedspladser. Hvis en ny markedsplads *ikke* vises på "
"listen efter synkronisering, indikerer det, at markedspladsen enten er "
"inkompatibel med Shopee Open Platform eller ikke tilgængelig for din "
"specifikke sælgerkonto. Konsulter Shopee Open Platform-dokumentationen eller "
"kontakt deres support for yderligere assistance."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector/setup.rst:226
msgid ""
"While Odoo allows creating the same Shopee shop multiple times, only one "
"instance will function due to token limitations. To avoid order management "
"issues, synchronize each shop only once. For connection updates, manually "
"fetch orders first before re-establishing the connection."
msgstr ""
"Selvom Odoo tillader oprettelse af den samme Shopee-butik flere gange, vil "
"kun én instans fungere på grund af tokenbegrænsninger. For at undgå "
"problemer med ordrestyring skal du kun synkronisere hver butik én gang. Ved "
"opdatering af forbindelsen skal du manuelt hente ordrer først, før du "
"genetablerer forbindelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:6
msgid "Subscriptions"
msgstr "Abonnementer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:8
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Subscriptions** app is designed to manage recurring revenue "
"through subscription-based products or services. It supports automated "
"invoicing, renewal management, and customer lifecycle tracking."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Abonnementer**-appen er designet til at administrere tilbagevendende "
"indtægter gennem abonnementsbaserede produkter eller tjenester. Den "
"understøtter automatiseret fakturering, fornyelsesstyring og sporing af "
"kundelivscyklus."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:12
msgid ""
"Subscriptions can be created manually or automatically through online sales, "
"with varying options for recurring billing. The app integrates with other "
"Odoo modules such as **Invoicing**, **CRM**, **Sales**, and **Helpdesk** to "
"support end-to-end subscription workflows."
msgstr ""
"Abonnementer kan oprettes manuelt eller automatisk gennem onlinesalg med "
"varierende muligheder for tilbagevendende fakturering. Appen integrerer med "
"andre Odoo-moduler såsom **Fakturering**, **CRM**, **Salg** og "
"**Kundeservice** for at understøtte end-to-end abonnementsworkflows."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:18
msgid "Renew a subscription"
msgstr "Forny et abonnement"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:18
msgid "Understand the core management activity for subscriptions"
msgstr "Forstå kerneaktiviteten for håndtering af abonnementer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:24
msgid "Upsell a subscription"
msgstr "Mersalg af et abonnement"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:24
msgid "Offer more value for current subscribers on the same sales order"
msgstr "Tilbyd mere værdi til nuværende abonnenter på samme salgsordre"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:28
msgid "Close a subscription"
msgstr "Luk et abonnement"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:30
msgid ""
"Customize subscription plan templates tailored to various product offerings"
msgstr "Tilpas abonnementsskabeloner til forskellige produkttilbud"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:36
msgid "eCommerce integration"
msgstr "Webshop-integration"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:36
msgid "Offer subscription products through your Odoo eCommerce store"
msgstr "Tilbyd abonnementsprodukter gennem din Odoo-webshop"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:43
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Subscriptions <https://www.odoo.com/slides/"
"subscription-20>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo-tutorials: Abonnementer <https://www.odoo.com/slides/subscription-20>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:46
msgid "Set up recurring plans"
msgstr "Opsæt tilbagevendende planer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:48
msgid ""
"To get started with subscription products in Odoo, *recurring plans* "
"(previously known as *recurrence periods*) must first be configured."
msgstr ""
"For at komme i gang med abonnementsprodukter i Odoo skal *tilbagevendende "
"planer* (tidligere kendt som *gentagelsesperioder*) først konfigureres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:51
msgid ""
"Recurring plans are the time windows in which subscriptions are active "
"before they renew again. While a subscription is active, customers receive "
"products or services, and may also have access to additional benefits such "
"as support desk triage. In terms of payment, these recurring plans designate "
"how often the customer is charged in order to maintain the benefits of their "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Abonnementsplaner er tidsvinduerne, hvor abonnementer er aktive, før de "
"fornyes igen. Mens et abonnement er aktivt, modtager kunderne produkter "
"eller tjenester og kan også have adgang til yderligere fordele såsom "
"supportdesk-prioritering. Hvad angår betaling, angiver disse "
"abonnementsplaner, hvor ofte kunden opkræves for at opretholde fordelene ved "
"deres abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:56
msgid ""
"To configure recurring plans, go to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> "
"Configuration --> Recurring Plans`."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere abonnementsplaner skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Abonnementsplaner`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:59
msgid ""
"By default, the **Subscriptions** app includes a number of common recurring "
"plans already available, such as :guilabel:`Monthly` and :guilabel:`Yearly`."
msgstr ""
"Som standard inkluderer **Abonnementer**-appen en række almindelige "
"abonnementsplaner, der allerede er tilgængelige, såsom :guilabel:`Månedligt` "
"og :guilabel:`Årligt`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:62
msgid ""
"Create a new recurring plan by clicking :guilabel:`New` on "
"the :guilabel:`Recurring Plans` dashboard, to reveal a blank form where the "
"plan :guilabel:`Name`, :guilabel:`DETAILS`, :guilabel:`SELF-SERVICE` "
"and :guilabel:`Pricing` field values are specified."
msgstr ""
"Opret en ny abonnementsplan ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` "
"på :guilabel:`Abonnementsplaner`-dashboardet for at åbne en tom formular, "
"hvor feltværdierne for "
"planens :guilabel:`Navn`, :guilabel:`DETALJER`, :guilabel:`SELVBETJENING` "
"og :guilabel:`Prissætning` angives."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:None
msgid "A blank recurring plan form in the Odoo Subscriptions application."
msgstr "En tom abonnementsplanformular i Odoo Abonnementer-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:70
msgid ""
"The `Days` unit of measure *cannot* be used as a :guilabel:`Billing Period` "
"for subscription products. The daily recurrence period in Odoo is designated "
"for rentals, and **cannot** be added to subscription-based sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Måleenheden `Dage` *kan ikke* bruges som :guilabel:`Faktureringsperiode` for "
"abonnementsprodukter. Den daglige gentagelsesperiode i Odoo er beregnet til "
"udlejning og **kan ikke** tilføjes til abonnementsbaserede salgsordrer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:74
msgid ""
"This limitation is there to avoid sales orders that would generate daily "
"invoices."
msgstr ""
"Denne begrænsning er der for at undgå salgsordrer, der ville generere "
"daglige fakturaer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:77
msgid "DETAILS section"
msgstr "DETALJER-sektion"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:79
msgid ""
"After giving the recurring plan a suitable :guilabel:`Name` (e.g. `Monthly`, "
"`Bi-weekly`, `Quarterly`, etc.), proceed to the form's :guilabel:`DETAILS` "
"section to fill out the following configuration fields:"
msgstr ""
"Efter at have givet abonnementsplanen et passende :guilabel:`Navn` (f.eks. "
"`Månedligt`, `Hver anden uge`, `Kvartalsvis` osv.), fortsæt til "
"formularens :guilabel:`DETALJER`-sektion for at udfylde følgende "
"konfigurationsfelter:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:83
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Billing Period`: determines the frequency with which the "
"subscription is billed. Set the unit of time "
"(:guilabel:`Weeks`, :guilabel:`Months`, or :guilabel:`Years`) in the drop-"
"down menu and the numerical value in the corresponding text field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktureringsperiode`: bestemmer hyppigheden, hvormed abonnementet "
"faktureres. Indstil tidsenheden (:guilabel:`Uger`, :guilabel:`Måneder` "
"eller :guilabel:`År`) i rullemenuen og den numeriske værdi i det tilsvarende "
"tekstfelt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Automatic Closing`: a numerical value, in days, where the "
"subscription is set to close automatically if payment is not made."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Automatisk lukning`: en numerisk værdi i dage, hvor abonnementet "
"er indstillet til at lukke automatisk, hvis betaling ikke foretages."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:90
msgid ""
"If a subscription is set to renew on the 1st of every month, and "
"the :guilabel:`Automatic Closing` value is set to `15` :guilabel:`Days`, "
"then the subscription will close on the 16th of that month if payment is not "
"received."
msgstr ""
"Hvis et abonnement er indstillet til at forny den 1. i hver måned, og "
"værdien for :guilabel:`Automatisk lukning` er sat til `15` :guilabel:`Dage`, "
"vil abonnementet lukke den 16. i den måned, hvis betaling ikke modtages."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Align to Period Start`: sets new and recurring subscription plans "
"to bill on the first day of the next :guilabel:`Billing Period`. When a "
"subscription plan is purchased in the middle of a billing period, the "
"invoice shows a reduced cost. Setting a custom period start dates (such as "
"the 5th of each month) requires custom development and is not available by "
"default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zarovnat na začátek období`: nastaví nové a opakující se plány "
"předplatného tak, aby se fakturovaly první den "
"příštího :guilabel:`Fakturačního období`. Pokud je plán předplatného "
"zakoupen uprostřed fakturačního období, faktura zobrazuje sníženou cenu. "
"Nastavení vlastního data začátku období (například 5. den každého měsíce) "
"vyžaduje vlastní vývoj a není ve výchozím nastavení k dispozici."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:100
msgid ""
"On the 15th of July, a customer purchases a monthly subscription for a "
"streaming service. Selecting :guilabel:`Align to Period Start` for this "
"recurring plan configures this subscription to bill on the 1st of each "
"month. The subscription begins as soon as payment is confirmed. The "
"quotation shows the full cost of the subscription for July 1 - 31, but the "
"invoice shows an adjusted cost for July 15 - 31. On the 1st of August, the "
"customer is charged the full price for the month's subscription."
msgstr ""
"15. července si zákazník zakoupí měsíční předplatné streamovací služby. "
"Výběr možnosti :guilabel:`Zarovnat na začátek období` pro tento opakující se "
"plán nastaví toto předplatné tak, aby se fakturovalo 1. den každého měsíce. "
"Předplatné začíná okamžitě po potvrzení platby. Cenová nabídka zobrazuje "
"plnou cenu předplatného za období 1.–31. července, ale faktura zobrazuje "
"upravenou cenu za období 15.–31. července. 1. srpna je zákazníkovi účtována "
"plná cena za měsíční předplatné."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Company`: optional assignment, if the database has :doc:`Multi-"
"company <../general/companies/multi_company>` functionality enabled. "
"Assigning this value will make the recurring plan available for that "
"company's location, specifically."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Virksomhed`: valgfri tildeling, hvis databasen har :doc:`Multi-"
"virksomhed <../general/companies/multi_company>`-funktionalitet aktiveret. "
"Tildeling af denne værdi vil gøre abonnementsplanen tilgængelig specifikt "
"for den pågældende virksomheds placering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:110
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Email Template`: assigns a specific email template to be "
"used in subscriptions invoicing communications. The default assignment here "
"is `Invoice: Sending` which contains various dynamic fields that "
"autopopulate specific variables across the :guilabel:`Subject` field "
"and :guilabel:`Content` tab, such as the customer's name, invoice number, "
"total amount invoiced, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Faktura-e-mailskabelon`: tildeler en specifik e-mailskabelon, der "
"skal bruges i abonnementsfaktureringskommunikation. Standardtildelingen her "
"er `Faktura: Afsendelse`, som indeholder forskellige dynamiske felter, der "
"automatisk udfylder specifikke variabler på tværs af feltet :guilabel:`Emne` "
"og fanen :guilabel:`Indhold`, såsom kundens navn, fakturanummer, samlet "
"faktureret beløb osv."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:116
msgid ""
"Although this field is optional, it is recommended to use it since this type "
"of communication fulfills good business practices around price transparency, "
"regular customer communication (especially as it relates to charged "
"amounts), and helps build contextual financial documentation around "
"recurring revenues."
msgstr ""
"Selvom dette felt er valgfrit, anbefales det at bruge det, da denne type "
"kommunikation opfylder god forretningspraksis omkring prisgennemsigtighed, "
"regelmæssig kundekommunikation (især som det relaterer sig til opkrævede "
"beløb), og hjælper med at opbygge kontekstuel finansiel dokumentation "
"omkring tilbagevendende indtægter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:0
msgid ""
"An email template in Odoo used to send subscriptions invoicing messages to "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"En e-mailskabelon i Odoo brugt til at sende "
"abonnementsfaktureringsmeddelelser til kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:124
msgid ""
"The `Invoice: Sending` email template is accessible by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-arrow-right` (:guilabel:`Internal link`) that appears after "
"hovering over the :guilabel:`Invoice Email Template` drop-down field in "
"the :guilabel:`Recurring Plans` form."
msgstr ""
"E-mailskabelonen `Faktura: Afsendelse` er tilgængelig ved at klikke "
"på :icon:`fa-arrow-right` (:guilabel:`Internt link`), der vises efter at "
"have holdt musen over :guilabel:`Faktura-e-mailskabelon`-feltet "
"i :guilabel:`Abonnementsplaner`-formularen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:129
msgid "SELF-SERVICE section"
msgstr "SELVBETJENING-sektion"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:131
msgid ""
"The following optional fields enable customers to take administrative "
"actions on their own subscriptions. Enabling any of these options may "
"decrease customer service request volume or increase customer lifetime value "
"(LTV)."
msgstr ""
"Følgende valgfrie felter gør det muligt for kunder at foretage "
"administrative handlinger på deres egne abonnementer. Aktivering af nogen af "
"disse muligheder kan reducere mængden af kundeserviceanmodninger eller øge "
"kundens levetidsværdi (LTV)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:135
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closable`: checking this box will give customers the power to "
"close their own subscriptions. Consider enabling this option to reduce "
"customer service requests and improve the overall customer experience; "
"customers that can manage their own subscriptions in this way helps offload "
"tedious tasks for sales and support teams, and reduces the likelihood of "
"negative reviews."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kan lukkes`: ved at markere dette felt vil kunder få mulighed for "
"at lukke deres egne abonnementer. Overvej at aktivere denne mulighed for at "
"reducere kundeserviceanmodninger og forbedre den overordnede kundeoplevelse; "
"kunder, der kan administrere deres egne abonnementer på denne måde, hjælper "
"med at aflaste kedelige opgaver for salgs- og supportteams og reducerer "
"sandsynligheden for negative anmeldelser."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:141
msgid ""
"Although this option is generally advisable to enable, sales teams with "
"strong customer offboarding processes may consider leaving this option "
"unchecked in order to force an interaction that might save the subscription "
"or a different form of recurring revenue (such as in the case of a lesser "
"subscription or a new trial period with an alternative plan)."
msgstr ""
"Selvom denne mulighed generelt er tilrådelig at aktivere, kan salgsteams med "
"stærke kunde-offboarding-processer overveje at lade denne mulighed være "
"umarkeret for at fremtvinge en interaktion, der måske kan redde abonnementet "
"eller en anden form for tilbagevendende indtægt (såsom i tilfældet med et "
"mindre abonnement eller en ny prøveperiode med en alternativ plan)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:146
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add Products`: allows customers to add new products or edit "
"existing product quantities to their recurring sales orders, thereby "
"enabling customer-driven upselling. When enabled, :doc:`Upsell quotations "
"<subscriptions/upselling>` are generated in Odoo whenever a customer "
"performs a quantitative adjustment on their sales order product lines."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilføj produkter`: giver kunderne mulighed for at tilføje nye "
"produkter eller redigere eksisterende produktmængder til deres "
"tilbagevendende salgsordrer og muliggør dermed kundestyret mersalg. Når "
"funktionen er aktiveret, genereres :doc:`mersalgstilbud <subscriptions/"
"upselling>` i Odoo, hver gang en kunde foretager en kvantitativ justering af "
"sine salgsordreproduktlinjer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:151
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Renew`: enabling this allows customers to manually create "
"a :doc:`Renewal quotation <subscriptions/renewals>` for their subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forny`: aktivering af denne funktion giver kunderne mulighed for "
"manuelt at oprette et :doc:`fornyelsestilbud <subscriptions/renewals>` til "
"deres abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Optional Plans`: adding values here from the drop-down field menu "
"enables customers to switch their subscription plans, in which case a new "
"subscription quotation or renewal quote is created to accommodate the change "
"request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valgfrie planer`: tilføjelse af værdier her fra rullemenuen giver "
"kunderne mulighed for at skifte deres abonnementsplaner, hvorefter der "
"oprettes et nyt abonnementstilbud eller fornyelsestilbud for at imødekomme "
"ændringsanmodningen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:158
msgid "Pricing tab"
msgstr "Fanen priser"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:160
msgid ""
"Make product-specific pricing adjustments, as part of the recurring plan, by "
"adding them to the :guilabel:`Pricing` tab order lines. Sequentially add "
"the :guilabel:`Products`, along with any respective :guilabel:`Product "
"Variants`, and then assign a :guilabel:`Pricelist` (if available) and "
"a :guilabel:`Recurring Price`."
msgstr ""
"Foretag produktspecifikke prisjusteringer som en del af den tilbagevendende "
"plan ved at tilføje dem til ordrelinjerne på fanen :guilabel:`Priser`. "
"Tilføj sekvensielt :guilabel:`Produkter` sammen med eventuelle "
"respektive :guilabel:`Produktvarianter`, og tildel derefter "
"en :guilabel:`Prisliste` (hvis tilgængelig) og en :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende "
"pris`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:166
msgid ""
"Price rules that are added here take precedent over the default pricing "
"information on the subscription product's form. This is meant to accommodate "
"deals, discounts, and similar pricing adjustment strategies that would "
"incentivize customers to purchase the recurring plan."
msgstr ""
"Prisregler, der tilføjes her, har forrang frem for standardprisoplysningerne "
"på abonnementsproduktets formular. Dette er beregnet til at rumme tilbud, "
"rabatter og lignende prisjusteringsstrategier, der ville give kunderne "
"incitament til at købe den tilbagevendende plan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:171
msgid "Smart buttons"
msgstr "Intelligente knapper"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:173
msgid ""
"At the top of the individual :guilabel:`Recurring Plans` form, are two smart "
"buttons to aid in navigating the recurring revenue sources attached to the "
"plan:"
msgstr ""
"Øverst på den enkelte formular for :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende planer` er der "
"to smarte knapper til at hjælpe med at navigere mellem de tilbagevendende "
"indtægtskilder, der er knyttet til planen:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:176
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subscriptions`: shows the number of active subscriptions sales "
"orders that fall under the recurring plan. Clicking the button leads to a "
"tabled list view, where each row hyperlinks to a respective subscriptions "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Abonnementer`: viser antallet af aktive abonnementssalgsordrer, "
"der falder ind under den tilbagevendende plan. Klik på knappen for at komme "
"til en tabellisteoversigt, hvor hver række indeholder et hyperlink til en "
"respektiv abonnementssalgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subscription Items`: lists all the individual recurring "
"subscription services that are active, in an itemized "
"fashion. :guilabel:`Subscription` and :guilabel:`Customer` values will "
"repeat if the customer ordered multiple subscriptions on the same sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Abonnementselementer`: viser alle de enkelte tilbagevendende "
"abonnementstjenester, der er aktive, på en specificeret måde. Værdierne "
"for :guilabel:`Abonnement` og :guilabel:`Kunde` gentages, hvis kunden har "
"bestilt flere abonnementer på samme salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:186
msgid "Product form configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguration af produktformular"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:188
msgid ""
"With recurring plans set up, create a subscription product by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Products --> Products`, and click "
"either an existing product to edit, or make a new one by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New` to open up the subscription product's form."
msgstr ""
"Når de tilbagevendende planer er sat op, oprettes et abonnementsprodukt ved "
"at navigere til :menuselection:`Abonnementer app --> Produkter --> "
"Produkter`, og klik enten på et eksisterende produkt for at redigere det, "
"eller opret et nyt ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` for at åbne "
"abonnementsproduktets formular."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:193
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Subscriptions` option is already enabled, "
"prompting Odoo to recognize it as a subscription product. Be sure to leave "
"the :guilabel:`Subscriptions` and :guilabel:`Sales` options enabled."
msgstr ""
"Som standard er funktionen :guilabel:`Abonnementer` allerede aktiveret, "
"hvilket får Odoo til at genkende det som et abonnementsprodukt. Sørg for at "
"lade funktionerne :guilabel:`Abonnementer` og :guilabel:`Salg` være "
"aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:None
msgid "A basic subscription product form in Odoo Subscriptions application."
msgstr ""
"En grundlæggende abonnementsproduktformular i Odoo Abonnementer-"
"applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:200
msgid ""
"On the product form, configure the following items in the :guilabel:`General "
"Information` tab so the subscription product will function correctly:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurer følgende elementer på fanen :guilabel:`Generelle oplysninger` på "
"produktformularen, så abonnementsproduktet fungerer korrekt:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product type`: this value is typically set to "
"a :guilabel:`Service`, however other product types may be used depending on "
"the purpose of the subscription (e.g., physical product box subscriptions, "
"eLearning course with supplemental physical goods, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkttype`: denne værdi er typisk sat til "
"en :guilabel:`Tjeneste`, men andre produkttyper kan bruges afhængigt af "
"formålet med abonnementet (f.eks. fysiske produktboksabonnementer, eLearning-"
"kursus med supplerende fysiske varer osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:206
msgid ""
":doc:`Invoicing policy <sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy>`: set this value "
"to when the customer should be charged for their subscription."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Faktureringspolitik <sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy>`: indstil denne "
"værdi til, hvornår kunden skal betale for deres abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:208
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unit of Measure`: how the product should be counted in Odoo, for "
"stock purposes. For most subscriptions, the :abbr:`UoM (Unit of Measure)` "
"will be :guilabel:`Units`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Måleenhed`: hvordan produktet skal tælles i Odoo til lagerformål. "
"For de fleste abonnementer vil :abbr:`ME (måleenhed)` "
"være :guilabel:`Enheder`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Price`: enter the recurring cost of the subscription that "
"the customer will pay per recurrence period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salgspris`: indtast den tilbagevendende pris for abonnementet, "
"som kunden betaler pr. tilbagevendende periode."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:214
msgid ""
"When creating a subscription for a physical good, selecting the "
"wrong :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` will lead to errors when creating "
"invoices. Physical products must be set to :guilabel:`Ordered quantities`."
msgstr ""
"Når du opretter et abonnement på en fysisk vare, vil valg af den "
"forkerte :guilabel:`Faktureringspolitik` føre til fejl ved oprettelse af "
"fakturaer. Fysiske produkter skal være indstillet til :guilabel:`Bestilte "
"mængder`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:218
msgid ""
"Optionally set up information on the :doc:`Attributes & Variants <sales/"
"products_prices/products/variants>` tab if the subscription contains "
"multiple choices for customers (i.e. food delivery, tailored fashion boxes, "
"etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Eventuelt kan du opsætte oplysninger under fanen :doc:`Attributter og "
"varianter <sales/products_prices/products/variants>`, hvis abonnementet "
"indeholder flere valgmuligheder for kunder (f.eks. madlevering, "
"skræddersyede modekasser osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:222
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Recurring Prices` tab, clarify the pricing options for the "
"subscription. For each option available, click :guilabel:`Add a price rule` "
"to add a new row."
msgstr ""
"På fanen :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende priser` skal du præcisere "
"prismulighederne for abonnementet. For hver tilgængelig mulighed skal du "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en prisregel` for at tilføje en ny række."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:226
msgid ""
"Longer time :guilabel:`Recurring Plan` time periods are typically "
"incentivized with cost savings. Consider dropping the "
"total :guilabel:`Recurring Price` values to offer customers a discount while "
"supporting the business's financial runway."
msgstr ""
"Længere :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende plan`-tidsperioder incitamenteres typisk "
"med besparelser. Overvej at reducere de samlede :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende "
"pris`-værdier for at tilbyde kunderne en rabat og samtidig understøtte "
"virksomhedens økonomiske bæredygtighed."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:230
msgid ""
"Last, if the subscription is meant to be sold on the **eCommerce** website, "
"click the :icon:`fa-globe` :menuselection:`Go To Website` smart button and "
"in the product page header, click the gray slider "
"from :guilabel:`Unpublished` to the green :guilabel:`Published` status."
msgstr ""
"Pokud má být abonnement prodáván na **webshopové** stránce, klikněte na "
"chytré tlačítko :icon:`fa-globe` :menuselection:`Přejít na webovou stránku` "
"a v záhlaví produktové stránky klikněte na šedý posuvník "
"z :guilabel:`Nezveřejněno` na zelený stav :guilabel:`Zveřejněno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:237
msgid "Create a subscriptions quotation"
msgstr "Vytvořit nabídku abonnementu"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:239
msgid ""
"Manually create a new customer subscription by navigating to either "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` or :menuselection:`Subscriptions` app dashboards, "
"and then clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Vytvořte nový abonnement zákazníka ručně přechodem do dashboardu "
"aplikace :menuselection:`Salg` nebo :menuselection:`Abonnementer` a poté "
"kliknutím na :guilabel:`Nový`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:243
msgid ""
"Products that have been marked as :guilabel:`Subscriptions` on their product "
"forms, and are also sold on the **eCommerce** website will *automatically* "
"create and confirm subscription quotations in the backend of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Produkty, které byly na svých produktových formulářích označeny "
"jako :guilabel:`Abonnementer` a jsou také prodávány na **webshopové** "
"stránce, *automaticky* vytvoří a potvrdí nabídky abonnementů v backendu Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:248
msgid ""
"Sales orders with a defined recurring plan automatically become "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Salgsordrer s definovaným opakujícím se plánem se automaticky stanou "
"abonnementy."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:250
msgid ""
"On the quotation form, fill in the necessary fields such "
"as :guilabel:`Customer` and :guilabel:`Recurring Plan`, as well as "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Na formuláři nabídky vyplňte potřebná pole, jako je :guilabel:`Zákazník` "
"a :guilabel:`Opakující se plán`, stejně jako kartu :guilabel:`Řádky "
"objednávky`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:253
msgid "Optionally, specify a:"
msgstr "Volitelně uveďte:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:255
msgid ""
":doc:`Quotation Template <sales/sales_quotations/quote_template>`, if one is "
"readily available to help populate the form fields."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Šablonu nabídky <sales/sales_quotations/quote_template>`, pokud je k "
"dispozici a pomůže vyplnit pole formuláře."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expiration` date, to indicate when the subscription offer is no "
"longer valid."
msgstr ""
"Datum :guilabel:`Vypršení`, které označuje, kdy již nabídka abonnementu není "
"platná."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:260
msgid ""
"Expiration dates pair well with :doc:`discounts <sales/products_prices/"
"prices/discounts>` to incentivize faster purchases, since the discount will "
"expire with the quotation if it's not turned into a sales order within the "
"specified date range."
msgstr ""
"Data vypršení dobře fungují se :doc:`slevami <sales/products_prices/prices/"
"discounts>` k motivaci rychlejších nákupů, protože sleva vyprší s nabídkou, "
"pokud není do zadaného časového období přeměněna na salgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:264
msgid ""
":doc:`Pricelist <sales/products_prices/prices/pricing>`, if one is available "
"and appropriate to use (i.e., summer sale discount, VIP customer, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Ceník <sales/products_prices/prices/pricing>`, pokud je k dispozici a "
"vhodný k použití (např. letní výprodej, VIP zákazník atd.)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:266
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Terms`, to set a specified time window for when the "
"subscription must be paid. This is not to be confused for when the quotation "
"is *confirmed* and becomes a sales order, to where, payment may then be "
"obtained immediately or within a certain amount of days, weeks, months, etc."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Platební podmínky`, k nastavení určeného časového okna, kdy musí "
"být abonnement zaplacen. To není zaměnit s tím, kdy je nabídka *potvrzena* a "
"stává se salgsordre, kde může být platba získána okamžitě nebo do určitého "
"počtu dnů, týdnů, měsíců atd."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:None
msgid "A completed example of a new subscription quotation in Odoo."
msgstr "Dokončený příklad nové nabídky abonnementu v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:275
msgid ""
"Define different invoice and delivery addresses by enabling "
"the :doc:`Customer Addresses </applications/finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices/customer_addresses>` feature."
msgstr ""
"Definujte různé fakturační a dodací adresy povolením funkce :doc:`Adresy "
"zákazníka </applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/"
"customer_addresses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:281
msgid "Confirmation"
msgstr "Bekræftelse"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:283
msgid ""
"Send the quotation to the customer for confirmation by clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Send By Email`, or confirm it immediately by clicking "
"on :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Odešlete nabídku zákazníkovi k potvrzení kliknutím na :guilabel:`Odeslat e-"
"mailem`, nebo ji potvrďte okamžitě kliknutím na :guilabel:`Potvrdit`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:287
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Preview` to preview the customer portal where the "
"customer can view their quotation, sign and pay it, and communicate with you."
msgstr ""
"Klikněte na :guilabel:`Náhled` pro náhled zákaznického portálu, kde může "
"zákazník zobrazit svou nabídku, podepsat a zaplatit ji a komunikovat s vámi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:290
msgid ""
"If an :guilabel:`Online signature` or :guilabel:`Online payment` is required "
"to confirm the quotation, set the checkboxes next to either (or both) of "
"these labels in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, under the :guilabel:`SALES` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Pokud je k potvrzení nabídky vyžadován :guilabel:`Online podpis` "
"nebo :guilabel:`Online platba`, zaškrtněte políčka vedle jednoho (nebo obou) "
"těchto štítků na kartě :guilabel:`Ostatní informace`, pod "
"sekcí :guilabel:`SALG`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:295
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/payments/online`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions.rst:296
msgid ""
":doc:`Payment providers and payment methods </applications/finance/"
"payment_providers>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Poskytovatelé plateb a platební metody </applications/finance/"
"payment_providers>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:3
msgid "Subscriptions and automatic payments"
msgstr "Abonnementer og automatiske betalinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:5
msgid ""
"By default, the **Subscriptions** app will automatically generate quotations "
"and invoices for customers, but it can also support automatic payments. "
"Setting up automatic payments requires additional configuration, including "
"choosing an automatic payment provider and either setting up a customer "
"portal or an **eCommerce** website. Here's an overview of how to get started."
msgstr ""
"Som standard vil **Abonnementer**-appen automatisk generere tilbud og "
"fakturaer til kunder, men den kan også understøtte automatiske betalinger. "
"Opsætning af automatiske betalinger kræver yderligere konfiguration, "
"herunder valg af en automatisk betalingsudbyder og enten opsætning af en "
"kundeportal eller en **Webshop**-hjemmeside. Her er en oversigt over, "
"hvordan du kommer i gang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:11
