#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:24
msgid "Here are the steps to setting up automatic payments."
msgstr "Her er trinene til opsætning af automatiske betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:26
msgid "Choose a payment provider that supports tokenization."
msgstr "Vælg en betalingsudbyder, der understøtter tokenisering."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:27
msgid ""
"Follow the provider's own setup guide to create an account and begin "
"configuring their API credentials in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Følg udbyderens egen opsætningsvejledning for at oprette en konto og begynde "
"at konfigurere deres API-legitimationsoplysninger i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:29
msgid ":ref:`Enable <payment_providers/add_new>` the payment provider."
msgstr ":ref:`Aktiver <payment_providers/add_new>` betalingsudbyderen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:30
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure the payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>` for "
"the chosen payment provider."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurer betalingsmetoderne <payment_providers/payment_methods>` for "
"den valgte betalingsudbyder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:32
msgid ""
":ref:`Configure the tokenization <payment_providers/tokenization>` for the "
"chosen payment provider."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Konfigurer tokenisering <payment_providers/tokenization>` for den "
"valgte betalingsudbyder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:36
msgid "How customers can set up automatic payments"
msgstr "Sådan kan kunder oprette automatiske betalinger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:38
msgid ""
"Once these steps are complete, payment providers will be able to create "
"tokens with customers' saved payment details during the checkout process. "
"Saved payment details can then be used for future online or recurring "
"subscription charges. Customers can also log into their :doc:`customer "
"portal <../../general/users/user_portals>` and enter their payment "
"information there."
msgstr ""
"Når disse trin er gennemført, vil betalingsudbydere kunne oprette tokens med "
"kunders gemte betalingsoplysninger under betalingsprocessen. Gemte "
"betalingsoplysninger kan derefter bruges til fremtidige online- eller "
"tilbagevendende abonnementsgebyrer. Kunder kan også logge ind på "
"deres :doc:`kundeportal <../../general/users/user_portals>` og indtaste "
"deres betalingsoplysninger der."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:43
msgid ""
"Some payment providers will automatically save customers' payment "
"information as part of the checkout process. Others will give them the "
"option to save their information for future payments. If customers choose "
"not to save their payment information, they will not be able to make "
"automatic payments."
msgstr ""
"Nogle betalingsudbydere gemmer automatisk kunders betalingsoplysninger som "
"en del af betalingsprocessen. Andre giver dem mulighed for at gemme deres "
"oplysninger til fremtidige betalinger. Hvis kunder vælger ikke at gemme "
"deres betalingsoplysninger, kan de ikke foretage automatiske betalinger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:49
msgid ""
"Building an **eCommerce** website requires the :doc:`Website <../../websites/"
"website>` app."
msgstr ""
"Oprettelse af en **Webshop** kræver :doc:`Hjemmeside <../../websites/"
"website>`-appen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:52
msgid "What happens if an automatic payment fails?"
msgstr "Hvad sker der, hvis en automatisk betaling mislykkes?"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:54
msgid "When an automatic payment fails, the sales order is updated with:"
msgstr "Når en automatisk betaling mislykkes, opdateres salgsordren med:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:56
msgid "a :guilabel:`Payment Failure` tag"
msgstr "et :guilabel:`Betalingsfejl`-mærke"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:57
msgid ""
"the :guilabel:`Contract in exception` checkbox ticked (in "
"the :guilabel:`Subscription` section of the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kontrakt med undtagelse`-afkrydsningsfeltet markeret "
"(i :guilabel:`Abonnement`-sektionen på fanen :guilabel:`Anden info`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:60
msgid ""
"Being marked :guilabel:`Contract in exception` prevents scheduled actions "
"from running, which keeps the system from accidentally double-charging the "
"customer if the automatic payment actually went through. Because the status "
"of the payment failed to register with the system, users must manually check "
"if the payment has been made before automatic payments and other scheduled "
"actions can resume."
msgstr ""
"Označení :guilabel:`Smlouva ve výjimce` brání spuštění naplánovaných akcí, "
"což zabraňuje systému v náhodném dvojím účtování zákazníkovi, pokud "
"automatická platba skutečně proběhla. Protože se stav platby nepodařilo "
"zaregistrovat v systému, musí uživatelé ručně zkontrolovat, zda byla platba "
"provedena, než budou moci pokračovat automatické platby a další naplánované "
"akce."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:65
msgid ""
"To do this, navigate to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Subscriptions "
"--> Quotations`. Click into the desired subscription, then check the Chatter "
"to see if the payment was made."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li to provést, přejděte na :menuselection:`Aplikace Abonnementer --> "
"Abonnementer --> Cenové nabídky`. Klikněte na požadované předplatné a poté "
"zkontrolujte Chatter, zda byla platba provedena."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:68
msgid ""
"If the payment *was not* made, first enter :doc:`developer mode <../../"
"general/developer_mode>`. Then, click the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, and "
"untick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Contract in exception`. Reload the "
"sales order and confirm that the :guilabel:`Payment Failure` tag is gone."
msgstr ""
"Pokud platba *nebyla* provedena, nejprve vstupte do :doc:`vývojářského "
"režimu <../../general/developer_mode>`. Poté klikněte na "
"kartu :guilabel:`Ostatní informace` a zrušte zaškrtnutí políčka "
"vedle :guilabel:`Smlouva ve výjimce`. Znovu načtěte prodejní objednávku a "
"ověřte, že štítek :guilabel:`Selhání platby` zmizel."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:72
msgid ""
"If the payment *was* made, a new invoice must be made and posted manually. "
"This automatically updates the next invoice date of the subscription. Once "
"the invoice is created, enter :doc:`developer mode <../../general/"
"developer_mode>` and navigate to the new sales order. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab, and untick the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Contract in exception`. Reload the sales order and confirm "
"that the :guilabel:`Payment Failure` tag is gone."
msgstr ""
"Pokud platba *byla* provedena, musí být nová faktura vytvořena a zaúčtována "
"ručně. Tím se automaticky aktualizuje datum další faktury předplatného. "
"Jakmile je faktura vytvořena, vstupte do :doc:`vývojářského režimu <../../"
"general/developer_mode>` a přejděte na novou prodejní objednávku. Klikněte "
"na kartu :guilabel:`Ostatní informace` a zrušte zaškrtnutí políčka "
"vedle :guilabel:`Smlouva ve výjimce`. Znovu načtěte prodejní objednávku a "
"ověřte, že štítek :guilabel:`Selhání platby` zmizel."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:None
msgid ""
"The contract in exception option selected with the payment failure tag shown."
msgstr ""
"Vybraná možnost smlouvy ve výjimce se zobrazeným štítkem selhání platby."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:81
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Contract in exception` option selected with "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Failure` tag shown."
msgstr ""
"Vybraná možnost :guilabel:`Smlouva ve výjimce` se zobrazeným "
"štítkem :guilabel:`Selhání platby`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:84
msgid ""
"In both cases, once the :guilabel:`Contract in exception` checkbox is no "
"longer ticked, Odoo handles renewals automatically again. If the "
"subscription remains in :guilabel:`Payment Failure`, it is ignored by Odoo "
"until the sales order is closed."
msgstr ""
"I begge tilfælde, når afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Kontrakt i undtagelse` "
"ikke længere er markeret, håndterer Odoo fornyelser automatisk igen. Hvis "
"abonnementet forbliver i :guilabel:`Betalingsfejl`, ignoreres det af Odoo, "
"indtil salgsordren lukkes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:89
msgid ":doc:`../../finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:90
msgid ":doc:`../../general/users/user_portals`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/users/user_portals`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:3
msgid "Close subscriptions"
msgstr "Uzavřít abonnementy"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Subscriptions** app provides flexibility for businesses to decide "
"whether customers can self-manage their subscriptions, or restrict that "
"ability entirely."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Abonnementer**-appen giver virksomheder fleksibilitet til at "
"beslutte, om kunder selv kan administrere deres abonnementer, eller om denne "
"mulighed skal begrænses helt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:9
msgid ""
"A subscription must have been invoiced before it can be closed. "
"Subscriptions that have not yet been invoiced may be cancelled instead."
msgstr ""
"Et abonnement skal være faktureret, før det kan lukkes. Abonnementer, der "
"endnu ikke er faktureret, kan i stedet annulleres."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:15
msgid ""
"To allow customers to close their own subscriptions using their user portal, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Configuration --> "
"Recurring Plans`. From there, either create a new plan by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New` or select an existing one to modify it."
msgstr ""
"For at give kunder mulighed for selv at lukke deres abonnementer via deres "
"brugerportal skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Abonnementer-app --> "
"Konfiguration --> Tilbagevendende planer`. Derfra kan du enten oprette en ny "
"plan ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` eller vælge en eksisterende plan for at "
"ændre den."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:19
msgid ""
"Once on the :guilabel:`Recurring Plans` form, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Closable` option in the :guilabel:`Self-Service` section. "
"This adds a drop-down menu that allows plans to be closed either on the date "
"of the user's choosing or at the end of the current renewal period."
msgstr ""
"Når du er på :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende planer`-formularen, skal du "
"aktivere :guilabel:`Kan lukkes`-indstillingen i :guilabel:`Selvbetjening`-"
"afsnittet. Dette tilføjer en rullemenü, der gør det muligt at lukke planer "
"enten på en dato efter brugerens valg eller ved udgangen af den aktuelle "
"fornyelsesperiode."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Closable option enabled and displaying the drop-down menu in Odoo "
"Subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Indstillingen Kan lukkes aktiveret og viser rullemenuen i Odoo Abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:30
msgid ""
"The methods available for closing a subscription depend on "
"users' :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`. Users with "
"administrator access rights to the Odoo database can close the subscription "
"from within the **Subscriptions** app. External users must use "
"their :doc:`user portal <../../general/users/user_portals>`."
msgstr ""
"De tilgængelige metoder til at lukke et abonnementafhænger af "
"brugernes :doc:`adgangsrettigheder <../../general/users/access_rights>`. "
"Brugere med administratoradgangsrettigheder til Odoo-databasen kan lukke "
"abonnementet inde fra **Abonnementer**-appen. Eksterne brugere skal bruge "
"deres :doc:`brugerportal <../../general/users/user_portals>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:36
msgid "With administrator access rights"
msgstr "Med administratoradgangsrettigheder"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:38
msgid ""
"After a quotation for a subscription product has been confirmed, it becomes "
"a sales order, and the subscription status changes to :guilabel:`In "
"Progress`. At that point, the subscription may be closed."
msgstr ""
"Efter at et tilbud på et abonnementsprodukt er blevet bekræftet, bliver det "
"til en salgsordre, og abonnementsstatus ændres til :guilabel:`I gang`. På "
"det tidspunkt kan abonnementet lukkes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:42
msgid ""
"From the dashboard, open the :menuselection:`Subscriptions` app. By default, "
"the **Subscriptions** dashboard displays both :guilabel:`In Progress` "
"and :guilabel:`Paused` subscriptions. Open an in-progress subscription."
msgstr ""
"Fra dashboardet skal du åbne appen :menuselection:`Abonnementer`. Som "
"standard viser dashboardet **Abonnementer** både :guilabel:`I gang` "
"og :guilabel:`Sat på pause` abonnementer. Åbn et abonnement, der er i gang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:46
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Close` button is at the top of the subscription order. "
"Clicking it opens the *Close Subscription* form, allowing an administrator "
"to enter the date when the subscription is to be closed in "
"the :guilabel:`When` field and select the reason for closing from the drop-"
"down menu of options in the :guilabel:`Reason` field. Custom reasons may be "
"created by opening the :guilabel:`Reason` drop-down and "
"choosing :guilabel:`Search more...`"
msgstr ""
"Knappen :guilabel:`Luk` findes øverst i abonnementsordren. Når du klikker på "
"den, åbnes formularen *Luk abonnement*, hvor en administrator kan indtaste "
"datoen for, hvornår abonnementet skal lukkes i feltet :guilabel:`Hvornår`, "
"og vælge årsagen til lukning fra rullemenuen med valgmuligheder i "
"feltet :guilabel:`Årsag`. Brugerdefinerede årsager kan oprettes ved at åbne "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Årsag` og vælge :guilabel:`Søg efter mere...`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:52
msgid ""
"When the desired :guilabel:`Reason` is entered, click the :guilabel:`Submit` "
"button. Clicking :guilabel:`Submit` on the :guilabel:`Close` form updates "
"the chatter with the reason for closing. Once it's been closed, "
"a :guilabel:`Churned` banner appears on the subscription order and the "
"chatter reflects the subscription's updated status, end date, and reason for "
"closure."
msgstr ""
"Når den ønskede :guilabel:`Årsag` er indtastet, skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Send`. Når du klikker på :guilabel:`Send` i "
"formularen :guilabel:`Luk`, opdateres chatteren med årsagen til lukning. Når "
"det er blevet lukket, vises et banner med :guilabel:`Churned` på "
"abonnementsordren, og chatteren afspejler abonnementets opdaterede status, "
"slutdato og årsag til lukning."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:None
msgid ""
"A churned sales order for a closed subscription in Odoo Subscriptions "
"showing the banner\n"
"and the chatter."
msgstr ""
"En churned salgsordre for et lukket abonnement i Odoo Abonnementer, der "
"viser banneret\n"
"og chatteren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:62
msgid "Customer view"
msgstr "Kundevisning"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:65
msgid ""
"As an administrator, the ability to visualize what users see when managing "
"their subscriptions is accessible via the :guilabel:`Preview` button at the "
"top of each subscription sales order."
msgstr ""
"Som administrator er muligheden for at visualisere, hvad brugere ser, når de "
"administrerer deres abonnementer, tilgængelig via "
"knappen :guilabel:`Forhåndsvisning` øverst i hver abonnementssalgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:68
msgid ""
"In the user portal, subscriptions may be managed by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Subscriptions` button on the home page. Clicking this button "
"takes the user to the :guilabel:`Subscriptions` page, where they can see a "
"list of all subscriptions associated with their account, including those "
"that are currently closed."
msgstr ""
"I brugerportalen kan abonnementer administreres ved at klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Abonnementer` på startsiden. Når du klikker på denne "
"knap, kommer brugeren til siden :guilabel:`Abonnementer`, hvor de kan se en "
"liste over alle abonnementer, der er tilknyttet deres konto, herunder dem, "
"der i øjeblikket er lukket."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:73
msgid ""
"Clicking a subscription opens the details page for that subscription, which "
"includes a :guilabel:`Close Subscription` button. Clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Close Subscription` button opens a :guilabel:`Close "
"Subscription` pop-up, where users must select from a list of reasons why "
"they are choosing to close the subscription."
msgstr ""
"Når du klikker på et abonnement, åbnes detaljsiden for det pågældende "
"abonnement, som indeholder en knap :guilabel:`Luk abonnement`. Når du "
"klikker på knappen :guilabel:`Luk abonnement`, åbnes en pop op "
"med :guilabel:`Luk abonnement`, hvor brugere skal vælge fra en liste over "
"årsager til, hvorfor de vælger at lukke abonnementet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:None
msgid ""
"The close subscription pop-up window customers see when closing a "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Vinduet med lukning af abonnement, som kunder ser, når de lukker et "
"abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:82
msgid ""
"Users must choose a pre-configured reason why the subscription is being "
"closed. They **cannot** enter a custom reason from the user portal. "
"Administrators can create custom reasons for users to choose from by logging "
"into the database and navigating to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> "
"Configuration --> Close Reasons`."
msgstr ""
"Brugere skal vælge en forudkonfigureret årsag til, at abonnementet lukkes. "
"De kan **ikke** indtaste en brugerdefineret årsag fra brugerportalen. "
"Administratorer kan oprette brugerdefinerede årsager, som brugere kan vælge "
"imellem, ved at logge ind i databasen og navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer app --> Konfiguration --> Lukkeårsager`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:87
msgid ""
"Once the customer has chosen a reason for closing the subscription, they can "
"click the :guilabel:`Submit` button on the pop-up window. Upon closure, the "
"subscription order in the user portal is labeled :guilabel:`Closed`. Within "
"the database, the subscription is marked *Churned*, and the specified reason "
"for closure is added to the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Når kunden har valgt en årsag til at lukke abonnementet, kan de klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Send` i pop op-vinduet. Ved lukning er abonnementsordren "
"i brugerportalen mærket :guilabel:`Lukket`. I databasen er abonnementet "
"markeret som *Churned*, og den angivne årsag til lukning tilføjes til "
"chatteren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/closing.rst:93
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:166
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:71
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:79
