msgstr ":doc:`../subscriptions`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:3
msgid "Subscriptions in the eCommerce shop"
msgstr "Abonnementer i webshop"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:5
msgid ""
"Subscription products can be sold in Odoo **eCommerce** app shops just like "
"regular sales products."
msgstr ""
"Abonnementsprodukter kan sælges i **Webshop**-appens butikker ligesom "
"almindelige salgsprodukter."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:7
msgid ""
"To begin selling subscription products in an *eCommerce* shop, "
"first :doc:`configure the product <../subscriptions>` as a regular recurring "
"sales product. After configuration is complete, click the :guilabel:`Go to "
"Website` smart button on the product's form to navigate to the product's "
"**eCommerce** page."
msgstr ""
"For at begynde at sælge abonnementsprodukter i en *Webshop*-butik skal du "
"først :doc:`konfigurere produktet <../subscriptions>` som et almindeligt "
"tilbagevendende salgsprodukt. Når konfigurationen er færdig, skal du klikke "
"på smartknappen :guilabel:`Gå til hjemmeside` på produktets formular for at "
"navigere til produktets **Webshop**-side."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:12
msgid ""
"From here, review the subscription product and its recurring periods. Then, "
"toggle the switch in the upper-right corner from :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"to :guilabel:`Published`. Once published, the subscription product is "
"available to purchase on the eCommerce website, along with options for the "
"configured recurring periods."
msgstr ""
"Herfra kan du gennemgå abonnementsproduktet og dets tilbagevendende "
"perioder. Skift derefter knappen i øverste højre hjørne fra :guilabel:`Ikke "
"udgivet` til :guilabel:`Udgivet`. Når produktet er udgivet, er "
"abonnementsproduktet tilgængeligt til køb på webshop-hjemmesiden sammen med "
"muligheder for de konfigurerede tilbagevendende perioder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:None
msgid ""
"Subscription product on eCommerce website showing different recurring "
"periods."
msgstr ""
"Abonnementsprodukt på webshop-hjemmeside, der viser forskellige "
"tilbagevendende perioder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:21
msgid ":doc:`Configure subscription products <../subscriptions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Konfigurere abonnementsprodukter <../subscriptions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/ecommerce.rst:22
msgid ":doc:`Product variants <../sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Produktvarianter <../sales/products_prices/products/variants>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:3
msgid "Renew subscriptions"
msgstr "Forny abonnementer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:5
msgid ""
"Subscription renewal is the process customers follow when they willingly "
"choose to continue a subscription product or service. Subscribers go through "
"the renewal process at different intervals -- weekly, monthly, annually, "
"etc. -- depending on the duration of the agreed-upon contract. Most "
"companies that offer subscriptions prefer to automate the renewal process "
"for customers. However, manual subscription renewals are still used in some "
"cases."
msgstr ""
"Obnovení předplatného je proces, kterým zákazníci dobrovolně pokračují v "
"odběru produktu nebo služby. Předplatitelé procházejí procesem obnovení v "
"různých intervalech – týdně, měsíčně, ročně atd. – v závislosti na délce "
"dohodnuté smlouvy. Většina společností, které nabízejí předplatná, dává "
"přednost automatizaci procesu obnovení pro zákazníky. V některých případech "
"se však stále používají ruční obnovení předplatného."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:11
msgid ""
"With the Odoo **Subscriptions** application, a company can manage all of its "
"subscriptions in one place. Renewals can be processed automatically or "
"manually, include additional products or upsells per renewal order, and be "
"filtered in batch views to locate customers who need to renew their "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"S aplikací **Abonnementer** od Odoo může společnost spravovat všechna svá "
"předplatná na jednom místě. Obnovení lze zpracovávat automaticky nebo ručně, "
"zahrnovat dodatečné produkty nebo upselly při každé objednávce obnovení a "
"filtrovat je v dávkových zobrazeních pro vyhledání zákazníků, kteří "
"potřebují obnovit svá předplatná."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:17
msgid "Create a renewal manually"
msgstr "Vytvoření obnovení ručně"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:19
msgid ""
"In order to create a renewal quotation, there are certain prerequisites that "
"a subscription must meet."
msgstr ""
"Aby bylo možné vytvořit nabídku na obnovení, musí předplatné splňovat určité "
"předpoklady."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:22
msgid "A quotation with a subscription product must be confirmed."
msgstr "Cenová nabídka s produktem předplatného musí být potvrzena."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:23
msgid "A configured *recurring plan* must be selected."
msgstr "Musí být vybrán nakonfigurovaný *opakující se plán*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:24
msgid ""
"Payment from the customer for the initial subscription must be invoiced and "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"Platba od zákazníka za počáteční předplatné musí být vyfakturována a "
"zaregistrována."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:26
msgid ""
"To check if an existing subscription quotation meets the prerequisites, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Subscriptions --> "
"Quotations` and select the desired quotation from the list. Properly "
"configured subscriptions show as being in the :guilabel:`Sales Order` stage, "
"have an :guilabel:`In Progress` tag, and have the :guilabel:`Renew` button "
"in the row of buttons directly above the order form."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li zkontrolovat, zda existující cenová nabídka předplatného splňuje "
"předpoklady, přejděte na :menuselection:`Aplikace Abonnementer --> "
"Abonnementer --> Cenové nabídky` a ze seznamu vyberte požadovanou cenovou "
"nabídku. Správně nakonfigurovaná předplatná se zobrazují ve "
"fázi :guilabel:`Salgsordre`, mají štítek :guilabel:`Probíhá` a mají "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Obnovit` v řádku tlačítek přímo nad formulářem "
"objednávky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:None
msgid "Renew button on subscription sales order with Odoo Subscriptions."
msgstr "Forny-knap på salgsordre for abonnement med Odoo Abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:36
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Renew` button is clicked, Odoo instantly presents a new "
"renewal quotation, complete with a :guilabel:`Renewal Quotation` tag. "
"Important reference information like the start date and next invoice date "
"are automatically added to the renewal quotation's chatter."
msgstr ""
"Po kliknutí na tlačítko :guilabel:`Obnovit` Odoo okamžitě zobrazí novou "
"cenovou nabídku na obnovení se štítkem :guilabel:`Nabídka na obnovení`. Do "
"chatteru nabídky na obnovení jsou automaticky přidány důležité referenční "
"informace, jako je datum zahájení a datum další faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:40
msgid ""
"From here, follow the standard sales flow to :ref:`confirm the quotation "
"<sales/sales_quotations/send-and-confirm>`, :doc:`invoice the order <../../"
"sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy>`, and :ref:`register payment "
"<finance/accounting/register-payment-invoice-bill>`."
msgstr ""
"Odtud postupujte podle standardního prodejního procesu, :ref:`potvrďte "
"cenovou nabídku <sales/sales_quotations/send-and-"
"confirm>`, :doc:`vyfakturujte objednávku <../../sales/sales/invoicing/"
"invoicing_policy>` a :ref:`zaregistrujte platbu <finance/accounting/register-"
"payment-invoice-bill>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:45
msgid ""
"Once the renewal quotation is confirmed, it becomes a sales order and "
"a :icon:`fa-usd` :guilabel:`Sales History` smart button appears at the top "
"of the page. When the :icon:`fa-usd` :guilabel:`Sales History` smart button "
"is clicked, Odoo loads a new page showcasing the different sales orders "
"attached to this subscription, along with their "
"individual :guilabel:`Subscription Status`."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile je nabídka na obnovení potvrzena, stane se z ní prodejní objednávka "
"a v horní části stránky se zobrazí chytré tlačítko :icon:`fa-"
"usd` :guilabel:`Historie prodeje`. Po kliknutí na chytré tlačítko :icon:`fa-"
"usd` :guilabel:`Historie prodeje` Odoo načte novou stránku zobrazující různé "
"prodejní objednávky připojené k tomuto předplatnému spolu s jejich "
"individuálním :guilabel:`Stavem předplatného`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:None
msgid "Renewal quotation in the Odoo Subscriptions application."
msgstr "Fornyelsestilbud i Odoo Abonnementer-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:73
msgid ":doc:`../sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales/sales_quotations/create_quotations`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/renewals.rst:58
#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:74
msgid ":doc:`../sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:3
msgid "Subscription reports"
msgstr "Abonnementsrapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:8
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Subscriptions** app provides a series of reporting pages to help "
"companies analyze how subscriptions are performing. There are four different "
"reports: *Subscriptions Analysis*, *Retention Analysis*, *MRR Breakdown*, "
"and *MRR Analysis*."
msgstr ""
"Aplikace Odoo **Abonnementer** poskytuje řadu reportovacích stránek, které "
"pomáhají firmám analyzovat výkonnost abonnementer. Existují čtyři různé "
"reporty: *Analýza abonnementer*, *Analýza udržení*, *Rozpis MRR* a *Analýza "
"MRR*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:12
msgid ""
"Each report is viewed in its own dedicated reporting page, and shares common "
"elements with the others, as well as unique elements."
msgstr ""
"Každý report je zobrazen na vlastní vyhrazené stránce a sdílí s ostatními "
"společné i unikátní prvky."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:16
msgid "Reporting page elements"
msgstr "Elementer på rapportsiden"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:18
msgid "The following sections describe elements found on each reporting page."
msgstr "Følgende afsnit beskriver elementer, der findes på hver rapportside."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:23
msgid ""
"*Filters* are used to narrow down metrics to show specific analytics. *Group "
"By* is used to gather the data from specific sections into groups for more "
"organized analysis. Visit the :doc:`Search, filter, and group records <../../"
"essentials/search>` documentation for more information about custom filters "
"and groups."
msgstr ""
"*Filtry* slouží k zúžení metrik pro zobrazení specifických analýz. *Seskupit "
"podle* slouží ke seskupení dat z konkrétních sekcí pro organizovanější "
"analýzu. Pro více informací o vlastních filtrech a skupinách navštivte "
"dokumentaci :doc:`Vyhledávání, filtrování a seskupování záznamů <../../"
"essentials/search>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:34
msgid ""
":guilabel:`My Subscriptions`: Show subscriptions created by the current "
"database user."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Moje abonnementer`: Zobrazit abonnementer vytvořené aktuálním "
"uživatelem database."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotations`: Show subscriptions that are currently in the "
"*Quotation* stage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nabídky`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které jsou aktuálně ve fázi "
"*Nabídka*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:36
msgid ""
":guilabel:`In Progress`: Show subscriptions that are currently in the *In "
"Progress* stage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Probíhající`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které jsou aktuálně ve fázi "
"*Probíhající*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Paused`: Show subscriptions that are currently in the *Paused* "
"stage."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pozastavené`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které jsou aktuálně ve fázi "
"*Pozastavené*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:38
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Churned`: Show subscriptions that are currently marked *Churned*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zrušené`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které jsou aktuálně označené "
"jako *Zrušené*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To renew`: Show subscriptions that are currently marked *To "
"renew*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`K obnovení`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které jsou aktuálně označené "
"jako *K obnovení*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurring`: Shows subscriptions that renew at specific intervals."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opakované`: Zobrazit abonnementer, které se obnovují v "
"konkrétních intervalech."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:41
msgid ":guilabel:`Non-recurring`: Shows one-time subscriptions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Neopakované`: Zobrazit jednorázové abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`First contract date`: Show subscriptions with a specific first "
"contract date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum první smlouvy`: Zobrazit abonnementer s konkrétním datem "
"první smlouvy."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next Invoice Date`: Show subscriptions with a specific next "
"invoice date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum další faktury`: Zobrazit abonnementer s konkrétním datem "
"další faktury."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`End Date`: Show subscriptions with a specific end date."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum ukončení`: Zobrazit abonnementer s konkrétním datem "
"ukončení."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subscription State`: Groups the results by the current state of "
"each subscription (Quotation, In Progress, Churned, etc.)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stav abonnementu`: Seskupí výsledky podle aktuálního stavu "
"každého abonnementu (Nabídka, Probíhající, Zrušené atd.)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: Groups the results by the Sales Team to whom a "
"subscription is assigned."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Prodejní tým`: Seskupí výsledky podle prodejního týmu, kterému je "
"abonnement přiřazen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: Groups the results by the Salesperson to whom a "
"subscription is assigned."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sælger`: Grupperer resultaterne efter den sælger, som et "
"abonnement er tildelt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Referrer`: Groups the results by the referrer from which a "
"subscription originated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Henviser`: Grupperer resultaterne efter den henviser, som et "
"abonnement stammer fra."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer`: Groups the results by the customer to which a "
"subscription belongs."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kunde`: Grupperer resultaterne efter den kunde, som et abonnement "
"tilhører."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Country`: Groups the results by the country from which a "
"subscription originated."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Land`: Grupperer resultaterne efter det land, som et abonnement "
"stammer fra."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:62
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Template`: Groups the results by the quotation template used as "
"the basis for the subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skabelon`: Grupperer resultaterne efter den tilbudsskabelon, der "
"bruges som grundlag for abonnementet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Plan`: Groups the results by the recurring plan type of the "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plan`: Grupperer resultaterne efter abonnementets tilbagevendende "
"plantype."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product`: Groups the results by the products included in the "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Produkt`: Grupperer resultaterne efter de produkter, der er "
"inkluderet i abonnementet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`First Contract Date`: Groups the results by the date the "
"subscription was created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Første kontraktdato`: Grupperer resultaterne efter den dato, hvor "
"abonnementet blev oprettet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Next Invoice Date`: Groups the results by the next invoice date "
"of the subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Næste fakturadato`: Grupperer resultaterne efter abonnementets "
"næste fakturadato."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Date`: Groups the results by end date of the subscription, "
"whether or not the subscription has ended."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slutdato`: Grupperer resultaterne efter abonnementets slutdato, "
"uanset om abonnementet er afsluttet eller ej."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom Group`: Allows the database user to create a custom group "
"with numerous options."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Brugerdefineret gruppe`: Giver databasebrugeren mulighed for at "
"oprette en brugerdefineret gruppe med adskillige muligheder."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:73
msgid "Views"
msgstr "Visninger"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:75
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Subscription Analysis`, :guilabel:`MRR Breakdown`, "
"and :guilabel:`MRR Analysis` reporting pages, three different view options "
"are located in the upper-right corner. There are no other view options "
"available on the :guilabel:`Retention Analysis` reporting page."
msgstr ""
"På rapporteringssiderne :guilabel:`Abonnementsanalyse`, :guilabel:`MRR-"
"opdeling` og :guilabel:`MRR-analyse` findes tre forskellige "
"visningsmuligheder i øverste højre hjørne. Der er ingen andre "
"visningsmuligheder tilgængelige på "
"rapporteringssiden :guilabel:`Fastholdelsesanalyse`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:79
msgid "The available view options are:"
msgstr "De tilgængelige visningsmuligheder er:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:81
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`Graph` view: Displays the total number of "
"subscriptions in a graph, allowing for quick visual comparisons of "
"subscriptions. This is the default view across the reporting pages."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`Graf`-visning: Viser det samlede antal "
"abonnementer i en graf, hvilket muliggør hurtige visuelle sammenligninger af "
"abonnementer. Dette er standardvisningen på tværs af rapporteringssiderne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:84
msgid ""
":icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot` view: Displays the detailed Monthly "
"Recurring Revenue by both stage and month in a customizable table. This can "
"be modified to display information into more detailed categories, such as "
"salesperson, referrer, and more."
msgstr ""
":icon:`oi-view-pivot` :guilabel:`Pivot`-visning: Viser den detaljerede "
"månedlige tilbagevendende omsætning efter både fase og måned i en "
"tilpasselig tabel. Dette kan ændres til at vise information i mere "
"detaljerede kategorier, såsom sælger, henviser og mere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:87
msgid ""
":icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`List` view: Displays the subscriptions in a "
"detailed list, allowing for easy viewing of detailed individual records."
msgstr ""
":icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`Liste`-visning: Viser abonnementerne i en "
"detaljeret liste, hvilket giver nem visning af detaljerede individuelle "
"poster."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:93
msgid ""
"The pivot view has its own metric-specific :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down "
"menu of data-related options to choose from when creating a subscriptions "
"report."
msgstr ""
"Pivotvisningen har sin egen målingsspecifikke rullemenu :guilabel:`Målinger` "
"med datarelaterede muligheder at vælge imellem, når man opretter en "
"abonnementsrapport."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:96
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Measures` button is clicked, a series of selectable "
"measures becomes available, via a drop-down menu. When any of the options "
"are selected from the :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down menu, the chosen "
"metrics related to that specific measure appear on the pivot table."
msgstr ""
"Når knappen :guilabel:`Målinger` klikkes, bliver en række valgbare målinger "
"tilgængelige via en rullemenu. Når en af mulighederne vælges fra "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Målinger`, vises de valgte metrics relateret til den "
"specifikke måling på pivottabellen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:100
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Subscriptions Analysis` page, those measures are:"
msgstr "På siden :guilabel:`Abonnementsanalyse` er disse målinger:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Expected Cost`: Measures the cost of the subscriptions for the "
"business as determined by the untaxed amount minus the margin."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forventet omkostning`: Måler omkostningen ved abonnementerne for "
"virksomheden som bestemt af det uafgiftspligtige beløb minus avancen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monthly Recurring`: Measures the gross monthly recurring revenue "
"for the subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Månedlig tilbagevendende`: Måler den bruttoindtægt for månedligt "
"tilbagevendende indtægter for abonnementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:105
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quantity`: Measures the number of products included in the "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antal`: Måler antallet af produkter inkluderet i abonnementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurring Revenue`: Measures the recurring revenue for the "
"subscriptions based on their next recurrence period (weekly, monthly, "
"annually, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tilbagevendende omsætning`: Måler den tilbagevendende omsætning "
"for abonnementerne baseret på deres næste gentagelsesperiode (ugentlig, "
"månedlig, årlig osv.)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:108
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Unit Price`: Measures the price for the business of each product "
"in the subscription."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Enhedspris`: Måler prisen for virksomheden for hvert produkt i "
"abonnementet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Untaxed Amount Delivered`: Measures the cost of the physical "
"products in the subscription that aren't subject to a tax and have been "
"delivered to the customer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ekskl. moms leveret beløb`: Måler omkostningerne for de fysiske "
"produkter i abonnementet, der ikke er underlagt moms, og som er blevet "
"leveret til kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:111
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Untaxed Total`: Measures the total cost of the products in the "
"subscription that aren't subject to a tax."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`I alt ekskl. moms`: Måler de samlede omkostninger for produkterne "
"i abonnementet, der ikke er underlagt moms."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:113
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Yearly Recurring`: Measures the projected yearly revenue for the "
"subscriptions, regardless of their recurrence period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Årligt tilbagevendende`: Måler den forventede årlige omsætning "
"for abonnementerne, uanset deres gentagelsesperiode."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:116
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`MRR Breakdown` and :guilabel:`MRR Analysis` pages, those "
"measures are:"
msgstr ""
"På siderne :guilabel:`MRR-opdeling` og :guilabel:`MRR-analyse` er disse "
"målinger:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active Subscriptions Change`: Measures the net change in active "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ændring i aktive abonnementer`: Måler nettoændringen i aktive "
"abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`ARR Change`: Measures the total change in annual recurring "
"revenue for all subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ARR-ændring`: Måler den samlede ændring i årlig tilbagevendende "
"omsætning for alle abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:121
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MRR Change`: Measures the total change in monthly recurring "
"revenue for all subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MRR-ændring`: Måler den samlede ændring i månedlig "
"tilbagevendende omsætning for alle abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:124
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Retention Analysis` page offers wholly unique measures, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"Siden :guilabel:`Fastholdsesanalyse` tilbyder helt unikke målinger, herunder:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Amount To Pay In POS`: Measures the amount to be paid in still-to-"
"be-invoiced subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Beløb til betaling i POS`: Måler det beløb, der skal betales i "
"endnu ikke fakturerede abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Margin`: Measures the total margin of the subscriptions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Margin`: Måler den samlede margin for abonnementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Prepayment percentage`: Measures the percentage of subscriptions "
"revenue that has been prepaid."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forudbetalingsprocent`: Måler procentdelen af "
"abonnementsomsætning, der er blevet forudbetalt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:131
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Weight`: Measures the shipping weight of physical "
"products included in the subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Forsendelsesvægt`: Måler forsendelsesmængden af fysiske produkter "
"inkluderet i abonnementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Count`: Measures the count of non-subscription products in the "
"subscriptions."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Antal`: Måler antallet af ikke-abonnementsprodukter i "
"abonnementerne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:136
msgid "Reporting pages"
msgstr "Rapportsider"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:138
msgid ""
"To access, analyze, and customize various reports related to subscriptions, "
"navigate to the :menuselection:`Subscriptions` app and click "
"the :guilabel:`Reporting` drop-down menu in the header to reveal the "
"following reporting pages:"
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til, analysere og tilpasse forskellige rapporter relateret "
"til abonnementer skal du navigere til appen :menuselection:`Abonnementer` og "
"klikke på rullemenuen :guilabel:`Rapportering` i overskriften for at afsløre "
"følgende rapporteringssider:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:142
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Subscriptions Analysis`: Accessible by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Reporting --> Subscriptions`. Users "
"can view specific data related to recurring subscriptions, quantity of "
"subscriptions, in-progress or paused subscriptions, and more. By default, "
"the :guilabel:`Subscriptions Analysis` page uses the :guilabel:`Graph` view "
"with the :guilabel:`Bar Chart` option and :guilabel:`Stacked` options "
"enabled. The :guilabel:`In Progress or Paused` filters "
"and :guilabel:`Recurring` grouping are also enabled by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Abonnementsanalyse`: Tilgængelig ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer-app --> Rapportering --> Abonnementer`. "
"Brugere kan se specifikke data relateret til tilbagevendende abonnementer, "
"antal abonnementer, igangværende eller pausede abonnementer og mere. Som "
"standard bruger siden :guilabel:`Abonnementsanalyse` "
"visningen :guilabel:`Graf` med indstillingen :guilabel:`Søjlediagram` og "
"indstillingen :guilabel:`Stablet` aktiveret. "
"Filtrene :guilabel:`Igangværende eller pauseret` og "
"grupperingen :guilabel:`Tilbagevendende` er også aktiveret som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:148
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Retention Analysis`: Accessible by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Reporting --> Retention`. "
"The :guilabel:`Retention Analysis` reporting page differs from the other "
"**Subscriptions** app reporting pages in that it does **not** provide any "
"additional view options. The data on this page is only presented in a "
"customizable data chart. The :guilabel:`Count` measure option is selected by "
"default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fastholdsesanalyse`: Tilgængelig ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer-app --> Rapportering --> Fastholdelse`. "
"Rapporteringssiden :guilabel:`Fastholdsesanalyse` adskiller sig fra de andre "
"rapporteringssider i appen **Abonnementer** ved, at den **ikke** tilbyder "
"yderligere visningsmuligheder. Dataene på denne side præsenteres kun i et "
"tilpasseligt datadiagram. Måleindstillingen :guilabel:`Antal` er valgt som "
"standard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MRR Breakdown`: Accessible by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Reporting --> MRR Breakdown`. This "
"page clearly divides |MRR| and |ARR| metrics for subscriptions into various "
"graphs, lists, and charts. By default, the data displayed on "
"the :guilabel:`MRR Breakdown` reporting page is in graph view with "
"the :guilabel:`Bar Chart` and :guilabel:`Stacked` options selected. "
"The :guilabel:`MRR Change` measure option is selected by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MRR-opdeling`: Tilgængelig ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer-app --> Rapportering --> MRR-opdeling`. "
"Denne side opdeler tydeligt |MRR| og |ARR|-metrics for abonnementer i "
"forskellige grafer, lister og diagrammer. Som standard vises dataene på "
"rapporteringssiden :guilabel:`MRR-opdeling` i grafvisning med "
"indstillingerne :guilabel:`Søjlediagram` og :guilabel:`Stablet` valgt. "
"Måleindstillingen :guilabel:`MRR-ændring` er valgt som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/reports.rst:158
msgid ""
":guilabel:`MRR Analysis`: Accessible by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Reporting --> MRR Analysis`. This "
"page offers a time-based collection of analytics showcasing how subscription "
"|MRR| and |ARR| have changed over the course of any given period of time. By "
"default, the data displayed on the :guilabel:`MRR Analysis` reporting page "
"is in graph view, with the :guilabel:`Line Chart`, :guilabel:`Stacked`, "
"and :guilabel:`Cumulative` options enabled. The :guilabel:`MRR Change` "
"measure option is selected by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`MRR-analyse`: Tilgængelig ved at navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Abonnementer-app --> Rapportering --> MRR-analyse`. "
"Denne side tilbyder en tidsbaseret samling af analyser, der viser, hvordan "
"abonnements-|MRR| og |ARR| har ændret sig over en given tidsperiode. Som "
"standard vises dataene på rapporteringssiden :guilabel:`MRR-analyse` i "
"grafvisning med "
"indstillingerne :guilabel:`Linjediagram`, :guilabel:`Stablet` "
"og :guilabel:`Kumulativ` aktiveret. Måleindstillingen :guilabel:`MRR-"
"ændring` er valgt som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:3
msgid "Subscriptions with deliveries"
msgstr "Abonnementer s dodávkami"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:5
msgid ""
"Subscriptions and subscription products are compatible with deliveries. With "
"some minor configuration, it is possible to offer customers subscriptions of "
"regularly delivered physical goods such as a meal delivery box or magazine."
msgstr ""
"Abonnementer a produkty pro předplatné jsou kompatibilní s dodávkami. S "
"menší konfigurací je možné zákazníkům nabídnout předplatné pravidelně "
"dodávaného fyzického zboží, jako je box s jídlem nebo časopis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:10
msgid ""
"An independent coffee shop offers local customers a monthly coffee bean "
"subscription service. Each month, Odoo automatically generates a sales order "
"and invoice in the Sales app and a delivery order in the Inventory app to "
"ensure that the coffee beans get delivered to subscribed customers."
msgstr ""
"Nezávislá kavárna nabízí místním zákazníkům měsíční předplatné zrnkové kávy. "
"Každý měsíc Odoo automaticky vygeneruje salgsordre a fakturu v aplikaci Salg "
"a leveringsordre v aplikaci Lager, aby zajistila, že se zrnková káva doručí "
"předplaceným zákazníkům."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:18
msgid ""
"Selling deliverable subscription products requires that two different apps "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`: the **Subscriptions** app and the "
"**Inventory** app. The **Subscriptions** app allows for the creation and "
"management of subscription products while the **Inventory** app, in addition "
"to managing inventory, allows for adding shipping information to quotations "
"and automatically creating delivery orders when invoices are created."
msgstr ""
"Prodej dodatelných produktů předplatného vyžaduje, aby "
"byly :ref:`nainstalovány <general/install>` dvě různé aplikace: aplikace "
"**Abonnementer** a aplikace **Lager**. Aplikace **Abonnementer** umožňuje "
"vytváření a správu produktů předplatného, zatímco aplikace **Lager** kromě "
"správy inventáře umožňuje přidání informací o dopravě do nabídek a "
"automatické vytváření dodacích příkazů při vytvoření faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:24
msgid ""
"After installing both **Subscriptions** and **Inventory**, enter the "
"**Settings** app, search for \"delivery\", and tick the :doc:`Delivery "
"Methods </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration>` box in the :guilabel:`Inventory` section. This allows "
"for adding the cost of shipping to quotations and invoices."
msgstr ""
"Po instalaci aplikací **Abonnementer** i **Lager** vstupte do aplikace "
"**Nastavení**, vyhledejte „dodávka\" a zaškrtněte políčko :doc:`Způsoby "
"dodání </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration>` v sekci :guilabel:`Lager`. To umožňuje přidat náklady "
"na dopravu do nabídek a faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:31
msgid "Creating a subscription delivery product"
msgstr "Vytvoření produktu předplatného s dodávkou"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:33
msgid ""
"To create a deliverable subscription product, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Subscriptions app --> Products --> Products`. Click an "
"existing product or create a new one and set the :guilabel:`Product Type` to "
"`Goods`. Click the :guilabel:`Recurring prices` tab and :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`. Choose an existing :guilabel:`Recurring plan` or create a new one, "
"and add a :guilabel:`Pricelist`."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li vytvořit dodatelný produkt předplatného, přejděte "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikace Abonnementer --> Produkty --> Produkty`. "
"Klikněte na existující produkt nebo vytvořte nový a nastavte :guilabel:`Typ "
"produktu` na `Zboží`. Klikněte na kartu :guilabel:`Opakující se ceny` "
"a :guilabel:`Přidat řádek`. Vyberte existující :guilabel:`Opakující se plán` "
"nebo vytvořte nový a přidejte :guilabel:`Ceník`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:39
msgid "Choosing a delivery method"
msgstr "Výběr způsobu dodání"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:41
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Delivery "
"Methods`. By default there is only one delivery method available: Standard "
"delivery. Businesses with more substantial delivery needs can :doc:`create "
"new delivery methods </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>` or :doc:`add "
"third-party shipping carrier integration </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>` to "
"their Odoo databases."
msgstr ""
"Přejděte na :menuselection:`Aplikace Lager --> Konfigurace --> Způsoby "
"dodání`. Ve výchozím nastavení je k dispozici pouze jeden způsob dodání: "
"Standardní dodání. Podniky s rozsáhlejšími potřebami dodávek mohou do svých "
"databází Odoo :doc:`vytvořit nové způsoby dodání </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"new_delivery_method>` nebo :doc:`přidat integraci externího přepravce </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:50
msgid "Creating a subscription delivery quotation"
msgstr "Vytvoření nabídky předplatného s dodávkou"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:52
msgid ""
"As with creating a subscription delivery product, creating a subscription "
"delivery quotation is similar to :ref:`the regular process <subscriptions/"
"quotations>`, but with an additional step. After entering all other "
"information for the quotation, click the :guilabel:`Add shipping` button in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab. Choose a shipping method from the dropdown "
"and, if necessary, enter the item's weight and dimensions and click "
"the :guilabel:`Get rate` button. Then click :guilabel:`Add` to add the "
"delivery details as a line item to the quotation. From here, proceed with "
"confirming the quotation and generating a sales order as normal."
msgstr ""
"Stejně jako při vytváření produktu předplatného s dodávkou je vytvoření "
"nabídky předplatného s dodávkou podobné :ref:`běžnému procesu <subscriptions/"
"quotations>`, ale s dalším krokem. Po zadání všech dalších informací pro "
"nabídku klikněte na tlačítko :guilabel:`Přidat dopravu` na "
"kartě :guilabel:`Řádky objednávky`. Vyberte způsob dopravy z rozbalovací "
"nabídky a v případě potřeby zadejte hmotnost a rozměry položky a klikněte na "
"tlačítko :guilabel:`Získat sazbu`. Poté klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat`, "
"abyste přidali podrobnosti o dodání jako řádkovou položku do nabídky. Odtud "
"pokračujte potvrzením nabídky a vygenerováním salgsordre jako obvykle."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:61
msgid "Validating delivery orders"
msgstr "Potvrzení dodacích příkazů"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:63
msgid ""
"Once the sales order for a subscription delivery product has been finalized, "
"a :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button appears that opens the delivery order "
"for the sale. After clicking through, if there is enough stock to fulfill "
"the delivery order, it appears as being in the :guilabel:`Ready` stage. If "
"there is not enough stock to fulfill the order, it appears as "
"being :guilabel:`In Progress` instead. Once the delivery order is in the "
"Ready stage, click :guilabel:`Validate` to advance the stage "
"to :guilabel:`Done` and automatically generate a delivery slip and send it "
"to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Jakmile je salgsordre pro produkt předplatného s dodávkou dokončena, objeví "
"se chytré tlačítko :guilabel:`Dodávka`, které otevře dodací příkaz pro "
"prodej. Po kliknutí, pokud je dostatek zásob k vyřízení dodacího příkazu, "
"zobrazí se ve fázi :guilabel:`Připraveno`. Pokud není dostatek zásob k "
"vyřízení objednávky, zobrazí se místo toho jako :guilabel:`Probíhá`. Jakmile "
"je dodací příkaz ve fázi Připraveno, klikněte na :guilabel:`Potvrdit`, "
"abyste posunuli fázi na :guilabel:`Hotovo` a automaticky vygenerovali dodací "
"list a odeslali ho zákazníkovi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:72
msgid ":doc:`../subscriptions/renewals`"
msgstr ":doc:`../subscriptions/renewals`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:75
msgid ":doc:`../sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales/products_prices/prices/pricing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/subscriptions_deliveries.rst:76
msgid ":doc:`../subscriptions/automatic_payments`"
msgstr ":doc:`../subscriptions/automatic_payments`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:3
msgid "Upsell subscriptions"
msgstr "Mersalg på abonnementer"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:5
msgid ""
"When a subscription sales order is opened, either in the **Sales** or "
"**Subscriptions** apps, that subscription may then be upsold via "
"the :guilabel:`Upsell` button at the top of the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Når en abonnementssalgsordre åbnes, enten i appen **Salg** eller "
"**Abonnementer**, kan dette abonnement derefter mersalges via "
"knappen :guilabel:`Mersalg` øverst på salgsordren."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:None
msgid ""
"Upsell button for subscription sales orders highlighted in Odoo "
"Subscriptions."
msgstr "Upsell-knap til abonnementsalgsordrer fremhævet i Odoo Abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:11
msgid ""
"Upselling involves changing a subscription to include a more expensive "
"product or service. Upselling may also involve adding discounts to encourage "
"conversion. Before sending an upsell quotation to a customer, the unit "
"price, taxes, and even discount may all be adjusted. Using the *Upsell* "
"feature allows for greater convenience and continuity when making changes to "
"an exisiting subscription."
msgstr ""
"Upselling involverer at ændre et abonnement til at inkludere et dyrere "
"produkt eller en dyrere tjeneste. Upselling kan også involvere at tilføje "
"rabatter for at tilskynde til konvertering. Før der sendes et upsell-tilbud "
"til en kunde, kan enhedsprisen, skatter og selv rabat alle justeres. Brug af "
"funktionen *Upsell* giver større bekvemmelighed og kontinuitet, når der "
"foretages ændringer i et eksisterende abonnement."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:17
msgid "How to upsell a subscription"
msgstr "Sådan laver du upsell af et abonnement"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:20
msgid ""
"A subscription sales order **must** be invoiced before it can be upsold."
msgstr "En abonnementsalgsordre **skal** faktureres, før den kan upsælges."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:22
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Upsell` button to bring up a new quotation form. This "
"quotation's status as an upsell is indicated by the :guilabel:`Upsell` icon "
"in the corner of the form. The chatter for the new form also includes "
"information linking the upsell order to the original order."
msgstr ""
"Klik på knappen :guilabel:`Upsell` for at åbne en ny tilbudsformular. Dette "
"tilbuds status som et upsell angives af ikonet :guilabel:`Upsell` i hjørnet "
"af formularen. Chatten for den nye formular inkluderer også oplysninger, der "
"forbinder upsell-ordren med den oprindelige ordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:None
msgid ""
"Chatter for an upsell order showing information related to the original "
"subscription sales\n"
"order."
msgstr ""
"Chat for en upsell-ordre, der viser oplysninger relateret til den "
"oprindelige abonnementsalgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:30
msgid ""
"Within the new form, the initial subscription product appears in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab. The :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab also "
"features a reminder that recurring products are prorated based on the "
"original subscription's starting date."
msgstr ""
"I den nye formular vises det oprindelige abonnementsprodukt i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer`. Fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` indeholder også "
"en påmindelse om, at tilbagevendende produkter forholdsmæssigt beregnes "
"baseret på det oprindelige abonnements startdato."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:35
msgid ""
"The prorated amount is **only** applied to *Service* product types. It is "
"**not** applied to *Goods*, even if the message appears and suggests "
"otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Det forholdsmæssige beløb anvendes **kun** på produkttyper af typen "
"*Service*. Det anvendes **ikke** på *Varer*, selvom meddelelsen vises og "
"antyder andet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:38
msgid ""
"From this new upsell quotation form, new subscription products can be added "
"in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, by clicking :guilabel:`Add a product` "
"and selecting the desired subscription products. Once the desired upsell "
"subscription products have been added, the quotation can be sent to the "
"customer for approval by clicking the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Fra denne nye upsell-tilbudsformular kan nye abonnementsprodukter tilføjes i "
"fanen :guilabel:`Ordrelinjer` ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj et produkt` "
"og vælge de ønskede abonnementsprodukter. Når de ønskede upsell-"
"abonnementsprodukter er blevet tilføjet, kan tilbuddet sendes til kunden til "
"godkendelse ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once the quotation is confirmed by the customer, the upsold products are "
"added to the initial subscription. The quotation's prices are then prorated "
"based on the current invoicing period's remaining time."
msgstr ""
"Når tilbuddet bekræftes af kunden, tilføjes de upsælgede produkter til det "
"oprindelige abonnement. Tilbuddets priser beregnes derefter forholdsmæssigt "
"baseret på den aktuelle faktureringsperiodes resterende tid."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:47
msgid ""
"Once the customer approves, click the :guilabel:`Confirm` button on the "
"quotation, making it a sales order. When that's clicked, a :guilabel:`Sales "
"History` smart button appears, displaying how many sales orders are attached "
"to this initial subscription sales order."
msgstr ""
"Når kunden godkender, skal du klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Bekræft` på "
"tilbuddet, hvilket gør det til en salgsordre. Når der klikkes på den, vises "
"en smart-knap :guilabel:`Salgshistorik`, der viser, hvor mange salgsordrer "
"der er knyttet til denne oprindelige abonnementsalgsordre."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:51
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Sales History` smart button is clicked, Odoo reveals a "
"separate page containing a list of the related sales orders, clearly "
"showcasing their individual :guilabel:`Subscription Status`."
msgstr ""
"Når der klikkes på den smarte knap :guilabel:`Salgshistorik`, viser Odoo en "
"separat side med en liste over relaterede salgsordrer, der tydeligt viser "
"deres individuelle :guilabel:`Abonnementsstatus`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:None
msgid ""
"The related sales order accessed from the Sales History smart button in Odoo "
"Subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"Den relaterede salgsordre tilgået fra smart-knappen Salgshistorik i Odoo "
"Abonnementer."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:59
msgid "Discount configuration"
msgstr "Rabatkonfiguration"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:61
msgid ""
"Discounts can be easily applied to upsold subscriptions to incentivize "
"customers to purchase more expensive or additional subscriptions. To do "
"this, the *Discounts* feature must be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Rabatter kan nemt anvendes på upsælgede abonnementer for at tilskynde kunder "
"til at købe dyrere eller yderligere abonnementer. For at gøre dette skal "
"funktionen *Rabatter* være aktiveret."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:64
msgid ""
"To activate the *Discounts* feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. Scroll to the :guilabel:`Pricing` section and "
"tick the checkbox beside :guilabel:`Discounts`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"For at aktivere funktionen *Rabatter* skal du navigere "
"til :menuselection:`Salg-app --> Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`. Rul ned "
"til afsnittet :guilabel:`Prisfastsættelse` og sæt flueben "
"ved :guilabel:`Rabatter`. Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:69
msgid "Create alternative"
msgstr "Opret alternativ"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:71
msgid ""
"Customers can also be presented with alternative subscription quotations. "
"Alternative quotations can be created even after sending an upsell quotation "
"to a customer."
msgstr ""
"Kunder kan også præsenteres for alternative abonnementstilbud. Alternative "
"tilbud kan oprettes, selv efter at der er sendt et upsell-tilbud til en "
"kunde."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/upselling.rst:74
msgid ""
"To create an alternative upsell quotation, click the :guilabel:`Create "
"Alternative` button at the top of the upsell quotation form. This opens a "
"new upsell sales order that is linked to the previous upsell and "
"subscription sales orders."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette et alternativt upsell-tilbud skal du klikke på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Opret alternativ` øverst på upsell-tilbudsformularen. "
"Dette åbner en ny upsell-salgsordre, der er forbundet med de tidligere "
"upsell- og abonnementsalgsordrer."

